hadiths[502]{hadithnumber,text}:
4773,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon mein se sab se badh kar umda akhlaq ke Malik they. aapney eik roz mujhey kisi kaam ke liye bheja , maine kaha : Allah ki qasam ! main nahin jaunga , halanke merey dil mein tha ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo bhi farmaya hai main uskey liye jaunga . kehtey hain : isliye main nikla yahan tak ke bachchon ke paas se mera guzar hua jo baazar mein khel rahey they. to achcha ( kya dekhta hun ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey merey peechhey se meri guddi pakdey huey they. maine aap ki taraf dekha to aap hans rahey they. farmaya : '' Anas ! udhar jao jahan ka maine tumhen kaha hai. maine arz kiya : haan aey Allah ke Rasool ! ja raha hun. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : qasam Allah ki ! maine saat saal aap ki khidmat ki hai ya nau saal , mujhey nahin maloom ke aapney mujhey kisi kaam par jo maine kiya ho, kabhi yun kaha ho : to ne aisey kyon kiya?'' ya koi kaam jo maine chhod diya ho, to kaha ho ke ''aisey aisey kyon nahin kya?''"
4774,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Madina Munawwara mein das saal tak khidmat ki jabkey main eik naukhez ladka tha. merey sab kaam us meyaar ke nahin hotey they jaisey merey Habib (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khahish hoti thi. (uskey bawajood ( aapney mujhey kabhi uff tak nahin kaha aur na yun kaha : to ne ye kyon kiya ? aur is tarah kyon nahin kiya?
4775,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne ham se bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey sath masjid mein baitha kartey they aur baaten kartey rehtey they. jab aap uthtey to ham bhi khadey ho jatey , yahan tak ke ham dekhtey ke aap apni kisi ehliya ke ghar mein dakhil ho gaey hain. chunanche aap eik din hamarey sath baaten kartey rahey jab aap uthey to ham bhi uth khadey huey . phir ham ne dekha ke eik badwi ne aap ko ja liya aur aap ki chadar pakad kar khinchney laga yahan tak ke aap ki gardan surkh ho gaee . Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke chadar bhi badi khurdari thi. aap uski taraf mutawajjeh huey to us Erab (dehati) ne aap se kaha : mujhey merey ye do oont laad den . bila-shuba aap mujhey koi apney zaati maal se nahin dengey aur na apney baap ke maal se dengey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, main Allah se istighfar karta hun. nahin, mein Allah se istighfar karta hun. nahin, mein Allah se istighfar karta hun aur main tujhey us waqt tak nahin dey sakta jab tak mujhey chhod na do jo ye tum ne mujhey pakda hua hai.'' aur wo badwi har baar aap se yehi kehta tha : Allah ki qasam ! main tumhen nahin chhodun ga. aur raawi ne puri hadees zikr ki . phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko bulaya aur us se kaha : '' isko iskey ye dono oont laad do , eik par jo aur eik par khajoor.'' phir aap hamari taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''tum log jao, tum par Allah ki barkaten hon.''"
4776,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nek chalan, umda kirdaar aur miyaanaarawi (beech ki rah ikhtiyar karna) nabuwat ka pachchiswan hissey hai.''"
4777,"Janab Sehal bin Muaz apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ghussa pi jaey jabkey wo us par amal daraamad ki qudrat rakhta ho to Allah usey qiyamat ke din bar sar makhluq bulaeyga aur usey ikhtiyar dega ke jannat ki hoor-ain mein se jisey chahey muntakhab kar ley . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke sanad ke raawi Abu-Marhoom ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Memun hai."
4778,"As-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se kisi ke bete ne apney walid se bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : aur mindarja baala hadees ki manind zikr kiya. kaha : ''Allah usey aman aur emaan se bhar dega.'' magar us mein ye nahin : ''Allah usey bulaeyga.'' mazeed kaha : ''jis shakhs ne zeenat aur jamaal wala libas tarak kiya halanke wo uski istataat rakhta ho.'' Bishr bin Mansoor ne kaha mera khayal hai ke aapney farmaya : '' . . . . wo usney tawaazeh (mehmaan nawazi) ki wajeh se chhoda ho to Allah usey izzat aur karaamat ka joda pahnaaey ga. aur jisney Allah ki raza ke liye nikah kar diya ho to Allah usey taaje-shaahi pahnaaeyga .''"
4779,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum log zabardast pahlwaan (bahut ziyada pachhaarney wala) kisey kehtey ho?'' Sahaba ne kaha : jisey log pachhaad na saken . aapney farmaya : ''nahin, pahlwaan wo hai jo ghussay ki haalat mein apney aap ko qabu mein rakhey.''"
4780,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke do aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney eik doosrey ko gaaliyaan deney lagey. unmein eik is qadr ghazabnaak ho gaya ke maine samjha ke intehai ghussey se uski naak hi char jaeygi . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba mujhey eik kalima maloom hai, agar ye keh ley to uska ye ghussa door ho jaey.'' (Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo kiya hai? aapney farmaya : ''yun keh ley (اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الشيطان الرجيم ) ''aey Allah ! main shaitan mardud ke shar se teri panah chahta hun.'' chunanche Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) us shakhs se kehney lagey ke ye kalima padh ley magar usney inkar kar diya balke aur ladney laga aur ghussey honey laga."
4781,"Janab Sulaiman bin Surad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney eik doosrey ko bura bhala kehney lagey yahan tak ke eik ki aankhen surkh ho gaeen aur galey ki ragein phool gaeen . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey eik kalima maloom hai, agar ye shakhs wo kalima keh ley to us-se ye kaiyfiyat door ho jaeygi .) aur wo kalima ye hai :) (أعوذ بالله من الشيطان الرجيم) ''main shaitan mardud ke shar se Allah ki panah mein aata hun.'' magar wo aadmi kehney laga : kya tum samajhtey ho ke main majnun hun?"
4782,"Hazrat Abu-Zar Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko ghussa aaye aur wo khada hua ho, to baith jaey, isi tarah agar uska ghussa fard (door) ho jaey (to behtar) warna let jaey.''"
4783,Janab Bakr (bin Abdullah) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko (kisi kaam sey) bheja aur ye hadees bayan ki. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees (bawajood-ye-key mursal hai) sahih tar hai.
4784,"Abu-Waeil Al Qaas (Waaiz) kehtey hain ke ham Janab Urwa bin Muhammad Sa'di (Rahimahullah) ke yahan gaey. eik aadmi ne unse koi baat ki to unhen ghussa aa gaya , to wo uthey aur wuzu kiya phir (wuzu karkey) wapis aaye aur bayan kiya ke mujhey merey walid ne merey dada Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''bila-shuba ghussa shaitan ki taraf se hota hai aur shaitan ko aag se paida kiya gaya hai aur aag ko pani se bujhaya jata hai. so jab tum mein se kisi ko ghussa aa jaey to usey chahiye ke wo wuzu kar ley.''"
4785,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab bhi do kamon mein se kisi ka ikhtiyar diya gaya to aapney hamesha aasan hi ko ikhtiyar farmaya ba-sharte-ke wo gunah na hota . agar us mein gunah hota to aap sab se badh kar us-se door honey waley hotey they. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kabhi apni zaat ke liye intiqam nahin liya , siwaye iskey ke Allah ki hurmaton ki paamaali hoti ho, to usmein Allah ke liye intiqam letey they."
4786,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kabhi kisi khaadim ya aurat ko nahin maara.
4787,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Allah ke farman (خذ العفو) ''maaf karna apnaaiye'' ki tafseer mein unhoney bayan kiya ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya tha ke logon ki aadaat aur maamlat mein unke sath maafi ka ravaiya ikhtiyar karen."
4788,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab kisi ke mutalliq koi (namunasib) khabar milti to yun na kehtey : falan ko kya hua hai ke yun kehta hai ya karta hai? balke yun farmatey : '' logon ko kya hua hai ke aisey aisey kehtey hain ya kartey hain.''
4789,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya jabkey uspar zard rang ka kuchh nishan tha. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi shakhs ko uskey munh par bahut kam aisi baat kehtey they jo usko nagawar ho. (yani uski ghalati par usko na toktey they.) jab wo chala gaya to aapney farmaya : ''agar tum hi usko keh do ke is (rang) ko dho daley (to behtar ho). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke iska raawi ''Salam Alvi'' haqeeqat mein aulade-Ali mein se nahin (ye doosra shakhs hai. iska naam Salam bin Qais hai aur ye Basri hai chunkey sitarey ooper hotey hain ( sitaron par nazar rakhney ki wajeh se usey Alvi kaha janey laga . isney Hazrat Adi bin Irtaat ke samney chaand dekhney ki gawahi di to unhoney qubul na ki.
4790,"Nasar bin Ali aur Muhammad bin Mutawakkil Asqalani dono Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marfooan riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin bholaa-bhaala aur sakhi hota hai aur faajir aadmi faraibi aur bakheel hota hai.''"
4791,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan aaney ki ijazat talab ki to aapney farmaya : ''kunbey ka bahut bura aadmi hai.'' phir farmaya : ''usey ijazat dey do bula lo.'' jab wo andar aa gaya to aapney uskey sath nihayat narmi ke sath baaten kin . Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (kehti hain mein) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney uskey sath badi narmi ke sath baaten ki hain, halanke aapney uskey mutalliq aisey aisey farmaya tha. aapney farmaya : ''qiyamat ke din Allah ke yahan sab se bura wo aadmi hoga jisey logon ne uski badsalooki ki wajeh se chhod diya ho.''"
4792,"Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, eik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan aaney ki ijazat chahi to aapney farmaya : ''kunbey ka bahut bura aadmi hai.'' phir jab wo aap ke paas aa gaya to aapney uskey sath badi faraakhdili ke sath baaten kin . jab wo chala gaya to maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jab usney ijazat maangi to aapney farmaya : ''kunbey ka bura aadmi hai.'' jab wo aa gaya to aapney uskey sath badi faraakhdili ke sath baaten ki hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Aaisha ! bila-shuba Allah taala kisi bad-go, takalluf se badgoi karney waley se mohabbat nahin karta . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ( بئس أخو العشيرة (ke maani ki baabat sawal kiya gaya to unhoney bayan kiya ke ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khususiyat hai."
4793,Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne is qissey mein bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Aaisha ! bad-tareen hain wo log jin ki zaban ke shar se bachney ke liye izzat ki jaey.
4794,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine nahin dekha ke kisi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kaan mein sargoshi karna chahi ho to aapney us-se apna sar door kar liya ho, yahan tak ke wo aadmi khud hi aap se apna sar door karta tha. aur maine nahin dekha ke kisi ne aap ka haath pakda ho, to aapney uska haath jhatak diya ho, yahan tak ke wo khud se aap ka haath chhodta tha."
4795,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Ansari ke paas se guzrey jabke wo apney bhai ko haya ke baarey mein waaz kar raha tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey chhod do. bila-shuba ''haya'' emaan se hai.''"
4796,"Janab Abu-Qatada (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ham Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they jabkey wahan Bashir bin Kab bhi they (ba ke pesh ke sath) Hazrat Imran bin Husain ne hadees bayan ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haya sarasar khair hai.'' Bashir bin Kab ne kaha : hamein kaee kitabon mein milta hai ke baaz haya itminan aur waqar ki wajeh se hoti hai aur baaz haya kamzori aur buzdili ki wajeh se hoti hai. to Hazrat Imran ne hadeese-Rasool dobara dohraee aur phir Bashir ne bhi apni baat dohra di. raawi bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) is qadr ghussay mein aagey ke unki aankhen surkh ho gaee aur boley : main tujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees suna raha hun aur to mujhey apni kitabon se bataey ja raha hai. ham ne kaha : aey Abu-Najeed ! bas keejiye . bas keejiye. (isey yehi tanbih kafi hai.)"
4797,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''guzishta anbiya ki ta'leemaat mein se jo baat logon ke paas mehfooz rahi hai wo yehi hai ke jab haya na rahey to jo ji chahey kar.'' (be-haya baash aur har che khuwahi kin.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) se puchha gaya : kya Qaanabi ke paas Shoba ke wastey se is hadees ke siwa koi aur hadees bhi hai? unhoney farmaya : nahin."
4798,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''bila-shuba momin apney Husne-akhlaq (umda aadaat) ki bina par roze-daar, shabb zinda daar ka darja hasil kar leta hai.''"
4799,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meezaan (taraazu) mein Husne-khalq se badh kar aur koi chiz bhari nahin hogi. Abu-Waleed Tiyalisi kehtey hain (Qasim bin Abi Baza ki sanad mein tasreeh hai ke) maine Ata kekharani se suna hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye Ata bin Yaqoob hain aur Ibrahim bin Naafe ke mamu hain. unki nisbat '' kekharani aur kokharani '' dono tarah bayan ki jati hai."
4800,"Saiyedna Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main zimmedar hun eik mehal ka , jannat ki eik janib mein , us shakhs ke liye jo jhagda chhod dey , agar-che haq par ho. aur eik mehal ka , jannat ke darmiyan mein , us shakhs ke liye jo jhoot chhod dey, agar-che mazak hi mein ho, aur jannat ki aalaa manaazil main eik mehal ka , us shakhs ke liye jo apney akhlaq ko umda bana ley.''"
4801,"Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kadwee zaban wala bad-mizaaj jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga aur na takabbur se chalney wala. aur ''جواظ'' ka mafhoom hai sakht mizaj , bad-khulq."
4802,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki oontni) azbaa hamesha sab se aagey rehti thi koi us se aagey na badhta tha. eik badwi apney eik jawan oont par aaya aur us oontni se muqabla kiya aur is-se aagey badh gaya. is-se as-haabe Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko goya nagawari hui , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah par ye haq hai ke jo koi bhi duniya mein ooncha hota hai to wo usey neecha dikha deta hai."
4803,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye qissa marwi (bayan) hai. is mein hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah par haq hai ke duniya mein jo chiz bhi sar ooncha uthati hai to wo usey neecha dikha deta hai.
4804,Janab Hammam (bin Haris (Rahimahullah) ( kehtey hain ke eik shakhs aaya aur usney Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke munh par unki tareef shuru kar di. to Hazrat Miqdad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ne mitti uthai aur uskey munh par dey maari aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jab tumhara samna aisey logon se ho jo tareef aur khushamad karney waley hon to unke munhon mein mitti dalo.''
4805,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Bakra apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein doosrey ki tareef ki to aapney us-se farmaya : '' to ne apney sathi ki gardan kaat di .'' aapney ye teen baar farmaya. phir farmaya : ''agar koi apney kisi sathi ki tareef karna hi chahta ho to chahiye ke yun kahey : ''main usey yun samajhta hun. . . . ke wo aisey aisey hai. . . aur Allah ke ilm ke muqabley mein , main iski safai nahin deta.''"
4806,Janab Mutrif (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke merey walid ( Abdullah bin shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ke main bano Aamir ke wafad ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. to ham ne kaha : aap hamarey (saiyed) sardar hain. aapney farmaya : ''saiyed (aur haqeeqi sardar) Allah tabarak w taala hai.'' ham ne kaha : aap hamarey sahab Fazal aur Fazilat aur udaarta aur sakhawat dikhaney hain. to aapney farmaya : ''tum is tarah ki baat keh saktey ho. magar kahen shaitan tumhen apna wakeel na bana ley (ke koi aisi baat keh guzro jo meri shaan ke mutabiq na ho.'')
4807,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shan Wale Allah  ki sift aur narmi se mausoof hai, usey narmi aur naram khooi pasand hai. wo us par wo kuchh inayat farmata hai jo turshi aur karakhtgi (sakhtee) par nahin deta.''"
4808,"Janab Miqdam bin Shureh apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke maine Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke jangal mein jana kaisa hai? to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un tilon ki taraf nikal jaya kartey they. aapney eik baar irada kiya ke jangal mein jaeyn to aapney merey paas sadqe ki oonton mein se eik oontni bheji jis par abhi sawari nahin hui thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! narmi ikhtiyar kiya karo, bila-shuba narmi jis chiz mein bhi ho wo usey muzayyan aur khoobsurat bana deti hai aur jis chiz se nikal li jaey usey bad-soorat aur bhadda bana deti hai. ibn Sabaah ne apni hadees mein wazeh kiya ke (حرمة) se murad aisi oontni hai jis par ba-qaeeda sawari na hui ho."
4809,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs naram khooi se mehroom hua wo sab bhalaiyon se mehroom hua.''"
4810,"Janab Musab apney walid (Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain. Aamash kehtey hain aur mujhey aisey hi maloom hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya, aapney farmaya : ''kisi kaam mein jald bazi nahin ( karni ( chahiye siwaye uskey ke aakhirat ka kaam ho.''"
4811,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs logon ka shukriya ada nahin karta , wo Allah ka bhi shukr guzar nahin hota .''"
4812,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke muhajrin kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! sara ajr to ansaar ley gaey . aapney farmaya : ''nahin, jab tak tum Allah taala se unke liye duayen kartey rahogey aur un se ehsan mandi ka izhar karogey.'' (us tarah unko ajr milney ke sath sath tumhen bhi milega)"
4813,"Janab Umara bin Ghaziya ne bayan kiya ke meri qom ke eik aadmi ne Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kiya, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisey koi Atiya aur hadiya diya jaey to agar himmat ho aur muyassar ho to uska badla dey aur agar na paey to uski madah (tareef) aur sanaa karey. jisney apney Mohsin ki madah (tareef) ki usney uska shukriya ada kiya aur jisney us (ke ehsan) ko chupaya usney uski nashukri ki. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat ko Yahya bin Ayub ne b-waaste Umara bin Ghaziya , Shurehbil se aur usney Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke sanad mein Umara bin Ghaziya ne jis aadmi ka naam liya aur yun kaha hai ke ''meri qom ke eik aadmi ne mujh se bayan kiya. ''wo Shurehbil hi hai. goya unhoney uska naam zikr karna pasand nahin kiya."
4814,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi par koi ehsan kiya phir us doosrey ne uska zikr kiya to ye uska shukriya ada karna hai aur agar us ( doosrey ( ne usey chupaya to ye uski nashukri aur na-qadri ki.''"
4815,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' raaston par bethney se bacho.'' logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamen to us se chaara nahin hai, ham ne aapas mein baat cheet kerni hoti hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar us se inkar kartey ho to phir raastey ke haq ka khayal rakho .'' unhoney puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! raastey ka kya haq hai? aapney farmaya : '' nazar neechi rakhna, takleef deh chiz ka hata dena, salam ka jawab dena , bhali baat kehna aur burai se rokna .''"
4816,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is qissey ( hadees ( mein bayan kya, aapney farmaya : '' raah geer ki rehnumai karna ( bhi raastey ke haq mein shamil hai.'' ("
4817,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne is qissey ( hadees ( mein bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pareshan haal ki madad karo aur raasta bhool janey waley ki rehnumai karo.''
4818,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey aap se eik kaam hai. aapney us se farmaya : ''aey Umme- falan ! kisi gali ke koney par beth jao main terey sath beth sakta hun (teri baat sun sakta hun.'') chunanche wo beth gaee aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi uskey sath beth gaey yahan tak ke usney apna maqsad pa liya . ibn Esa ne (حتى قضت حاجتها) ka lafz zikr nahin kya. aur kaseer (bin Ubaid ( ne apni sanad mein) Anana se riwayat kartey huey ) عن حميد an أنس kaha .
4819,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke us aurat ki aql mein koi kami thi. aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani bayan kya.
4820,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' behtareen majlis wo hai jo wasee aur khuli ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke raawi hadees Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Umra ka sahih nasab yun hai : '' Abdur-Rehman bin Amr bin Abu-Umra ansari''"
4821,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Saiyedna abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi shakhs dhoop mein betha ho, . . . . Mukhlid ke alfaz hain agar koi saye mein betha ho. . . . aur phir us se saya tal jaey aur wo kuch dhoop mein aa jaey aur kuch saye mein to wahan se uth jaey.''"
4822,"Janab Qais ( Qais bin abu-Haazim ( apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke wo aaye jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they. to ye dhoop mein khadey ho gaey, to aapney unhen hukm diya to saye mein chaley gaey ."
4823,Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laye jabke Sahaba toliyan banaey bethey they. to aapney farmaya : ''kya baat hai ke tum toliyon mein juda juda bethey ho ?''
4824,Janab Aamash (Rahimahullah) ne ye riwayat bayan ki aur kaha : goya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ijtimaiyat ko pasand farmaya.
4825,Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein aatey they to jahan majlis pahunchi hoti wahin ( aakhir mein) beth jaya kartey they.
4826,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lanat ki hai aisey aadmi par jo halqey ke darmiyan mein bethta hai.
4827,"Janab Saeed bin abul-Hasan bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) eik gawahi ke silsiley mein hamarey yahan tashrif laye to majlis mein se eik aadmi unke liye apni jagah se uth khada hua. to unhoney us jagah bethney se inkar kar diya aur kaha : tehqiq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya hai. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se bhi roka hai ke koi shakhs kisi doosrey ke kapdey se jo usney usey na pehnaya ho, apna haath poonchhey."
4828,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to eik aadmi uskey liye apni jagah se uth khada hua , wo ( aaney wala ( wahan bethney laga to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko mana farma diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abu-Khaseeb ka naam Ziyad bin Abdur-Rehman hai."
4829,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin jo Quran majeed ki tilawat karta hai uski misal turanj ki si hai ke uski khushbu umda aur wo khush zaiqa bhi hota hai. aur momin jo Quran ki tilawat nahin karta uski misal khajoor ki si hai ke uska zaiqa umda hota hai magar us mein khushbu nahin hoti. aur faajir aadmi jo Quran padhta hai uski misal reaihaan (naazbu) ki si hai ke uski khushbu umda magar zaiqa kadwa hota hai. aur faajir aadmi jo Quran nahin padhta uski misal hanzal (indrayan) ki si hai ke uska zaiqa kadwa aur khushbu koi nahin hoti . aur nek aur saleh sathi ki misal kastoori waley ki manind hai agar tujhey us se na bhi mili to uski khushbu to ( zarur ( pahunchegi aur burey sathi ki misal bhattii waley ki tarah hai, agar tujhey uski kaalik na lagi to dhuwan to zarur aaeyga ."
4830,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ka pehla hissey '' uska zaiqa kadwa hota hai.'' tak bayan kya. aur ibn Muaz ne mazeed kaha ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham kaha kartey they ke saleh sathi ki misal . . . . aur baqiya hadees bayan ki ."
4831,"shabeel bin Azra ne Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' saleh sathi ki misal . . . .'' aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kya."
4832,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sirf momin aadmi ki sohbat ikhtiyar kar aur tera khana bhi koi muttaqi hi khaye.''"
4833,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insan apney mehboob sathi ke deen par hota hai. to tumhen chahiye ke ghor karo kis se dosti kar rahey ho.''"
4834,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) marfooan ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey) bayan kartey hain : '' roohen ( zaleel mein) mujtama lashkar thin , jinka ( wahan ( aapas mein ta'aruf ho gaya (duniya mein) unke andar ulfat ho jati hai aur jin ki) wahan ( aapas mein naa-waaqifi rahi ho wo (us duniya mein bhi) eik doosrey se juda juda rehti hain.''"
4835,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney Sahaba ko jab apney kisi kaam ke liye bheja kartey they to unhen farmatey : ''khushkhabri deney waley banna , nafrat na dilaana, aasani karna aur tangi aur mashaqqat na dalna .''"
4836,"Hazrat Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to log meri madah aur merey aamaal ka zikr kerney lagey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main uskey mutalliq tum se ziyada janta hun.'' maine arz kya : aapney baja farmaya , merey maa baap aap par qurban! aap merey sharaakat daar they aur bahut hi khoob sharaakat daar they. aap mein mukhalifat kerney ya ladney jhagadney wali koi baat nahin thi."
4837,Janab Yusuf (Rahimahullah) apney walid Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bethey baaten kar rahey hotey to aap ki nazar aksar aasman ki taraf hoti thi.
4838,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki guftgu mein intehai thehraw hota tha.
4839,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki guftgu is qadr wazeh hua karti thi ke her sunney wala usey samajh leta tha.
4840,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her guftgu jiski ibtida (shuruat) Allah ki hamd w sana se na ho wo be barkat hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat ko Yunus , Aqeel, Shoaib, aur Saeed bin Abdul-Azeez ne Zohri ke wastey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal riwayat kya hai."
4841,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her wo khutba jis mein tashahud ( Allah ki toheed aur Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki risaalat ka zikr ( na ho aisey hai jaisey juzaam zada (naqis aur aeb daar) haath .''
4842,Memun bin Abu-Shabeeb se riwayat hai ke Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas se eik saail guzra. to aapney usey roti ka eik tukda diya. phir eik doosra aadmi guzra jisney (achchhey) kapdey pehney huey they aur uski haalat umda thi to unhoney usko bithla kar khilaya . unse is farq ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''har shakhs ko uskey maqam par rakho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Yahya ki hadees mukhtasar hai Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Memun ne Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko nahin paya hai.
4843,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba boodhey musalman aur sahibe-Quran ki izzat karna jo us mein ziyadtiyon aur taqseer (kamiyon) se bachta ho aur) usi tarah ( haakim aadil ki izzat karna , Shan Wale Allah ki izzat karney ka hissa hai.''"
4844,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib , apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do aadmiyon ke darmiyan ghus kar mat betha jaey siwaye iskey ke wo ijazat dey den.''"
4845,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi ke liye halal nahin ke do aadmiyon ko juda juda kar dey ( jo mil kar baithey huey hon to un mein ghus baithey) siwaey iske ke un dono ki ijazat ho.''"
4846,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baithtey to apney ghutnon ko seeney se mila kar apney haath unke gird lapet liya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke sanad mein Mazkur Abdullah bin Ibrahim shaikh munkir hadees hai.
4847,Hazrat Qeela binte Makhrama (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke wo ( ''قرفصاء'' ( ki soorat mein baithey huey they (ke unke ghutney seeney se miley huey aur haath unke gird liptay huey they ( maine jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khushu aur inkisaar ki is kaifiyat mein dekha to khof se laraz uthi .
4848,Hazrat Shareed bin suwaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas se guzrey jabke main apna baayan haath kamar ke peechey karkey angoothey ki jagah par dabao dal kar betha hua tha to aapney farmaya : ''kya tum un logon ki tarah baithtey ho jin par Allah ka ghazab hua hai.''
4849,Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mana farmaya kartey they ke Isha ki Namaz se pehley soyaa jaey ya iskey baad baaton mein mashghool raha jaey.
4850,"Saiyedna Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Fajr ki Namaz padha letey to apni jagah par paalti maar kar baithey rehtey , yahan tak ke Suraj khoob chadh aata ."
4851,"Saiyedna Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do aadmi apney teesrey sathi ko chhod kar sargoshi na karen, us-se wo ranjeedah hoga.''"
4852,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya aur mazkura baala ki manind bayan kiya. Abu-Saaleh kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha , agar chaar afrad hon to? kaha ke us mein koi harj nahin."
4853,"Janab Suhel bin Abi saleh kehtey hain ke main apney walid ke paas baitha hua tha, unke paas eik ghulam bhi tha. to wo uth kar gaya aur phir wapis aa gaya to merey walid ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se hadees bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apni jagah se uth kar jaey aur phir wapis lot aaye to wohi us jagah ka ziyada haqdaar hai.''"
4854,"Janab Kab Ayaadi (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaya jaya karta tha. to Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( kisi jagah ( tashrif farma hotey aur ham bhi aap ke ird-gird baith jatey , to agar aap uth kar jatey aur wapis aaney ka irada rakhtey to apna joota ya jo kuch aap par) kapda waghera) hota, wahan chhod jatey , us-se Sahaba kiram aap ke wapis aaney ke mutalliq jaan jatey aur baithey rehtey."
4855,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo log kisi majlis se uthen aur unhoney us-mein Allah ka zikr na kiya ho, to wo aisey hain goya kisi murdar gadhey par se uthey hon aur (aakhirat mein) ye majlis unke liye hasrat ka baais hogi.'' (tamanna karengey kash ke ham ne us mein Allah ka zikr kar liya hota.)"
4856,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi jagah ya majlis mein baitha ho aur usmein usney Allah ka zikr na kiya ho, to ye uskey liye Allah ki taraf se bahut nuqsan ka baais hogi . aur jo koi kisi jagah letaa ho aur us-mein usney Allah ka zikr na kiya ho, to ye uskey liye Allah ki taraf se bahut nuqsan ka baais hogi.''"
4857,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne farmaya : chand kalimaat hain jo koi unhen apni majlis se uthtey huey teen baar padh ley to ye uskey liye kaffara bin jaeyngey , aur jo koi unhen apni us majlis ke doran mein padh ley , wo majlis khair ki ho ya zikr ki to ye uskey liye aisey hongey jaisey kisi tehreer ko mohar band kar diya gaya ho (uskey liye uska ajr aur gunahon ka kaffara hona mehfooz hoga. wo kalimaat ye hain : ) (سبحانك اللهم وبحمدك la إله إلا أنت أستغفرك وأتوب إليك) ''aey Allah ! to apni ta'reefon samet paak hai, terey siwa koi mabud nahin, mein tujh se apney gunahon ki maafi maangta hun aur main teri hi taraf ruju karney wala hun.''"
4858,"Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Amr ne b-waaste Maqbari Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kiya."
4859,Hazrat Abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney aakhiri dinon mein jab kisi majlis se uthtey to ye kalimaat kehtey they : (سبحانك اللهم وبحمدك أشهد أن la إله إلا أنت أستغفرك وأتوب إليك) eik aadmi ne aap se poochh liya ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap ye kalimaat kehtey hain jo pehley nahin kaha kartey they (is ki kya wajeh hai?) aapney farmaya : ''ye us chiz ke kaffaarey ke liye hai jo majlis mein ho jati hai.''
4860,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shakhs mujhey merey Sahaba ki baabat koi baat na pahunchaey . main chahta hun ke main tumharey paas aaun , to mera seena saaf ho (kisi ke mutalliq merey dil mein کدورت na ho).''"
4861,Janab Abdullah bin Amr bin Faghwa Khuzaae apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bulwaya . . . . jabke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey kuchh maal de-kar Makka mein Hazrat Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan bhejna chaha rahey they jo wo ehle-Quraish mein taqseem kar deta aur ye Fateh Makka ke baad ka waqia hai. . . aapney mujhey farmaya : ''koi safar-ka-sathi dhoond lo.'' chunanche Amr bin Umayya Zamri merey paas aaya aur kaha : suna hai ke tum makkey jana chahtey ho aur rafeeqe-safar ki talash mein ho. maine kaha : haan. usney kaha : main tumharey sath chalunga . chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya ke maine rafeeqe-safar dhoond liya hai. aapney puchha : ''kon?'' maine bataya ke Amr bin Umayya Zamri . aapney farmaya : ''jab tum uski qom ke ilaqey mein utro to hoshiyar rehna.'' kehney waley ne kaha hai ke bikri (ba ke zer ke sath) tera bhai hai magar us par aitimaad na karna . chunanche ham nikal padey . yahan tak ke jab main abwaa maqam par pahuncha to usney mujh se kaha ke mujhey apni qom se eik kaam hai main wadan ja raha hun tum yahan ruk kar mera intizar karna . maine kaha : khair salamti se jao . jab wo rawana hua to mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman yaad aaya to main apney oont par Sawar ho liya aur usey bhagaataa hua asaafir tak ja pahuncha. to achcha dekhta hun ke Umayya apni qom ke kuchh logon ke sath merey aadey aa gaya hai. chunanche maine apna oont aur tez bhagaayaa yahan tak ke un se aagey nikal gaya. jab unhoney dekha ke main unke haathon se nikal gaya hun to wo wapis ho gaey . phir wo (akela) merey paas aaya aur kehney laga ke mujhey apni qom ke yahan eik kaam tha. maine kaha : hoga. yahan tak ke ham Makka aagey aur maine wo maal Hazrat Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawaley kar diya.
4862,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin eik bil se do baar nahin dasaa jata.''"
4863,Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab chaltey to aisey lagta jaisey aagey ko jhukey jatey hon.
4864,Hazrat Abu-Tufail (Aamir bin Waasila) (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha. Saeed Jareeri ne un se puchha ke aapney unko kyonkar dekha? unhoney kaha : aap safed rang aur intehai khoobsurat they aur jab chaltey they to lagta tha ke ooper se nichey ko utar rahey hain.
4865,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke aadmi apni taang par taang rakhey . Quteba ki riwayat mein izafa hai ke jab wo chit letaa hua ho."
4866,Janab Ibad bin Tameem apney chacha ( Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha jabke aap chit letey huey they. Qaanabi ne kaha : masjid mein letey huey they aur aap apni eik taang dusri par rakhey huey they.
4867,Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) aisey kar liya kartey they (letney ki haalat main apni eik taang par dusri rakh liya kartey they).
4868,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi tum se baat kartey huey idhar-udhar se choukanna ho raha ho (ke kahin koi sunta to nahin) to ye baat amanat hai.''"
4869,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' majaalis amanat ke sath hain. siwaye teen majlison ke jin mein nahaq khoon bahaney , ya nahaq fohsh-kaari, ya nahaq maal maarney ki baat ho.''"
4870,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke nazdik qiyamat ke roz amanat mein ye baat bahut badi khayanat shumar hogi ke mard apni biwi ke aur biwi apney shohar ke qarib ho aur phir uskey raz ko afshaa (zahir) kar dey.''"
4871,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chughal khor jannat mein nahin jaeyga.''"
4872,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bad-tareen hai wo aadmi jo do-rukha ho ke unke paas jaey to eik munh ho, doosron ke paas jaey to doosra munh.''"
4873,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiskey duniya mein do munh huey ( jo aadmi do rukha hua ( qiyamat ke roz uski do zabanen hongi jo aag ki hongi.''"
4874,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! gheebat kya hai? aapney farmaya : '' tumhara apney bhai ka aisey andaz mein zikr karna jisey wo napasand karta ho.'' kaha gaya : jo baat main keh raha hun agar wo merey bhai mein (haqeeqat mein) ho? (to bhi wo gheebat hogi ?) aapney farmaya : ''agar us mein wo baat mojud ho aur tum kaho , tab hi to gheebat hai. agar tum koi aisi baat kaho jo us mein na ho, to tum ne uspar bohtan lagaya.''"
4875,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se keh diya : aap ko Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) mein yehi kafi hai ke wo aisey aisey hai. . . Musaddad ke ilawa doosrey ne wazahat ki ke us se unki murad Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ka pasta qad hona tha. . . . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne aisa kalima kaha hai ke agar usey samandar mein mila diya jaey to kadwa ho jaey.'' Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney kisi ki naqal utaari to aapney farmaya : ''main kisi ki naqal utaarna pasand nahin karta , chahey mujhey itna itna maal bhi miley.''"
4876,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se bada sood (sab se badi ziyadti) ye hai ke insan nahaq kisi ki izzat se kheley.''"
4877,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' beshak kabeera gunahon main eik bada kabeera gunah ye hai ke insan apney musalman bhai ki nahaq hatak aur tauheen kar dey . kabeera gunahon mein ye bhi hai ke koi eik ke badley do gaaliyaan dey ."
4878,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab mujhey Mairaj karaai gaee to mera guzar eik aisi qom par hua jinkey nakhun tanbey ke they jo apney chehron aur seenon ko chheel rahey they. maine puchha : aey Jibrael ! ye kon log hain? unhoney kaha : ye wo hain jo doosrey logon ka gosht khatey aur unki izzaton se kheltey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : is riwayat ko Yahya bin Usman ne baqiya se riwayat kiya magar is mein Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahin (mursal riwayat kiya)."
4879,Esa bin Abi Esa Sailheeni ne Abu-Mugheera se isi tarah riwayat kya jaisey ke) mazkura baala hadees mein) ibn Musaffi ne kaha .
4880,"Hazrat Abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey wo logo jo apni zabanon se emaan laye ho magar emaan unke dilon mein nahin utra hai ! musalmanon ki badgoi na kya karo aur na unke eaibon ke dar-pai  hua karo, bila-shuba jo unke eaibon ke dar-pai hoga Allah bhi uskey eaibon ke dar-pai hoga. aur Allah jiskey eaibon ke dar-pai ho gaya to usey uskey ghar ke andar ruswa kar dega .''"
4881,"Hazrat Mustaurid (bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi musalman ki wajeh se eik bhi luqma khaya hoga (us ki gheebat ya hatak waghaira karkey kisi se koi iwaz (badal) liya hoga) tu Allah taala usey jahannam se isi tarah ka luqma khilaaeyga . aur jisey kisi musalman ki wajeh se koi kapda pehnaya gaya tu Allah taala usey jahannam se usi tarah ka kapda pahnaaeyga . aur jisney kisi ka naam uchhala aur usey dikhaawe ke maqam par pahunchaya ho (us ka charchaa kiya ho) tu Allah qiyamat ke roz uski tashheer kerega aur dikhaawe ke maqam par khada kerega.'' (aisa azab dega ya aisi jagah azab dega ke uska sab logon mein charchaa hoga.)"
4882,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik musalman ke liye doosrey musalman ka maal , izzat aur khoon haram hai. bandey ke liye yehi burai kafi hai ke wo apney musalman bhai ko haqeer janey.''"
4883,"Janab Sehal bin Muaz bin Anas Juhni apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi momin ka kisi munafiq se bachaoo kiya. . . . raawi kehta hai mera khayal aapney yun kaha : Shan Wala Allah qiyamat ke din eik farishta bhejeyga. jo uskey gosht ko jahannam ki aag se bachaey ga. aur jisney kisi musalman par kisi chiz ki tohmat lagai ke uskey zariey se usney us par aeb lagana chaha tu Allah usey jahannam ke pul-siraat par rokey rakhega , yahan tak ke uskey kahey ki saza puri ho jaey.''"
4884,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) aur Abu-Talha bin Sehal Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi musalman ko kahin be-yaaro madadgar chhoda jahan ke wo be izzat kiya ja raha tha tu Allah usey aisi jagah be-yaaro madadgar chodeyga jahan wo chaheyga ke (kash) uski madad ki jaey. aur jisney kisi musalman ki madad ki (aur uska difaa kya ( jahan usey be-izzat aur zaleel kiya ja raha tha tu Allah uski aisi jagah madad farmaeyga jahan wo chaheyga ke uski madad ki jaey. Yahya kehtey hain : mujhey ye hadees Ubaidullah bin Abdullah bin umr aur Aqba bin Shaddad ne bhi riwayat ki hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye Yahya bin Saleem , Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke sahibzadey hain jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke azad karda ghulam they aur Ismail bin Bashir bano Maghaala ke azad karda ghulam hain aur Aqba bin Shaddad ki bajaey Utba bhi kaha gaya hai."
4885,"Hazrat Jundub (bin Abdullah Bijli (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai ke eik dehati aaya, usney apni sawari bithaai , uska ghutnaa baandha phir masjid ke andar aa gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi . jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam phera to wo apni sawari ke paas aaya, usey khola , us par Sawar hua phir oonchi aawaz mein bola : aey Allah ! mujh par rehem kar aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par rehem kar , aur hamari is rehmat mein kisi aur ko shareek na kar . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum kya samajhtey ho ye ziyada jahil hai ya uska oont . kya tum ne suna nahin jo wo keh raha hai?'' Sahaba ne kaha : kyon nahin."
4886,"Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha : kya tum se mumkin nahin ke Abu-Zaigham ya Abu-Zam-Zam ki tarah ho jao. naam mein Muhammad bin Ubaid ko shubha hua hai. jab subah hoti to wo kaha karta tha : aey Allah ! maine apni izzat terey bandon ke liye sadqa kar di hai. ( jinhonne meri koi be-izzati ki ho maine unhen maaf kar diya hai. ("
4887,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Ajlan se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi aajiz hai ke Abu-Zam-zam ki tarah ho jaey ?'' Sahaba ne kaha : Abu-Zam-zam kon hai? aapney farmaya : ''tum se pehley eik aadmi guzra hai. aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. kaha : jisney mujhey bura bhala kaha ho meri izzat uskey liye ( sadqa ( hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : is riwayat ko Haashim bin Qasim ne riwayat kiya to kaha : (عن محمد بن عبداللہ العمي an ثابت قال حدثنا Anas an النبي ﷺ) mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hammad ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai."
4888,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''agar to logon ki kamiyon ke peechhey pad gaya to to unhen bigaad dega '' . . . . ya . . . .''qarib hai ke to unhen bigaad dey.'' to Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : ye baat jo Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni Allah ne unhen us se bahut faeyda diya."
4889,"Janab Jubair bin Nafair , Kaseer bin Murra , Amr bin Aswad (Rahimahullah), Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb aur Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ameer ( haakime waqt ( agar tohmat aur shubhe ki bina par logon ke dar pai hoga to unko bigaad dega.''"
4890,"Janab Zaid bin Wahab bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas eik aadmi laya gaya aur bataya gaya ke ye falan aadmi hai aur iski dadhi se sharab ke qatrey tapak rahey hain. to Abdullah ne kaha : hamen toh laganey se mana kiya gaya hai, haan agar koi baat wazeh zahir ho to ham uski muaakhza (pakad) karengey."
4891,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi ki koi burai dekhi aur phir us par parda dal diya to usney goya qabr mein gaadii gaee ladki ko zinda kar diya .''"
4892,"Janab Dukhain jo Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke secretery they, ne bayan kiya ke hamarey kuchh hamsaaey they jo sharab peetey they. maine unko mana kiya magar wo baaz na aaye . maine Hazrat Aqba se kaha : hamarey ye hamsaaey sharab peetey hain, maine inko mana kiya hai magar ye baaz nahin aaye . main police ko bulata hun. to unhoney kaha : dafa kar unhen chhod dey. main phir dobara Hazrat Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur unhen bataya ke hamarey un hamsaayon ne sharab chhodney se inkar kar diya hai aur main police ko bulata hun. to unhoney kaha : afsos tujh par ! unhen chhoddey. bila-shuba maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai. aur (mazkura baala) hadees Muslim (bin Ibrahim) ke ham-maani bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Haashim bin Qasim ne Janab Leis se is riwayat mein bayan kiya ke aisey mat karo, balke unhen nasihat karo aur dhamki do."
4893,"Hazrat Salim apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalman musalman ka bhai hai, na us par zulm aur ziyadti karta hai aur na usey uskey halaat par chhod deta hai (ke uski koi parwa hi na karey) jo shakhs apney bhai ke kaam mein hoga (us ki koi zarurat puri kerega) tu Allah uskey kaam mein hoga (Allah taala bhi uski koi zarurat puri kar dega). aur jisney kisi musalman ka eik dukh door kiya Shan Wala Allah qiyamat ke roz uska eik dukh door kerega, aur jisney kisi musalman ka eaib chhupaya, Shan Wala Allah qiyamat ke roz uskey eaib chhupaeyga."
4894,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aapas mein gaali galoch karney waley jo bhi kahen, uska gunah ibtida (shuruat) karney waley hi par hai jab tak ke mazloom ziyadti na karey.''"
4895,"Hazrat Ayaaz bin Himaar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Shan Wale Allah ne mujhey ''wahi'' farmaee hai ke tawaazeh aur inkisaar (mahman nawazee aur winamrta) ikhtiyar karo yahan tak ke koi kisi par zulm aur ziyadti na karey aur na koi kisi par fakhr karey.''"
4896,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke eik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baithey huey they aur aap ke sath aap ke Sahaba bhi they ke eik aadmi ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura bhala kaha aur unhen aziyat di , to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh rahey . usney phir dusri baar aziyat di to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh rahey . usney phir teesri baar aziyat di to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey badley mein kuchh kaha . jab Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us-se badla liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth khadey huey, to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap mujh se naraz ho gaey ? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aasman se eik farishta utra tha jo us aadmi ko uskey kahe par jhutla raha tha. jab tum ne us se badla liya to shaitan aa gaya. aur jab shaitan aa gaya to main nahin baith sakta.''"
4897,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura bhala kaha karta tha. aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Safwan bin Esa ne ibne Ajlan se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai jaisey Sufiyan ne riwayat kiya hai.
4898,"Janab (Abdullah) ibne Aun (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke main aayat kareema (ولمن انتصر بعد ظلمه فأولئك ما عليهم من سبيل) mein waarid ( انتصار (ke maani poochhta tha ke mujhey Ali bin Zaid bin Jada'an ne apni soteli walida Umme- Muhammad se riwayat kiya aur ibne Aun ne kaha : un logon ka khayal tha ke Umme-Muhammad , Ummul-momenin ( Sayeda Aaisha ( (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaya jaya karti thi. Umme-Muhammad ne kaha : Ummul-momenin (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye, jabkey (Ummul-momenin) Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) bhi hamarey yahan thin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey apney haath se chheda (jaisey miyan biwi mein hota hai) to maine aap ka haath pakad liya aur aap ko isharay se samjhaya ke wo ( Zenab bhi) hamarey yahan mojud hain. to aap ruk gaey . phir Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) , Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par bolney lagen . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ko mana kiya magar wo na rukin to aapney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke usey jawab do , chunanche unhoney usi andaz se jawab diya aur) Sayeda Zenab par) ghalib aa gaeen. to Sayeda Zenab (Raziallahu anha) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaeen aur kaha ke Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) tum logon (banu Hashim) ke baarey mein aisey aisey baaten karti hai aur aisey aisey kiya hai. to Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas) ayen to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen kaha : ''Rabe Kaaba ki qasam ! ye tumharey Abba ki chahetee hai.'' chunanche Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) wapis chali gaeen aur aa kar unhen ( Hazrat Ali aur Zenab (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko) bataya ke maine aap ko aisey aisey kaha hai to aapney mujhey aisey aisey kaha hai. chunanche Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur aap se is baarey mein baat ki."
4899,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumhara koi faut ho jaey to usey chhod do aur uski eaib-chini mat karo.''"
4900,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney marney walon ki khoobiyaan bayan kiya karo aur unki buraiyon se baaz raho.''"
4901,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''bani-Israel mein do aadmi aapas mein bhai baney huey they. eik gunahon mein mulawwis tha jabke doosra ibadat mein koshaan rehta tha. ibadat mein raaghib jab bhi doosrey ko gunah mein dekhta to usey kehta ke baaz aa ja . aakhir eik din usney doosrey ko gunah mein paya to usey kaha ke baaz aa ja. usney kaha : mujhey rehney dey , mera maamla merey Rab ke sath hai. kya to mujh par koi chaukeedaar bana kar bheja gaya hai? to usney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! Allah tujhey maaf nahin karega ya tujhey jannat mein dakhil nahin karega. chunanche wo dono faut ho gaey aur Rabbul-Aalameen ke yahan jama huye, tu Allah ne ibadat mein koshish karney waley se farmaya : kya to merey mutalliq ( ziyada ( janney wala tha ya jo merey haath mein hai tujhey us par qudrat hasil thi ? aur phir gunah gaar se farmaya : ja meri rehmat se jannat mein dakhil ho ja . aur doosrey ke mutalliq farmaya : usey jahannam mein ley jao.'' Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : us zaat ki qasam jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! usney aisi baat keh di jisney uski duniya aur aakhirat tabah karkey rakhdi."
4902,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi gunah is laaiq nahin ke Allah taala uski saza duniya mein bhi jaldi dey dey aur uskey sath sath aakhirat mein bhi uski saza jama rakhey jaisey ke zulm aur ziyadti aur qata' rehmi hai.''
4903,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hasad (doosron par jalney aur kudhney) se apney aap ko bachao. bila-shuba hasad nekiyon ko aisey kha jata hai jaisey aag indhan ko . . . . ya farmaya. . . . ghaas phoos ko kha jati hai.''"
4904,"Janab Sehal bin Abu-Umama (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke wo aur uska walid Madina mein Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey . ye Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ke daur ki baat hai, jabkey wo Madina ke governer they. ham Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan pahunchey to wo badi halki phulki Namaz padh rahey they, goya ke musafir ki Namaz ho ya uskey qarib . jab unhoney salam phera to merey walid ne puchha : Allah aap par rehem farmaai ! ye bataeyn ke ye farz Namaz thi ya aapney koi nafl padhey hain? unhoney kaha : ye farz Namaz thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz aisey hi hoti thi. maine us mein se koi chiz nahin chhodi siwaye uskey jo koi mein bhool gaya hun (to wo alag baat hai). unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''apni jaanon par sakhti mat karo warna tum par sakhti ki jaeygi. bila-shuba kaee qomon ne apni jaanon par sakhtiyan kin tu Allah ne bhi un par sakhti ki . jangalon mein ma'badon ke andar aur girja-gharon mein unhi logon ke baqiaaya log hain ( jin ka Quran majeed mein zikr hai). un logon ne rehbaniyat ikhtiyar kar li, unhoney ye bidat nikali , ham ne usey un par farz nahin kya tha.'' (Al-hadeed-27) phir ham agley din subah ke waqt unke paas gaey to unhoney kaha : kya tum sawar nahin ho jatey ke kuchh dekho aur ibrat pakdo . walid ne kaha : haan chaltey hain. chunanche ham sab Sawar ho liye . to unhoney kuchh bastiyan dikhaeen ke unke log halak ho gaey they, mar khapp gaey they aur unhen barbad kar diya gaya tha aur unki bastiyan apni chhaton par giri padi thin . unhoney kaha : kya tum in bastiyon ko pehchantey ho? walid ne kaha : nahin, mujhey in bastiyon ka aur un logon ka koi ilm nahin hai. unhoney bataya ke ye us qom ki bastiyan hain jin ko bagawat aur hasad ne halak karkey rakh diya tha. bila-shuba hasad se nekiyon ka Noor bujh jata hai aur bagawat iski tasdeeq karti hai ya isey jhutla deti hai. aankh zina karti hai aur phir haath , paon , jism , zaban aur sharmgaah uski tasdeeq kar detey hain ya takzeeb (jhutla dena)."
4905,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banda jab kisi chiz ko lanat karta hai to wo lanat aasman ki janib chadhti hai to uskey aagey aasman ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain. phir wo zameen ki taraf utarti hai to uskey aagey uskey darwazey band kar diye jatey hain. phir wo daain aur baeyn jati hai. agar koi jagah na paey to jis par lanat ki gaee ho us par waqey ho jati hai ba-sharte-ke wo chiz uski haqdaar ho warna uskey kehney waley ki taraf laut jati hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Marwan bin Muhammad ne kaha : (sanad mein mazkur raawi Waleed bin Ribah Darasal ( Ribah bin Waleed hai. Yahya bin Hassaan ko is mein weham hua hai."
4906,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki lanat se lanat mat kiya karo aur Allah ke ghazab aur dozakh ki badduaa mat diya karo.''"
4907,Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo bahut ziyada lanat karney waley huey wo ( kisi ke) sifarishi ya gawah nahin bin sakengey.''
4908,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne hawa ko lanat ki . aur Muslim (bin Ibrahim (ke alfaz hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein hawa se eik shakhs ki chadar ud-gaee to usney usey lanat kar di , to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey lanat mat karo, bila-shuba ye (Allah ke hukm ki) paband hai. aur bila-shuba jisney kisi chiz ko lanat ki jabke wo uski haqdaar na ho, to ye lanat karney waley par laut-aati hai.''"
4909,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke unki koi chiz chori ho gaee to wo (chor ko) badduaa deney lagin . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : ''uski saza ko us se halka mat karo.''
4910,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghussa mat kiya karo . eik doosrey se hasad mat kiya karo . eik doosrey ko peeth mat diya karo (ke mail-jol chhod do) balke Allah ke bandey bhai bhai bin kar raho. kisi musalman ke liye halal nahin ke apney bhai se teen raat se ziyada mail-jol chhodey rahey.''"
4911,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi musalman ke liye jayez nahin ke apney bhai ke sath teen din se ziyada mail jol chhodey rahey ke jab dono ki mulaqat ho to ye bhi munh pher ley aur wo bhi. aur un mein sab se behtar wo hai jo Assalamualaikum kehney mein ibtida (shuruat) karey.''"
4912,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi musalman ko halal nahin ke kisi sahibe emaan se teen din se ziyada muqaatiaa (talluq khatm) karey. agar teen din guzar jaeyn to chahiye ke us se miley aur usko salam kahe . agar wo salam ka jawab dey dey to ajr aur sawab mein dono shareek ho gaey . agar wo jawab na dey to uska gunah usi doosrey ke zimmey hai.'' Ahmed ( Ahmed bin Saeed Sarkhasi ( ne mazeed kaha : '' salam karney wala muqaatiey (talluq khatm karne) ke gunah se nikal gaya .''"
4913,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi musalman ko munasib nahin ke kisi musalman se teen din se ziyada muqaatiaa (talluq khatm) rakhey . chunanche ( chahiye ke) jab us se miley to usey salam kahe , teen baar , agar kisi baar bhi jawab na dey to wohi gunah-gaar hua.''"
4914,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi musalman ke liye halal nahin ke apney bhai se teen din se ziyada mail-jol chhodey rahey. jisney teen din se ziyada muqaatiaa (talluq khatm) kiya aur mar gaya to wo aag mein jaeyga.''"
4915,Hazrat Abu-Kharaash Sulmee (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap farma rahey they : ''jisney eik saal tak apney bhai se rawaabit todey rakhey to wo aisey hai jaisey uska khoon bahaayaa ho.''
4916,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har somwaar aur Jumerat ko jannat ke darwazey kholey jatey hain to har wo banda jo Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek na karta ho usey bakhsh diya jata hai. siwaye uskey ke uskey aur uskey bhai ke darmiyan bughz aur narazi ho. to kaha jata hai : unhen mohlat do yahan tak ke suleh kar lein . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni baaz azwaaj (biwi) se chaalis din tak mail-jol chhod diya tha. aur Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne marney tak apney eik bete se muqaatiaa (talluq khatm) kiye rakha tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : yani ye muqaatiaa aur mail-jol chhodna agar Allah ke liye ho to us par ye chetawniyan nahin hain. Janab umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ne eik aadmi se apna chehra dhanp liya tha."
4917,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney aap ko guman se bachao , bila-shuba guman sab se jhooti baat hai, aur na toh lagao aur na jasoosi karo.''"
4918,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin momin ka aaena hai, aur momin momin ka bhai hai, uskey maal ka (nuqsan hota ho to) bachao karta hai aur uski ghair mojudgi mein uski ( izzat ki) hifazat karta hai.''"
4919,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen rozey , Namaz aur sadqey se badh kar afzal darjaat ke aamaal na bataun?'' Sahaba na kaha : kyon nahin, aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''aapas ke mail jol aur rawaabit ko behtar banana. (aur iskey bar-aks) aapas ke mail jol aur rawaabit mein phoot dalna (deen ko) munda deney wali khaslat hai.''"
4920,"Janab Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman apni walida (Umme-Kulsoom binte Aqba bin Abi Mueet) se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne do aadmiyon mein suleh karaney ki khatir baat bana kar kahi ho, usney jhoot nahin bola.'' Ahmed bin Muhammad aur Musaddad ki riwayat ke alfaz hain : ''jisney logon mein suleh karaney ke liye bhali baat kahi ya pahunchaai wo jhoota nahin hai.''"
4921,"Hazrat Umme-kulsoom binte Uqba (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai kehti hain : maine nahin suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jhoot ki kahin ijazat di ho magar teen mawaqe par . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''main aisey aadmi ko jhoota shumar nahin karta jo logon mein suleh karaney ki gharz se koi baat banata ho aur uska maqsad siwaye suleh aur islah ke kuchh na ho, aur jo shakhs ladaai mein koi baat banaey aur shohar jo apni biwi se ya biwi apney shohar ke samney koi baat banaey.''"
4922,Hazrat Rabeea binte-Muawwiz bin Afraa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab meri rukhsati hui us subah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye aur merey bistar par usi tarah tashrif farma huey they jaisey tum ( Khalid bin zakwaan ( merey paas baithey huey ho. to ( ansaar ki) chhoti bachchiyaan apney apney daf bajaney lagin aur merey un baap-daada ka zikr karney lagin jo Badr mein Shahid ho gaey they. yahan tak ke un mein se eik bachchi ne kaha : aur ham mein aisa Nabi hai jo kal aainda ki baat janta hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' is baat ko chhod do aur wohi kaho jo pehley keh rahi thi.''
4923,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Madina tashrif laye to Habshi logon ne aap ki aamad ki khushi mein apney nezon ke sath ( jangi fan ka ( muzahira kiya tha.
4924,"Janab Naafe bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne baansuri ki aawaz suni to unhoney apni ungliyan apney kanon par rakh lein aur raastey se door chaley gaey . aur phir mujh se puchha : aey Naafe ! kya bhala kuch sun rahey ho? maine kaha : nahin, to unhoney apni ungliyan apney kanon se utha lein aur kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha to aapney is tarah ki aawaz suni to aapney aisey hi kiya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye hadees munkar (zaeef) hai."
4925,(Mazkura baala riwayat ke silsiley mein) Janab Naafe (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath sawari par unke peechhey baitha hua tha ke unka guzar eik charwahey ke paas se hua jo baansuri baja raha tha. aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind zikr kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Mut-im (bin Miqdam) aur Naafe ke darmiyan Sulaiman bin Musa ka wasta badha diya gaya hai.
4926,"Janab Memun bin Mehraan , Naafe se riwayat kartey hain ke ham Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath they ke unhoney eik baansuri waley ki aawaz suni . aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind zikr kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye riwayat sab se ziyada munkir (zaeef) hai."
4927,"Salam bin Miskeen eik shaikh se riwayat kartey hain jo Janab Abu-Waeil (Rahimahullah) ke sath eik waleemey mein hazir tha. isliye wo log aapas mein khelney khilaney aur gaaney lagey to Janab Abu-Waeil (Rahimahullah) ne apni kamar se apna kapda khola aur kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai, wo farmatey they maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahey they : ''gaanaa dil mein nifaq paida karta hai.''"
4928,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik hijda laya gaya jisney apney haath paon mehndi se rangey huey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq daryaft farmaya : ''usey kya hai? '' bataya gaya ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye aurton ke sath mushaabihat karta hai. to aapney hukm diya aur usey maqam naqeea ki taraf nikal bahir kar diya gaya. Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham usey qatl na kar den? aapney farmaya : ''mujhey namaaziyon ko qatl kerney se mana kya gaya hai. Abu-Usama kehtey hain ke naqeea ( noon ke sath ( Madina se eik janib eik jagah ka naam hai jo Baqeea se alag hai.
4929,ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke yahan tashrif laye aur dekha ke unke yahan eik hijda hai aur wo un ( umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) (ke bhai Abdullah se keh raha hai ke agar kal Allah tumhen taaif Fateh kara dey to main tumhen eik aurat ke mutalliq bataunga jo chaar se aati aur aath se lot-ti hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen apney gharon se nikal do . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : uska matlab ye tha ke aurat ke pet par (farba andaam honey ki wajeh sey) chaar bal padtey hain. ( aurat ke pet par samney ki janib se chaar bal aur jab pusht pherey to pahluon ki janib se yehi bal chaar chaar ho kar aath bin jatey hain to arab mein aurat ka us andaz se farba andaam hona Husn samjha jata hai. (
4930,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hijdey banney waley mardon aur mardana andaz ikhtiyar kerney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai. aur farmaya : ''unhen apney gharon se nikal bahir karo, aur falan falan hijdey ko bahir nikal do .''"
4931,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main gudiyon ke sath khela karti thi. to kabhi-kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aatey aur merey yahan (mohalley ki) bachchiyan hotin. jab aap tashrif latey to wo chali jatin aur jab aap chaley jatey to wo aa jaya karti thin.
4932,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwa tabuk ya khaibar se wapis tashrif laye to merey taaqchey ke aagey parda pada hua tha. hawa chali to usney pardey ki eik janib utha di tab samney merey khiloney aur gudiyaan nazar aaye . aapney puchha : '' Aaisha ye kya hai? ''maine kaha : ye meri gudiyaan hain. aapney un mein kapdey ka eik ghoda bhi dekha jiskey do par they. aapney puchha : ''main unke darmiyan ye kya dekh raha hun ?'' maine kaha : ye ghoda hai. aapney puchha : '' aur uskey ooper kya hai? ''maine kaha : uskey do par hain. aapney kaha : ''kya ghodey ke bhi par hotey hain ?'' Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aapney suna nahin ke Hazrat Suleman Alehissalam ke ghodey ke par they? kehti hain : chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is qadr hansey ke maine aap ki daadhein dekhin .
4933,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se shaadi ki to meri umr saat saal ya chhe saal thi. jab ham Madina munawwara aaye to chand aurten aain . . . . Bishr bin Khalid ke alfaz hain : ( meri walida ( Umme-Ruman aain. . . . jabkey main eik jhooley par thi aur wo mujhey ley gaeen. mujhey tayyar kya, banaya sanwaara aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan bhej diya gaya. meri rukhsati hui to meri umr no saal thi. (meri walida ne) mujhey darwazey par khada kar diya to maine kaha ( هيه هيه ( yani inkar kerney ki aawaz . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) uski wazahat mein kehtey hain : yani maine lamba ( thanda ( saans liya aur mujhey eik ghar mein dakhil kar diya gaya to wahan ansaar ki kuch aurten thin. unhoney duaaey khair w barkat ke sath mera istaqbal kya. Hammad aur Abu-Usama ki riwayat eik doosrey mein mil gaee hai."
4934,Janab Abu-Usama ne mazkura baala hadees ke misl riwayat kya aur kaha : Allah karey teri qismat achi ho. aur mujhey un aurton ke hawaley kar diya. unhoney mera sar dhoya aur mujhey banaya sanwaara . aur main us waqt dar si gaee jab din chadhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey samney huey to unhoney mujhey aap ke hawaley kar diya.
4935,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab ham Madiney aaye to merey paas kuch aurten aain jabkey main eik jhooley par khel rahi thi. aur merey baal kanon se nichey utar rahey they. to wo mujhey ley gaeen aur mujhey tayyar kya, banaya sanwaara. phir wo mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aain. meri ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar ( rukhsati hui to meri umr no saal thi."
4936,"Janab Hisham bin Urwa ne apni sanad se us riwayat mein bayan kya ke Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : main apni saheliyon ke sath jhooley par thi , to unhoney mujhey eik ghar mein dakhil kar diya. wahan ansaar ki kuch aurten thin , to unhoney khair w barkat ki dua ke sath mera istaqbal kya."
4937,"Yahya bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haatib bayan kartey hain ke ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ham Madiney aaye aur bano Haris bin khazraj ke yahan hamara qiyam hua . kehti hain, Allah ki qasam ! main khajoor ki do lakdiyon mein lagey eik jhooley par thi ke meri walida ayen , to unhoney mujhey us se utaara, aur merey baal chhotey chhotey they. aur puri hadees bayan ki ."
4938,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs chausar khela usney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki .''"
4939,"Janab Suleman bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs nardsheer ( chausar ( khela goya usney apna haath suwar ke gosht aur khoon se aaluda kya. ''"
4940,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko dekha wo kabootri ke peechey laga hua tha. aapney farmaya : '' shetan , shaitaanni ke peechey laga hua hai.''"
4941,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain : '' rehem kerney walon par Rehman rehem farmaeyga . tum ehle zameen par rehem karo, aasman wala tum par rehem kerega . Musaddad ne (sanad mein waarid '' Abu-Qaboos '' ke mutalliq ( ye nahin kaha ke wo Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka maula tha. neez wazaahat k saath kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne riwayat kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai."
4942,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine us hujrey waley yani Hazrat abul-Qaasim saadiq w masdooq (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : '' kisi bad-bakht se hi rehmat chhini jati hai.''"
4943,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo hamarey chhoton par shafqat na karey aur hamarey badon ka haq na pehchaney wo ham mein se nahin.''"
4944,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' deen nasihat ( khulus w khair khuwahi (ka naam hai. deen nasihat ka naam hai. deen nasihat ka naam hai. Sahaba ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kis ke liye ? aapney farmaya : ''Allah ke liye, uski kitab ke liye, uskey Rasool ke liye, ahle-eman ke aimma w hukkaam aur aam musalmanon ke liye . ya kaha ke musalmanon ke aimma w hukkaam aur aam logon ke liye.''"
4945,"Hazrat Jarir (bin Abdullah bijli) (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sunney aur itaat kerney aur her musalman ke liye khair khuwahi kerney par baiat kar rakhi hai. raawi ne kaha : chunanche wo ( Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu)) jab koi chiz farokht kartey ya kharida kartey to kehtey : tehqiq jo chiz ham ne tum se li hai wo hamen apni chiz se jo ham ne tumhen di hai, ziyada piyari hai, chunanche tumhen ikhtiyar hai) apni chiz ya maal wapis lena chaho to ley saktey ho.)"
4946,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi musalman se duniya ka eik dukh door kya Allah azz-w-jall us se qiyamat ke roz ka eik dukh door kerega. aur jisney kisi mushkil mein padey shakhs ke liye aasani ki, Allah uskey liye duniya aur aakhirat mein aasani kerega. aur jisney kisi musalman ki parda daari ki Allah azz-w-jall duniya aur aakhirat mein uski parda daari kerega aur Allah azz-w-jall us waqt tak bandey ki madad mein rehta hai jab tak ke banda apney bhai ki madad mein rahey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Usman (bin abi Sheba ( ne abu-Muaawia se ye jumla riwayat nahin kya : '' jisney kisi mushkil mein padey shakhs ke liye aasani ki . . . .''"
4947,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' her neki sadqa hai.''
4948,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum qiyamat ke din apney aur apney aaba ke namon se pukarey jaogey. chunanche apney naam achey-achey rakha karo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibn Abu-Zakariya ne Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ko nahin paya ."
4949,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sab namon mein se Abdullah aur Abdur-Rehman Allah azz-w-jall ko bahut hi piyaarey hain.''"
4950,"Hazrat Abu-Wahab Jashmi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, . . aur unhen sahabi honey ka sharf hasil hai. . . wo kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' anbiya ke naam rakha karo aur Allah ko sab namon mein ziyada mehboob Abdullah aur Abdur-Rehman hain. sab se badh kar waqeiyat se qarib ye naam hain, Haris ( kheti baadi kerney wala (aur Hammam ( ranj w fikr mein pada hua (aur ye naam sab se burey hain, harab (ladaaka) aur Murra (kadwa).''"
4951,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke jab ( merey soteley bhai ( Abdullah bin abu-Talha ki wiladat hui to main usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaya. jabke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik chadar pehney apney oont ko gandhak laga rahey they. aapney puchha : ''kya tumharey paas khajoor hai? ''maine arz kya, ji haan. aur maine aap ko kaee khajuren pesh kin . aapney unhen apney munh mein dal kar chabaaya, phir bachey ka munh khol kar unhen uskey munh mein dal diya to wo apni zaban chalaney laga . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Ansariyon ki khajoor se mohabbat ! (yani dekho nau-maulood bhi kis chaahat se kha raha hai.'' (aur aapney uska naam Abdullah rakha ."
4952,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne '' aasiya '' naam badal diya aur farmaya : '' to jameela ( khoobsurat ( hai.''
4953,"Janab Muhammad bin Amr bin Ata (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hazrat Zenab bint Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne mujh se puchha ke tum ne apni bachi ka kya naam rakha hai? maine bataya ke '' barra '' ( nek , saliha) to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us naam se mana farmaya hai. mera naam '' barra '' rakha gaya tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney aap ko apney munh se nek aur saleh na kehlwaao. Allah tum mein se nek aur saleh logon ko khoob janta hai.'' puchha gaya : ham uska kya naam rakhen ? aapney farmaya : '' Zenab naam rakho .''"
4954,"Hazrat Usama bin Akhdari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke '' isram '' naami eik shakhs us wafad mein shamil tha jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan aaya . aapney us se puchha : '' tumhara naam kya hai? '' usney kaha : ''main isram ( kaatney wala ( hun, aapney farmaya : '' balke tum zar'a ho'' ( ba-maanaa boney aur kaasht kerney wala ( ."
4955,"Hazrat Hani bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab wo apni qom ka wafad lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un logon ko suna wo usey '' abul-Hakam '' ki kunniyat se pukartey hain, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bulaya aur farmaya : '' hukm '' ( faisla kerney wala ( Allah hi hai) ye usi ka naam hai) aur tamam faisley usi ki taraf hain. tumhen ye kunniyat '' abul-Hakam '' kyonkar di gaee hai? '' usney arz kya : beshak meri qom waley jab kisi chiz mein ikhtilaf kartey hain to merey paas aa jatey hain aur main un mein faisla kar deta hun aur phir dono razi ho jatey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to bahut achi baat hai. terey bete kon hain ?'' maine kaha : Shureh , Muslim aur Abdullah . aapney puchha : '' un mein bada kon hai? ''maine kaha : Shureh . aapney farmaya : '' to tum '' abu-Shuraih '' ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ye Shureh wohi hain jinhon ne qil'a tastar ki zanjeer todi aur us mein dakhil huey they. aur mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke unhoney tastar ka darwaza toda tha aur surang mein se uskey andar ghusey they."
4956,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab apney walid se wo dada ( huzn) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : '' tumhara kya naam hai? ''kaha : huzn .) ba-maana sakht aur dushwaar guzar zameen ( aapney farmaya : ''tum '' Sehal '' ho. ( ba-maana naram aur aasan ( .'' usney kaha : nahin '' Sehal '' ko to raundaa jata aur haqeer jana jata hai. Saeed kehtey hain : mujhey yaqeen raha ke hamen unke baad koi sakhti aur ghamii laahiq honey wali hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aas , aziz , atla, shetan , hakam, Ghurab , Hubaab aur Shahab ke naam badley hain. aur Shahab ka naam Hisham rakha . aur Harab ka Salam. Muztaja ka Manbais . eik ilaqey ka naam Ifra se badal kar khizra kar diya. شعب الضلالۃ ka شعب ,الھدی بنوالزنیہ ka banu-Rashda aur bano maghwiya ka banu-Rashda kar diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maine unki sandaein ikhtisaar ki wajeh se chhod di hain."
4957,"Janab Masruq se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se mila, to unhoney puchha tum kon ho? maine bataya ke Masruq bin Ajdaa. to umr ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''Ajdaa, shetan hai.''"
4958,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney bachey ya ghulam ka naam Yasar, mubarak, aasan, Ribah, Nafa Aawar, Najeeh,  kamyab, Aflah hergiz na rakhna. tum puchhogey kya wo yahan hai? to jawab milega nahin.'' ( maqsad ye hai ke is tarah badfali hogi) (Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( ye bas chaar naam hain, mazeed merey zimmey na laga dena ."
4959,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke ham apney ghulamon ke naam ye rakhen . Aflah , Yasar , Naafe aur Ribah ( nafa wala .)"
4960,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar Allah ne chaha main zinda raha to main apni ummat ko is se mana karunga ke wo '' Naafe , Aflah aur barkat '' naam rakhen .'' Aamash kehtey hain : mujhey maloom nahin Shekh ( abu-Sufiyaan ( ne Naafe ka zikr kya ya nahin. darasal aadmi jab aata hai aur poochhtey hai, kya barkat hai? '' to jawab milta hai nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : abu-Zubair ne b-waasta Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ki manind riwayat kya hai magar us mein '' barkat '' ka zikr nahin hai."
4961,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : '' qiyamat ke roz sab se bura naam us shakhs ka hoga jisney apna naam ''malikul-amlak'' (shahanshaah, maharaja) rakha . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Shuaib bin abu-Hamza ne b-waasta abu-Zanaad iski sanad se ye riwayat bayan ki to us mein (أخنع اسم) ki bajaey ( ) أخنى اسم) ( sabse bura naam ( kaha ."
4962,"Janab abu Jubera bin Suhaak bayan kartey hain ke aayat karima : (ولا تنابزوا بالألقاب بئس الاسم الفسوق بعد الإيمان) '' burey burey namon aur laqabon se mat pukaro , emaan ley aaney ke baad fisq ka naam bahut bura hai.'' ye ham , bano Salma ke baarey mein nazil hui thi. unhoney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein tashrif laye to ham mein koi aisa na tha ke uskey do ya teen naam na hon. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ko bulatey '' arey falan! ''to log kehtey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! rukiye. beshak ye aadmi is naam se naraz hota hai. chunanche aayat ( wla تنابزوا بالألقاب . . . .) utri ."
4963,"Janab Zaid bin Aslam apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne apney bete ko , jisney apni kunniyat '' abu-Esa '' rakh li thi , saza di. Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni kunniyat abu-Esa rakhi to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kaha : kya tumhen ye kafi nahin ke apni kunniyat '' abu-Adbullah '' rakh lo . unhoney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi ne meri ye kunniyat rakhi thi. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke agley pichley tamam gunah Allah ne bakhsh diye huey hain aur ham to eik doosrey jaisey log hain. ( ham mein koi bhi doosrey se afzal w aa'laa nahin) chunanche Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) apni wafat tak abu-Adbullah hi kahlaatey rahey ."
4964,"Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : maine Yahya bin moayan (Rahimahullah) se suna, wo Muhammad bin mehboob ki madah kartey they aur batatey they ke ye bahut ziyada sahab hadees they."
4965,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mera naam rakh saktey ho magar meri kunniyat par apni kunniyat na rakho . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke abu-Saaleh ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se aisey hi riwayat kya hai. neez abu-Sufiyaan , Salim bin Abu-Ja'ad , Suleman Yashkari aur ibne-Munkadir, Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aisey hi riwayat kartey hain aur Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi marwi (bayan) hai."
4966,"Janab abu-Zubair, Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs mera naam rakhey wo meri kunniyat ikhtiyar na karey. aur jisney meri kunniyat rakhi ho wo mera naam na rakhey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibne-Ajlaan ne b-waasta apney walid Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se usi riwayat ( riwayat Jabir (ke ham-maani riwayat kya hai. ( naam ya kunniyat mein se eik chiz jayez hai. dono ko jama karna jayez nahin .) aur abu-Zara'a se b-waasta Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) dono riwaayatein marwi (bayan) hain ( jama karna durust nahin, aur guzishta riwayat ki manind bhi ke sirf kunniyat jayez nahin .) Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Umra ki riwayat jo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se hai us mein bhi ikhtilaf hai. Sauri aur ibne-Juraij ne abu-Zubair ki manind riwayat kya ( jama karna durust nahin.) aur Maaqil bin Ubaidullah ne ibn Sirin ki tarah kaha ( naam rakhna jayez, magar kunniyat jayez nahin.) Musa bin Yasar ki riwayat b-waasta Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) mein bhi dono qol hain. us mein Hammad bin Khalid aur ibne-Abu-Fidyak ne ikhtilaf kya hai."
4967,"Janab Muhammad ibn hanfiya (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar aap ke baad merey yahan bacha paida ho, to kya main uska naam aur kunniyat aap ke naam aur kunniyat par rakh sakta hun ? aapney farmaya : '' haan .'' ( raawi hadees ( abu-Bakar bin Abu-Sheba ke alfaz mein) qillat (ka lafz nahin hai balke yun hai ke (قال علي للنبي ﷺ) '' Hazrat Ali ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochha.''"
4968,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey yahan bacha paida hua hai aur maine uska naam Muhammad aur kunniyat abul-Qaasim rakhi hai aur mujhey bataya gaya hai ke aap usey napasand farmatey hain. aapney farmaya : ''kya wajeh hai ke mera naam to jayez ho aur kunniyat haram .'' ya farmaya : '' kis chiz ne meri kunniyat haram thehra di aur naam jayez kar diya ?''
4969,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laya kartey they aur merey chhotey bhai ne jiski kunniyat '' abu-Umair '' thi , usney eik chidiya rakhi hui thi jis se wo khela karta tha. (us chidiya ko arbi mein (Nugher) kehtey they ( to wo mar gaee. eik din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas gaey aur usey ghamgin paya to puchha : ''usey kya hua hai? '' ham ne bataya ke uski chidiya ( Nugher ( mar gaee hai. to aapney us se farmaya : ''aey abu-Umair ! kya kar gaya ( tera ( ) Nugher ( ?''"
4970,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri sab saheliyon ki kunniyatein hain. aapney farmaya : '' to tum apney bete Abdullah ke naam se kunniyat rakh lo .'' maqsad tha ke apney bhaanjey ki nisbat se. Musaddad ne wazahat ki ke us se murad '' Abdullah bin Zuber '' hain. chunanche unhoney Umme- Abdullah kunniyat ikhtiyar kar li . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Qurran bin Tammam aur Maamer dono ne Hisham se usi ke manind riwayat kya hai aur Abu-Usama ne Hisham sey, usney Ibad bin Hamza se riwayat kya hai. aur aisey hi Hammad bin Salma aur Muslima bin Qanab ne Hisham se usi tarah riwayat kya jaisey Abu-Usama ne kaha ."
4971,"Hazrat Sufiyan bin Usaid Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' bahut badi khayanat hai ke to apney bhai se koi baat karey, wo tumhen sacha samajh raha ho, jabkey tum us se jhoot bol rahey ho.''"
4972,"Janab abu-Qulaba se riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu-Adbullah ( Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu)) se ya abu-Adbullah ( Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke aapney us baarey mein kya suna hai jo log ( '' زعموا '' (ke andaz mein baat kartey hain? ( logon ka khayal hai. baawar kya jata hai. kaha jata hai waghera .) . unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ( '' زعموا '' ( aadmi ki bahut buri sawari hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : abu-Adbullah se murad Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) hain."
4973,Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen khutba diya aur farmaya : '' (amma baad ! ( ! ( hamd w salaat ke baad .'' (
4974,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs ( angoor ke liye ( lafz '' karam '' istimal na karey. beshak '' karam '' ( sakhaawat ka mantooq ( musalman aadmi hai. balke yun kaha karo ''angooron ke baaghaat.''"
4975,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs apney ghulam aur londi ko) Abdee ( ''merey bandey '' ''meri bandi '' ke lafz se hergiz na pukarey . aur na koi ghulam apney Malik ko (rabbi) aur) rabati ( ''merey rab '' kaheye . Malik ko chahiye ke yun pukarey ( فتاى ( ''aey merey jawan '' ( فتاتي ( ''aey meri ladki '' aur mamlook ko chahiye ke kahey ( سيدي , سيدتي ( ''aey merey sardar ! ''bila-shuba tum sab mamlook ho aur '' rab ''Allah azz-w-jall hi hai.''"
4976,abu-Yunus ( Suleman bin Jubair ( ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya aur us riwayat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr nahin kya. ( moquf riwayat bayan ki aur) سيدي وسيدتي ( ki bajaey kaha : (aur chahiye ke) سيدي (aur ( maulaai) ''aey merey sardar ! '' kahey.
4977,"Janab Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi munafiq ko '' saiyed '' ( sardar , aaqa ( keh kar mat pukaro . isliye ke agar wo sardar hua to tum ne apney rab azz-w-jall ko naraz kar diya .''"
4978,"Hazrat abu-Umama apney walid (Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs hergiz yun na kahey '' mera nafs khabees ho gaya hai.'' agar kehna bhi ho to yun kahey : ''meri tabiat pareshan hai. tabiat kharab hai.''"
4979,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs hergiz yun na kahey : mera ji josh maarta hai. balke yun kahey : mera ji pareshan hai.''"
4980,"Saiyedna Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' yun mat kaho : jo Allah chahey aur falan chahey , balke yun kaho : jo Allah chahey phir falan chahey .''"
4981,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik khateeb ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney khutba diya to usney kaha من يطع الله ورسوله فقد رشد ومن يعصهما '' jisney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat ki bila-shuba wo hidayat yafta hua aur jisney un dono ki nafarmani ki .'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chal khada ho.'' ya farmaya '' chala ja , to bahut bura khateeb hai.''"
4982,"Janab abu-Maleeh eik shakhs se riwayat kartey hain, usney kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sawari par unkey peechey betha hua tha ke aap ki sawari ko thokar si lagi to meri zaban se nikla '' halak ho shetan .'' to aapney farmaya : ''ye mat kaho , tum jab ye kehtey ho to wo phool jata hai yahan tak ke eik ghar ke barabar ho jata hai aur wo samajhta hai ke meri quwat se aisey hua , lekin kaho ( بسم الله ( ''Allah ke naam se'' tum jab aisey kehtey ho to wo sikud jata hai, yahan tak ke makkhi ki manind ho jata hai.''"
4983,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum suno . . . . aur bilfaaz Musa ( bin-Ismail ( jab kahey. . . . banda ke log tabah ho gaey . to kehney wala hi sab se ziyada tabah haal hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : jab koi logon ko deeni haalat mein kami aur kharabi ki wajeh se aisey kahey to main us mein koi harj nahin samajhta . lekin jab koi apney aap ko bada aur logon ko haqeer samajhtey huey aisey kahey to najaaiz hai aur usi ki manahi hai."
4984,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hergiz aisa na ho ke ye badwi log tumhari Namaz ke naam par ghalib aa jaeyn. khabrdar ! bila-shuba uska naam '' Isha '' hai. lekin chunkey wo log oontniyon ka doodh dohney mein andhera kar detey hain ( to usi munaasibat se usey utma, yani andherey wali Namaz keh detey hain.'' ("
4985,"Janab Salim bin Abu-Ja'ad se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne kaha . . . . Musaair ka khayal hai ke wo qabeela khuza'aa se tha. . . . kash mein Namaz padh leta to sukoon paata . to doosrey logon ne goya uskey us andaz par aeb lagaya . to usney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : '' Bilal ! Namaz ki iqaamat kaho , hamen us se rahat pahunchao .''"
4986,"Janab Abdullah bin Muhammad ibn hanfiya (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke main aur merey walid Ansariyon mein hamarey sasuraaliyon ke yahan iyaadat ke liye gaey to Namaz ka waqt ho gaya. to usney apney ghar walon mein se kisi ko kaha : aey ladki ! wuzu ke liye pani lao , shayad mein Namaz padh lun to rahat paun. to ham ne unka ye jumla pasand na kya. to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai, aap farmatey they ''aey Bilal! utho hamen Namaz ke sath rahat pahunchao.''"
4987,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap her eik cheez mein deen hi ki nisbat ka khayal farmatey they."
4988,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Madiney mein koi afawaah phel gaee ( shayad koi dushman hamla aawar honey wala hai) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghodey par Sawar huey (aur idhar-udhar dekh bhaal kar aaye (aur farmaya : '' ham ne kuch nahin dekha hai.'' ya farmaya : '' ham ne khof ki koi baat nahin dekhi . aur ye ghoda to goya samandar hai.''
4989,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jhoot se bacho . bila-shuba jhoot gunah ki taraf ley jata hai aur gunah jahannam mein pehchaney wala hai. bila-shuba jo insan jhoot bolta ho aur jhoot hi ke dar pai rehta hai to wo bil-aakhir Allah ke yahan kazzaab ( intehai jhoota ( likh diya jata hai. ( hamesha ( sach apnao , sach ( insan ko) neki ki rehnumai karta hai aur neki jannat mein pahunchati hai. aur jo shakhs sach boltaa aur sach ke dar pe rehta hai to wo bil-aakhir Allah ke yahan Siddiq ( intehai sacha ( likh diya jata hai.''"
4990,"Janab Behaz bin Hakim (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke mujhey merey walid ( hakim ( ne apney walid ( Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qusheiri (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kya. kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna , aap farmatey they : '' halakat hai uskey liye jo is gharz se jhoot boley ke us se log hansein . halakat hai uskey liye ! halakat hai uskey liye ! ''"
4991,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke eik din meri walida ne mujhey bulaya . idhar aao , chiz dungi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey ghar mein tashrif farma they. aapney meri walida se daryaft farmaya : ''tum usey kya dena chahti ho?'' unhoney bataya ke main usey khajoor dena chahti hun. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se kaha : ''agar tum usey kuch na detin to tum par eik jhoot likh diya jata .''"
4992,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi aadmi ke gunah gaar honey ke liye yehi baat kafi hai ke wo her suni sunai baat bayan karta rahey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hafs bin umr ki riwayat mein Abu-Huraira ka zikr nahin ( riwayat mursal hai) . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : aur usey sirf Ali bin Hafs madaaini ne musnad riwayat kya hai."
4993,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur baqaul nasar (bin Ali ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' achcha guman rakhna husne-ibadat mein se hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : sanad mein mazkur Muhanna (bin Abu-Shibl ( qabile-bharosa hai aur Basri hai.
4994,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf mein they aur main raat ke waqt aap ki ziyaarat ke liye hazir hui. mein aap se baaten karti rahi , phir uth kar wapis janey lagi to aap bhi merey sath uthey taake mujhey wapis pahuncha ayen aur meri rihaaish Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke ehatey mein thi. to Ansariyon ke do aadmi guzrey. unhoney jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to zara tezi se chalney lagey. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' thehar jao ! ye ( merey sath ( Safiya binte-Huyi hai. un dono ne kaha : Subhanallah ( Allah paak hai) aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba shetan insan ke jism mein aisey gardish karta hai jaisey khoon . mujhey andesha hua ke kahin wo tumharey dilon mein kuch dal na dey .'' ya farmaya : '' koi buri baat na dal dey .''"
4995,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' banda jab apney bhai se koi wada kar ley aur uski niyat ye ho ke wo apna wada wafa kerega magar na kar sakey aur wadey par na pahunch saka ho to us par koi gunah nahin.''"
4996,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu-Hamsa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke maboos honey se pehley ki baat hai ke maine aap se eik soda kya aur kuch qeemat baqi reh gaee, to maine aap se wada kar liya ke main yahin aap ke paas ley aata hun. magar mujhey apni ye baat teen din baad yaad aai, phir main aaya to aap wahin they. aapney farmaya : ''aey jawan! to ne mujhey bahut aziyat pahunchai hai. main teen din se yahan intizar kar raha hun. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Muhammad bin Yahya ne kaha : (sanad mein mazkur) abdul-kareem, ye ibn Abdullah bin Shaqiq hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : b-waasta Ali bin Abdullah mujhey ye riwayat usi tarah pahunchi hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Bishr bin sari ne usey (عن عبد الكريم بن Abdullah بن شقيق) ki sanad se riwayat kya hai."
4997,"Hazrat Asma bint Saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri eik saukan hai, agar main uskey samney aisey zahir karun ke ye chiz mujhey merey shohar ne di hai, halanke di na ho to kya mujh par gunah hoga? aapney farmaya : ''jo koi aisey zahir karey ke ye chiz meri hai, halanke usey na di gaee ho to uski misal us shakhs ki si hai jo makar ke do kapdey pehney ho.''"
4998,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey koi sawari inayat farmaeyn . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham tujhey oontni ka bacha dey detey hain.'' wo bola : main oontni ke bachey ka kya karunga ? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''oont ko bhi to oontni hi jahannam deti hai.''
4999,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan andar aaney ki ijazat chahi, to unhoney Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki aawaz suni jo qadrey buland thi. jab wo andar aaye to unhoney usey tamaancha maarney ke liye pakda. aur boley : main tumhen dekhta hun ke tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney apni aawaz buland karti ho. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey bachaney lagey aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ghussey se bahir nikal aaye. jab abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) chaley gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dekha ! maine tujhey us aadmi se kaisey bachaya?'' Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne chand din twaqquf kya aur phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ( milney ke liye ( ijazat chahi aur unhen paya ke unki suleh ho chuki hai, to un se kaha : mujhey bhi apni suleh mein shamil kar lo jaisey tum ne mujhey apni ladaai mein shamil kya tha. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham ne kar liya , ham ne kar liya .''"
5000,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ghazwa tabuk ke safar mein , main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua . aap chamdey ke eik khemey mein thehrey huey they. maine salam kaha, to aapney jawab diya aur farmaya : '' andar aa jao.'' maine arz kya. kya main sara hi aa jaun, aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : '' sara hi aa jao.'' aur main andar hazir ho gaya."
5001,Usman bin abu-Atika ne bayan kya ke) mazkura baala qissey mein) Auf bin Malik ne jo kaha : ''main sara hi andar aa jaun .'' ye us wajeh se tha ke wo khema chhota sa tha.
5002,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke) eik baar ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey yun pukara ''aey do kanon waley ! ''
5003,"Janab Abdullah bin Saaib bin Yazid apney walid se wo dada se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''tum mein se koi shakhs apney bhai ki koi chiz hergiz na ley , na hansi mazaq mein aur na haqeeqat mein sachchey taur per .'' Suleman (bin Abdur-Rehman (ke lafz they (لعبا ولا جدا) '' aur jisney apney bhai se ( koi ( lathi ( bhi) li ho to usey wapis kar dey.'' Muhammad bin Bashaar ne ( Abdullah bin Saaib ke nasab mein) '' ibne-Yazid '' nahin kaha. aur (سمع النبي ﷺ يقول) ki bajaey ) (قال رسول الله ﷺ) kaha ."
5004,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Laila riwayat kartey hain ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne hamen bayan kya ke wo log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar mein ja rahey they, to un mein se eik aadmi so gaya aur doosra us se eik rassi leney laga jo uskey paas thi, to wo dar gaya, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi musalman ke liye halal nahin ke doosrey musalman ko daraaey.''"
5005,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tehqiq Allah azz-w-jall aisey aadmi se ghussay hota hai jo ( nahaq ( zaban aawar ho ( bahut baaten banaey ( apni zaban ko aisey chalaey jaisey gaey chalaati hai.'' (aur lapet lapet kar ghaas khati hai. ("
5006,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney guftgu ka her pher ( baaten bananey ka dhang ( isliye seekha ke wo uskey zariey se logon ke dil moh ley , tu Allah azz-w-jall qiyamat ke roz uska koi nafl aur farz qubul nahin kerega .''"
5007,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke mashriq ki janib se do aadmi aaye aur unhoney khitab kya to logon ko unke aslamiya khitab w bayan par bada tajjub hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba baaz bayan jadu hotey hain.''
5008,"Janab Abu-Zabiya (Kulai Himsi) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik din eik aadmi ne khitab kya aur bahut baaten kin. to Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar ye apni guftgu mein miyaana rawi ikhtiyar karta to uskey liye bahut behtar hota . maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''yaqeenan maine samjha hai ya ( farmaya ke) mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke guftgu mein beech ka rasta ikhtiyar karun. bila-shuba beech ka rasta sarasar khair hai.''"
5009,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi ka pet peep se bhar jaey ye uskey liye behtar hai ke she'ron se bharey. Janab abu-Ali (Lulu) (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is irshad ki wazahat mein Janab abu-Ubaid ka ye qol hamen pahuncha hai ke is se murad ye hai ke koi shakhs she'r w shaeyri mein is qadr munhamik ho jaey ke Quran karim aur Allah ke zikr hi se ghafil ho jaey (to intehai mazmoom hai. ( lekin Quran karim aur mashghalae-ilm ghalib rahey to aisa aadmi hamarey khayal mein uska misdaaq nahin banta ke uska pet she'ron se bhara ho. (aur ye hadees ke) ''bila-shuba kaee bayan jadu hotey hain.'' uska mafhoom ye hai ke koi insan kisi ki madah saraai pe aaye to is umdagi se karey ke logon ke dil uski taraf maael ho jaeyn aur phir jab uski mazammat kerney lagey to is andaz se karey ke log uski us dusri baat ke peechey lag jaeyn . goya ke usney sunneywalon ko apni baat ka jaadu kar diya ho."
5010,Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba kaee she'r hikmat bharey hotey hain.''
5011,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik badwi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur apney makhsus andaz mein baaten kerney laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba kaee bayan jadu hotey hain aur bila-shuba kaee sher hikmat hotey hain.''
5012,"Hazrat Sakhr bin Abdullah bin Barida ne apney walid se unhoney dada se riwayat kya, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''bila-shuba baaz bayan jadu hotey hain aur kaee ilm jihalat. beshak kaee she'r hikmat hotey hain aur baaz aqwal mehaz bojh.'' is par Sasaa bin Sauhaan ne kaha : sach farmaya Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne . aap ka ye farman : '' baaz bayan jadu hotey hain.'' iski wazahat ye hai ke kabhi-kabhi aadmi ke zimmey koi haq hota hai) ke wo haqdaar ko ada karey ( magar wo haqdaar ke muqabley mein charb zaban hota hai to logon ko apney bayan se jadu kar deta hai aur haq maar leta hai. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman : '' baaz ilm jihalat hotey hain.'' yun hai ke kabhi-kabhi koi sahibe-ilm un umur (baton) mein jin ki usey koi khabar nahin hoti takalluf se baat karta hai to jihalat ka irtikab karta hai. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye qol : '' kaee she'r hikmat hotey hain.'' to us se murad wo ashaar hain jin mein waaz w nasihat aur umda misalen zikr hoti hain jin se log nasihat paatey hain. aur aap ka ye kehna : '' kaee aqwal mehaz bojh hotey hain.'' yun hai ke aap apni baat aisey shakhs ke samney pesh kerney lagen jo uskey zoq aur mizaj ke mutabiq na ho aur na wo uska khaahishmand ho."
5013,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) , Hazrat Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey, jabkey wo masjid ( nabwi ( mein she'r padh rahey they, to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen tez nazron se dekha to unhoney jawab diya. bila-shuba main is (masjid) mein she'r padha karta tha aur is mein wo azeem hasti mojud hoti thi jo aap se kahin ziyada afzal thi."
5014,Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya. us mein mazeed hai : phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khayal hua ke ye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ijazat pesh kar dengey. chunanche unhoney unko ijazat de-di (ke wo masjid mein she'r padh saktey hain.)
5015,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Hassaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye masjide-nabawi mein member rakhwa diya kartey they. pas wo us par khadey ho kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mazammat kerney walon ki mazammat kya kartey they, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Hassaan jab tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se difaa karen, roohul-qudus ( Jibrael ameen ( uskey sath hain.''"
5016,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne aayat karima ( والشعراء يتبعهم الغاون ( '' shaairon ki perwi gumrah log kartey hain.'' ki tafseer mein farmaya ke uskey umoom ko mansookh karkey as-haabe-emaan ko alehda kar diya gaya hai aur farmaya hai) إلا الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات وذكروا الله كثيرا ( '' magar wo log jo emaan laye nek amal kiye aur Allah ka bahut zikr kya.''
5017,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Fajr ki Namaz se farigh hotey to daryaft farmaya kartey : ''kya aaj raat tum mein se kisi ne koi khuwab dekha hai? '' aur farmaya kartey they : '' beshak merey baad nabuwat ka koi hissey baqi nahin. siwaye iskey ke kisi ko koi nek khuwab aa jaey.''
5018,Saiyedna Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin ka khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaliswan hissey hai.''
5019,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab zamana qarib aa jaeyga , to musalman ka khuwab ghaaliban jhoota nahin hoga , aur sab se sacha khuwab usi ka hoga jo baat cheet mein sab se ziyada sacha hoga. khuwab teen tarah ke hotey hain : achcha khuwab Allah azz-w-jall ki janib se bashaarat hoti hai, aur eik khuwab shetan ki taraf se ghamgin kerney wala hota hai, aur eik khuwab bandey ke apney auhaam w khayalat hotey hain. to jab koi khuwab mein koi naa-pasandida chiz dekhay to chahiye ke uth khada ho, Namaz padhey aur logon se bayan na karey '' aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main khuwab mein paon mein bediyan dekhna pasand karta hun jabkey galey mein toq dekhna bura janta hun. paon mein bediyan dekhna deen mein Sabit qadmi ki alamat hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : '' zamana qarib aa janey '' ka mafhoom ye hai ke jab din aur raat barabar barabar ho jaeyn ( mausam bahar ho. ("
5020,"Hazrat Abu-Razeen ( Laqeet bin Sabra aqeeli) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khuwab ( goya ( perindey ke paon par hai jab tak ke uski tabeer na bayan kar di jaey. chunanche jab tabeer bayan kar di jati hai to ( wo usi tarah (ho jati hai.'' aur mera khayal hai ke aapney farmaya : ''usey apney kisi mohabbat kerney waley ( mukhlis (ya sahibe-ilm ke ilawa kisi se hergiz bayan na karo.''"
5021,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : '' achcha khuwab Allah azz-w-jall ki taraf se aur bura khuwab shetan ki taraf se hota hai. chunanche jab koi shakhs koi napasand chiz dekhay to chahiye ke apney baain janib teen baar thookey , phir uskey shar se Allah ki panah maangey . bila-shuba wo ( khuwab ( usey zarar nahin pahunchaega .''"
5022,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi aisa khuwab dekhay jo usey bura lagey to usey chahiye ke apni baain janib thook dey . aur teen baar , shetan ke shar se Allah ki panah talab karey, aur apni karwat badal ley.''"
5023,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' jisney mujhey khuwab mein dekha wo an-qareeb mujhey jaagtey mein bhi dekhega , ya farmaya ke usney goya mujhey jaagtey mein dekha . aur shetan meri soorat ikhtiyar nahin kar sakta. ''"
5024,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney koi tasweer banai tu Allah usey uski wajeh se qiyamat mein azab dega , yahan tak ke us mein rooh phoonkey , magar wo nahin phunk sakega aur jisney jhootey taur par ye daawa kya ke usney ye khuwab dekha hai to usey is baat ka mukallaf kya jaeyga ke jo ke daney mein gireh baandhey ( jo ke na-mumkin hai) aur jisney kisi qom ki baat sunney ki koshish ki jabkey wo apni baat kerney ke liye us se door ho rahey hon to qiyamat ke din uskey kaan mein seesa dala jaeyga.''"
5025,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine aaj raat dekha goya ham Aqba bin Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein hain aur hamen ( Madina ki maroof umda ( taza khajoor ibn taab ki pesh ki gaee hai. to maine uski ye tabeer ki hai ke hamen duniya mein rifat w sarbulandi hasil hogi aur aakhirat mein anjam umda hoga aur hamara deen bhi khoob ( phal phool gaya ( hai.''"
5026,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko jamaai aaye to chahiye ke wo apna munh band rakhey , bila-shuba (us mein) shetan dakhil ho jata hai.''"
5027,Janab Suhel (Rahimahullah) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind marwi (bayan) hai. ( magar us mein hai : ( '' jamaai agar Namaz mein aaye to jahan tak ho sakey munh band rakhney ki koshish karey.''
5028,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala chheenk ko pasand aur jamaai ko napasand karta hai. chunanche jab kisi ko jamaai aaye to jahan tak ho sakey usey rokey aur ہاء ہاء ki aawaz na nikaley . bila-shuba ye shetan ki taraf se hoti hai aur wo us se hanstaa hai.''"
5029,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab chheenk aati to aap apney munh par apna haath ya koi kapda rakh letey aur apni aawaz ko kam rakhtey . Yahya ko shak hai ke riwayat mein lafz ( khafz ( tha ya ( غض ( ) maani eik hi hain. (
5030,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik musalman par doosrey musalman bhai ke liye paanch baaten wajib hain. salam ka jawab dena , chheenk aaney par dua dena , dawat qubul karna , bimar pursii karna aur janaazey mein shareek hona .''"
5031,"Janab Hilal bin Yusaf kehtey hain : ham log Hazrat Salim bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan bethey they ke majlis mein se kisi ko chheenk aai to usney kaha '' ( Assalamualaikum ( '' ( tum par salamti ho ( to Hazrat Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum par aur tumhari maa par bhi . phir uskey baad farmaya : shayad tumhen meri baat nagawar guzri hai? usney kaha : aap meri maa ka kisi taur . . . . khair ya shar ke sath . . . . zikr na kartey to achcha tha. unhoney kaha : maine tum se wohi baat kahi hai jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kahi thi. ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bethey huey they ke qom mein se kisi ko chheenk aa gaee to usney kaha '' ( Assalamualaikum ( '' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jawab diya : ''tum par aur tumhari maa par bhi .'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko chheenk aaye to chahiye ke) الحمد الله ( '' sab tareefen Allah ke liye hain, kahey. raawi ne kaha ke unhoney kuch aur Hamdon ka zikr bhi kya. aur jo doosra uskey paas ho, usey chahiye ke yun kahey ( يرحمك الله ( ''Allah tum par rehem farmaai '' aur phir chheenk maarney wala un logon ko jawab dey ( يغفر الله لنا ولكم ( ''Allah taala hamen aur tumhen ( sab ko) maaf farma dey .''"
5032,Khalid bin Arfata ne Hazrat Salim bin Ubaid Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye (mazkura baala ( riwayat bayan ki .
5033,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko chheenk aaye to chahiye ke kahiye (الحمد لله على كل حال)'' her haal mein Allah ki tareef hai.'' aur uskey bhai ya sathi ko chahiye ke kahey ( يرحمك الله ( ''Allah tum par rehem farmaai '' aur phir wo jisey chheenk aai ho kahey ( يهديكم الله ويصلح بالكم ( ''Allah tumhen hidayat dey aur tumharey ahwaal durust kar dey .''"
5034,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : apney bhai ko uski chheenk aaney par teen baar jawab dey aur jo us se ziyada ho, to phir wo zukaam zada hai."
5035,"Janab Saeed bin abi Saeed ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya aur kaha ke mujhey yehi maloom hai ke unhoney is hadees ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf nisbat kya aur mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : usko abu-Nuem ne Musa bin Qais ke wastey se Muhammad bin Ajlan sey, unhoney Saeed se unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya."
5036,"Humeda ya Ubeda bint Ubed bin Rifaa Zarqi apney walid se bayan karti hain, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya, aapney farmaya : '' chheenk maarney waley ko teen baar jawab do . phir agar jawab dena chaho, to do aur agar chaho to, chhod do.''"
5037,"Janab Ayas bin Salma bin Akwa se riwayat hai wo apney walid se naqal kartey hain ke eik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein chheenk maari, to aapney usey dua di aur farmaya ( يرحمك الله ( ''Allah tujh par rehem farmaai .'' usney phir chheenk maari to aapney farmaya : ''usey zukaam hai.''"
5038,Hazrat abu-Barda apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke yahudi log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein jan-bujhkar chhenkein maara kartey they aur tawaqqo kartey they ke aap unhen dua detey huey ( يرحمكم الله ( ''Allah tum par rehem farmaai '' kahengey . magar aap unhen yun jawab detey ( يهديكم الله ويصلح بالكم ( ''Allah tumhen hidayat dey aur tumharey ahwaal ki islah farmaai .''
5039,"Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein do aadmiyon ko chheenk aai to aapney eik ko jawab diya aur doosrey ko na diya. to aap se kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! do aadmiyon ne chheenk maari , magar aapney eik ko jawab diya hai. . . Ahmed (bin Yunus ( ne wazahat ki ke yahan lafz ( فشمت أحدهما ( they ya ( فسمت أحدهما ( . . . . aur doosrey ko chhod diya hai? to aapney farmaya : '' usney ( jis ko maine jawab diya hai) Allah ki hamd ki hai aur usney Allah ki hamd nahin ki .''"
5040,"Hazrat Yaesh bin Tikhfa bin Qais ghifaarii ka bayan hai ke merey walid ( Tikhfa (Raziallahu anhu)) as-haabe-Suffa mein se they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : '' hamarey sath Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar chalo.'' to ham chal diye .) wahan pahunch kar) aapney farmaya : '' Aaisha ! hamen ( kuch ( khilao.'' to wo jasheesha ley aain jo ham ne khaya. (jasheesha is andaz ka khana hai ke gehun ko pees kar aataa handiya mein chadhaaein phir us mein gosht ya khajoor dal kar pakaein. isey eik tarah ka halim bhi kaha ja sakta hai.) phir aapney farmaya : '' Aaisha ! hamen kuch aur bhi khilao.'' to wo hees. (khajoor, ghi aur paneer waghera ka murakkab khana) ley ayen jo thoda sa tha, jaisey ke chidiya ho (ya mumkin hai ke Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) murad hun ke wo sachchai aur wafa daari mein qatat chidiyaa ki manind thin .) ham ne wo hees khaya . phir aapney farmaya : '' Aaisha ! hamen kuch pilao .'' to wo doodh ka eik bada piyala ley aain. ham ne wo pi liya. aapney phir farmaya : ''Aaisha! hamen aur bhi pilao.'' to wo eik chhota piyala ley aain, to ham ne wo bhi piya. phir aapney farmaya : ''agar chaho to so jao aur agar chaho to masjid mein chaley jao.''Tikhfa kehtey hain : main masjid mein ondhey munh apney pet ke bal leta hua tha ke merey phephdey mein takleef thi. to achcha maine paya ke kisi ne mujhey apney paon se harkat di hai aur keh raha hai.'' is tarah se sona Allah taala ko napasand hai.'' kehtey hain : maine dekha to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) they."
5041,"Janab Abdur-Rehman apney walid Ali bin Sheban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi aisi chhat par soey jiskey gird koi munder (parda waghera) na ho to us se zimma uth gaya.''"
5042,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs baa-wuzu ho kar Allah ka zikr kartey huey so jaey aur phir raat ko kisi waqt uski aankh khulay (aur bistar par apna pehlu waghera badley (aur Allah se duniya w aakhirat ki koi khair mang ley , to wo usey inayat farma dega . Sabit Bunani kehtey hain raawi hadees Abu-Zabiya hamarey yahan aaye aur unhoney hamen ye hadees b-waasta Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) . . . . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan ki . Sabit (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke eik sahab ne kaha : maine badi koshish ki hai ke raat ko uthun aur aisi koi dua kar lun magar main us mein kamiyab nahin ho saka."
5043,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko uthey qazaey-hajat ke liye gaey. phir apna chehra aur haath dhoey phir so gaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (qaza haajat) se murad hai peshab kya.
5044,Janab abu-Qulaba ne Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke khandan mein se kisi fard se riwayat kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka bistar aisey bichaya jata tha jaisey insan qabr mein rakha jata hai aur masjid aap ke sar ki taraf hoti thi.
5045,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sona chahtey to apna daayan haath apney rukhsaar ke nichey rakh letey , phir ye dua padhtey ( اللهم قني عذابك يوم تبعث عبادك ( ''aey Allah ! jis din to apney bandon ko uthaey mujhey apney azab se mehfooz rakhna .'' ye kalmaat teen baar dohraatey ."
5046,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''jab apney bistar par janey lago to wuzu kar liya karo jaisey Namaz ke liye kartey ho, phir apni daain karwat par let jao aur kaho : (اللهم أسلمت وجهي إليك وفوضت أمري إليك وألجأت ظهري إليك رهبة ورغبة إليك لا ملجأ ولا منجا منك إلا إليك آمنت بكتابك الذي أنزلت ونبيك الذي أرسلت)''aey Allah ! maine apna chehra terey tabey kar diya aur apna maamla terey sipurd kar diya, apni kamar teri taraf laga li (tujhey hi apna sahara bana liya ( mujhey tera hi dar hai aur shoq bhi teri taraf hai. tujh se bhag karkey merey liye terey siwa kahin koi jaey-panah aur najat ki jagah nahin. main teri is kitab par emaan laya jo to ne nazil ki hai aur us Nabi ko tasleem kya jisey to ne Rasool bana kar bheja hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to (is raat mein) mar gaya to fitrat (deen Islam) par marega. aur chahiye ke ye teri aakhiri baat ho (uskey baad koi aur guftgu na ho.'') Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : maine is dua ko yaad kartey huey dohraya to lafz keh diye ( وبرسولك الذي أرسلت ( ''main terey is Rasool par emaan laya jisey to ne bheja hai.'' to aapney farmaya : '' nahin ( balke jo alfaz maine tumhen padhaaey hain wohi yaad karo, aur wo alfaz hain ( ) ونبيك الذي أرسلت ( ''main terey us Nabi par emaan laya jisey to ne Rasool bana kar bheja hai.''"
5047,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh farmaya : ''jab tum apney bistar par aaney lago aur baa-wuzu ho to apni daahini janib par leto . . .'' phir mazkura baala hadees ki manind zikr kya."
5048,Hazrat Bara (bin Aazib) (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi hadees riwayat ki. Sufiyan ne (apney asaatza Aamash aur Mansoor ke mutalliq) kaha ke un mein se eik ke alfaz ye they : ''jab tum baa-wuzu ho kar apney bistar par aao.'' aur doosrey ne kaha : ''jab tum apney bistar par aaney ka irada karo to wuzu kar lo jaisey Namaz ke liye kartey ho.'' aur Motamir (ki pichhli riwayat : 5046) ke ham-maani bayan ki .
5049,Saiyedna Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab soney lagtey to ye dua padhtey they : ( اللهم باسمك أحيا وأموت ( ''aey Allah ! terey hi naam se main zinda hota aur marta hun. yani sota aur jaagta hun.'' aur jab jaagtey to ye padhtey : (الحمد لله الذي أحيانا بعد ما أماتنا وإليه النشور) '' tamam tareefen us Allah ki hain jisney hamen maarney ke baad zinda kya ( neend ke baad jagaya (aur usi ki taraf uthna hai.''
5050,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney bistar par aaney lagey to chahiye ke apney bistar ko apni chadar ke pallu se jhaad ley , kya khabar uskey baad us par koi chiz aa gaee ho, phir apni daain karwat par let jaey aur ye dua padhey : (باسمك ربي وضعت جنبي وبك أرفعه إن أمسكت نفسي فارحمها وإن أرسلتها فاحفظها بما تحفظ به الصالحين من عبادك) ''terey hi naam se aey merey rab ! maine apna pehlu rakha hai aur terey hi naam se usey uthaaunga. agar to meri jaan ko rok ley (maut de-de) to us par rehem farma aur agar chhod dey to uski hifazat farma jis tarah to apney nek bandon ki hifazat farmata hai.''"
5051,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab apney bistar par aatey, ye dua padhtey they : اللهم ! رب السموات ورب الأرض ورب كل شىء فالق الحب والنوى منزل التوراة والإنجيل والقرآن أعوذ بك من شر كل ذي شر أنت آخذ بنا صيته أنت الأول فليس قبلك شىء وأنت الآخر فليس بعدك شىء وأنت الظاهر فليس فوقك شىء وأنت الباطن فليس دونك شىء) Wahab (bin baqiya ( ki riwayat mein mazeed hai : (اقض عني الدين وأغنني من الفقر) ''aey Allah ! aey aasmano ke rab ! aey zameen ke rab ! aur her cheez ke rab ! aey daney aur guthli ko phaad kar uganey waley ! aey Torah , injeel aur Quran ko nazil kerney waley ! main her shar wali chiz sey, jinki peshani to hi pakdey huey hai, teri panah chahta hun. to sab se pehley hai, tujh se pehley kuch na tha. to sab se aakhir hai terey baad kuch na hoga. to hi zahir hai tujh se ziyada zahir koi nahin. to hi poshida hai tujh se poshida tar koi nahin. mera qarz ada farma dey aur mujhey ( logon ki) mohtaji se be parwa kar dey .''"
5052,Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sotey waqt ye kalmaat kaha kartey they (اللهم ! إني أعوذ بوجهك الكريم وكلماتك التامة من شر ما أنت آخذ بناصيته ‘ اللهم ! أنت تكشف المغرم والمأثم ‘ اللهم ! لا يهزم جندك ولا يخلف وعدك ولا ينفع ذا الجد منك الجد سبحانك وبحمدك) ''aey Allah ! main terey buzurgi waley chehrey ki panah mein aata hun aur terey kamil kalmaat ki panah leta hun her us chiz ke shar se jiski peshani to pakdey huey hai. ya Allah ! to hi qarz aur gunah door kar sakta hai. ya Allah ! terey lashkar ko paspa nahin kya ja sakta. tera wada khilaf nahin hota aur terey yahan kisi maaldaar ko uska maal (ya khandani sharf waley ko uska sharf) koi faeyda nahin dey sakta. to her aeb se paak aur tamam tareefon wala hai.''
5053,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney bistar par aatey to ye dua padhtey they : (الحمد لله الذي أطعمنا وسقانا وكفانا وآوانا فكم ممن لا كافي له ولا مئوي) '' tamam tareefen us Allah ki hain jisney hamen khilaya , pilaya , dukhon takleefon se hamari hifazat farmaai aur hamen rehney ki jagah inayat farmaai, kitni hi makhluq hai ke koi unki kifaayat kerney wala nahin aur na koi unhen jagah deney wala hai.''"
5054,"Hazrat Abu-Azhar Anmari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko soney lagtey to ye dua padhtey : (بسم الله وضعت جنبي ‘ اللهم ! اغفر لي ذنبي وأخسا شيطاني وفك رهاني واجعلني في الندي الأعلى)''Allah ke naam se maine apna pehlu rakh diya. aey Allah ! merey gunah bakhsh dey , merey shetan ko dafa ( door) kar dey , merey nafs ko) aag sey) azad kar dey aur mujhey aalaa w afzal majlis walon mein bana dey .'' ( malaaika aur anbiya aur rasulon ka saathi bana dey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain. us riwayat ko Abu-Hamaam ahwaazi ( Muhammad bin Zabarqan ( ne Saur se naqal kya to ( Abu-Azhar ki bajaey ( abu-Zuhair Anmari kaha."
5055,Hazrat Farwa bin Nofal apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Nofal (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya tha : ( قل ya أيها الكافرون ( padho aur usi par apni baat cheet khatam karkey so jao. beshak us mein shirk se baraat ka izhar hai.''
5056,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her raat jab apney bistar par tashrif latey to apney dono haathon ko ikhatta karkey un mein (قل هو الله أحد * قل أعوذ برب الفلق) aur (قل أعوذ برب الناس) suraten padh kar dam kartey aur phunk maartey, phir unhen jahan tak ho sakta purey jism par phertey. pehley apney sar, chehrey aur agley hissey se ibtida (shuruat) kartey aur teen baar aisa kartey.''"
5057,Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) soney se pehley ( المسبحات ( ki tilawat farmaya kartey they aur aapney farmaya : '' un main eik aayat hai jo hazar aayat se afzal hai.''
5058,"Saiyedna ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne ibn Barida ko bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab apney bistar par aatey to ye dua padha kartey they (لحمد لله الذي كفاني وآواني وأطعمني وسقاني والذي من على فأفضل والذي أعطاني فأجزل الحمد لله على كل حال ‘ اللهم رب كل شىء ومليكۃ وإله كل شىء أعوذ بك من النار) ''tamam tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney ( her tarah sey) meri kifaayat ki aur mujhey rehney ki jagah inayat farmaai, mujhey khilaya, pilaya aur jisney mujh par ehsan kya aur bahut ziyada kya, jisney mujhey diya aur bahut khoob diya. her haal mein Allah hi ki tareef hai. aey Allah! aey her chiz ke parwardigar aur uskey malik! aey her chiz ke mabud! main aag se teri panah chahta hun.''"
5059,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kahin leta ho aur us mein Allah ka zikr na kya ho to qiyamat ke din usey hasrat w afsos hoga. aur jo shakhs kahin betha ho aur wahan Allah azz-w-jall ka zikr na kya ho to qiyamat ke din usey hasrat w afsos hoga.''
5060,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' raat ke waqt jiski aankh khul jaey aur wo jaagney par ye kalmaat kahey (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له ‘ له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شىء قدير سبحان الله والحمد لله ولا إله إلا الله والله أكبر ولا حول ولا قوة إلا بالله) phir dua karey (رب اغفر لي) . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Waleed ke alfaz hain : ''phir ( koi si) dua kar ley, to qubul hogi aur agar uth khada ho, wuzu karey aur Namaz padhey to uski Namaz maqbool hogi.''"
5061,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko jaagtey to ye dua padha kartey they :(لا إله إلا أنت سبحانك ‘ اللهم ! أستغفرك لذنبي وأسألك رحمتك ‘ اللهم ! زدني علما ولا تزغ قلبي بعد إذ هديتني وهب لي من لدنك رحمة إنك أنت الوهاب)'' terey siwa koi mabud nahin, to paak hai. aey Allah ! main tujhi se apney gunahon ki bakhshish chahta hun, aur teri rehmat ka sawali hun. aey Allah ! merey ilm mein izafa farma, aur hidayat dey deney ke baad merey dil ko gumrah na kar dena, (aey merey rab! ( mujhey apney paas se rehmat inayat farma, beshak to hi inayat kerney wala hai.''"
5062,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se chakki peesney ki wjah sey haathon mein takleef ka izhar kya. phir aap ke paas kuch ghulam aaye to Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aap ke paas ayain ke aap se koi khaadim talab karen, magar aap na miley, to unhoney Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko bataya . jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye, to unhoney aap se zikr kya (ke Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aai thin ( to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye jabkey ham apney bistaron mein ja chukey they. aap tashrif laye to ham uthney lagey . aapney farmaya : '' apni apni jagah par raho .'' aap aaye aur hamarey darmiyan beth gaey, yahan tak ke maine aap ke qadmon ki thandak apney seeney mein mehsoos ki. aapney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisi baat na bataun jo tumharey liye us chiz se bahut behtar ho jiska tum ne mutalba kya hai? jab tum bistar par letney lago to tentis baar (Subhanallah) tentis baar (al-hamdulillah) aur chauntees baar (Allahu-akbar) padh liya karo . ye tumharey liye khaadim se kahin behtar hai.''"
5063,"ameerul-momeneen Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibne-Aabud se kaha : main tumhen apni aur Fatima bint Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat na bataun . Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney ehel mein sab se badh kar mehboob thin aur wo meri zojiyat mein thin. chakki chalaati thin yahan tak ke unke haathon mein gattey pad gaey . mishkizey mein pani bhar kar laati thin, us se seeney par nishan pad gaey . ghar mein jhaado deti thin us se kapdey kharab ho jatey they. handiya ke nichey aag jalaatin to usse kapdey gandey ho jatey they aur us se unhen taklif bhi hoti thi. phir ham ne suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuch ghulam laye gaey hain. to maine kaha : agar tum apney abba ke paas jao aur un se kisi khaadim ka kaho jo tumharey kaam kar diya karey (to behtar rahey.) chunanche wo aap ke paas gaeen magar paya ke aap ke paas kuch baaten kerney waley bethey hain to unhen baat kerney mein haya aai, lihaza wo wapis lot aain. agli subh aap hamarey yahan tashrif laye jabkey ham lihaaf odhey huey they. chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke sar ke paas beth gaey to unhoney apney walid se haya ke baais apna sar lihaaf mein dey liya . aapney daryaft farmaya : '' kal tumhen aale-Muhammad ke yahan kya kaam tha ?'' to wo khamosh rahin. aapney do baar poochha. to maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main arz kiye deta hun. bila-shuba ye merey yahan ( ghar mein) chakki peesti hain yahan tak ke haathon mein gattey pad gaey hain, mashk utha kar pani bhar kar laatii hain yahan tak ke seeney par nishan pad gaey hain, ghar mein jhaado deti hain aur kapdey ghubar aalud ho jatey hain, handiya ke nichey aag jalaati hain yahan tak ke kapdey siyah ho jatey hain, aur hamen maloom hua hai ke aap ke paas ghulam ya khaadim aaye hain to maine un se kaha ke aap se kisi khaadim ka poochen . . . . aur) mazkura baala ( riwayat hukm ke ham-maani zikr kya aur wo ziyada kamil hai."
5064,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye khabar bayan ki. us mein hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se (ye tasbeehat wala amal) suna hai, unhen kabhi nahin chhoda. sirf Siffen ki raat ko ye mujhey raat ke aakhiri pehar yaad ayain, to maine unhen us waqt padha ."
5065,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do amal aisey hain agar koi musalman banda unki pabandi kar ley , to jannat mein dakhil hoga aur wo bahut aasan hain magar un par amal kerney waley bahut kam hain. ( eik ye hai ke) her Namaz ke baad das baar ( '' Subhanallah '' ( das baar ( '' الحمد الله '' (aur das baar ( '' الله اكبر '' ( kahey to zaban ki adaegi ke aetbar se eik so pachas baar hai) majmui taur par paanchon namazon ke baad (aur tarazu main eik hazar paanch so hongey aur jab soney lagey to chauntees baar ( '' الله اكبر '' ( tentis baar ( '' الحمد الله '' (aur tentis baar ( '' Subhanallah '' ( kahey. zabani taur par to ye eik so baar hai magar meezaan mein ye tasbeehaat eik hazar hongi .'' yaqinan maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap unhen apney haath se shumar kartey they. Sahaba ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye kaisey hai ke ye amal aasan hai magar kerney waley thodey hain? aapney farmaya : '' sotay waqt mein kisi ke paas shetan aa jata hai aur pehley us se ke wo ye tasbihat puri kar ley, wo usey sula deta hai aur (usi tarah) Namaz mein shetan aa jata hai aur usey koi kaam yaad dila deta hai to wo unhen padhey baghair hi uth jata hai.''"
5066,"Umme-Hakam ke sahibzadey ya Zaba bint Zuber se riwayat hai) Umme-Hakam aur Zaba dono Zuber bin Abdul-Muttalib ki betiyan hain ( kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuch qaidi aaye to main , meri behan aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin . ham ne unhen apni wo mushkilat pesh kin jin se ham do-chaar hoti thin, aur ham ne arz kya ke un qaidiyon mein se koi khaadim hamen bhi diye janey ka hukm irshad farmaeyn to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Badr ke yateem tum se pehley ley chukey hain. phir tasbih wala qissa zikr kya aur us riwayat mein her Namaz ke baad ka bayan hai, sotay waqt ka zikr nahin hai."
5067,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Saiyedna abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey koi kalmaat irshad farmaeyn jo main subh aur shaam ke waqt padha karun. aapney farmaya : ''ye padha karo : (اللهم ! فاطر السموات والأرض عالم الغيب والشهادة رب كل شىء ومليكه أشهد أن لا إله إلا أنت أعوذ بك من شر نفسي وشر الشيطان وشركه) ''aey Allah! aasmano aur zameen ke paida kerney waley ! poshida aur zahir ke janney waley ! her cheez ke paalney waley aur uskey Malik ! main gawahi deta hun ke terey siwa koi mabud nahin. mein apney nafs ki shararat , shetan ke shar aur uskey shirk se teri panah mein aata hun.'' ye dua subh , shaam aur sotay waqt padha karo.''"
5068,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , jab subh hoti to ye dua padhtey they : (اللهم ! بك أصبحنا وبك أمسينا وبك نحيا وبك نموت وإليك النشور ) ''aey Allah! ham ne terey (fazal ke) sath subh ki aur terey ( fazal ke) sath shaam kartey hain. terey hi fazal se zinda aur terey hi naam par martey hain aur teri hi taraf uth kar jana hai.'' aur shaam ke waqt ye kalmaat yun kehtey : ( اللهم ! بك أمسينا وبك نحيا وبك نموت وإليك النشور ( ''aey Allah ! ham ne terey hi ( fazal ke) sath shaam ki aur terey hi fazal se zinda aur terey hi naam par martey hain aur teri hi taraf uthna hai.''"
5069,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ya shaam ke waqt nichey likhi dua padh ley , tu Allah taala uska chothai hissey aag se azad farma dega . aur jo shakhs usey do baar padhey , Allah uska aadha hissey aag se azad kar dega . aur jo shakhs usey teen baar padhey , Allah taala uska teen chothai aag se azad kar dega . aur jo shakhs chaar baar padhey , tu Allah taala usey ( kamil taur par) aag se azad farma dega.'' (dua ke kalmaat ye hain : ) ( اللهم ! إني أصبحت أشهدك وأشهد حملة عرشك وملائكتك وجميع خلقك أنك أنت الله la إله إلا أنت وأن محمدا عبدك ورسولك ) ''aey Allah ! maine subh ki hai aur tujhey gawah banata hun aur tera arsh uthaney waley aur deegar farishton aur teri sari makhluq ko gawah banata hun ke to hi Allah hai, terey siwa koi mabud nahin. aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) terey bandey aur terey Rasool hain.''"
5070,"Hazrat Abdullah apney walid Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ya shaam ke waqt ye dua padh ley aur phir apney us din ya raat mein faut ho jaey to jannat mein dakhil hoga .'' ( alfaz ye hain : ) (اللھم ! انت ربی لا إله إلا أنت خلقتني وأنا عبدك وأنا على عهدك ووعدك ما استطعت أعوذ بك من شر ما صنعت أبوء لك بنعمتك وأبوء بذنبي فاغفر لي إنه لا يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت)''aey Allah ! to hi mera rab hai. terey siwa koi mabud nahin. to ney mujhey paida kya hai aur main tera banda hun, main terey sath kiye huey ehad aur wadey par , jahan tak meri himmat hai, qaaim hun. main apney kiye ke shar se teri panah chahta hun. teri nematon jo mujh par hain mujhey unka iqrar hai aur mujhey apney gunahon ka bhi aetraaf hai. pas mujhey bakhsh dey. beshak terey siwa koi gunahon ko nahin bakhshta.''"
5071,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shaam ke waqt ye kalmaat padha kartey they : (أمسينا وأمسى الملك لله والحمد لله لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له . ۔ ) Jarir ki riwayat mein izafa hai lekin Zubeda ne kaha ke Ibrahim bin Suwed kaha kartey they : ( لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له ‘ له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شىء قدير رب ! أسألك خير ما في هذه الليلة وخير ما بعدها وأعوذ بك من شر ما في هذه الليلة وشر ما بعدها ‘ رب ! أعوذ بك من الكسل ومن سوء الكبر أو الكفر ‘ رب ! أعوذ بك من عذاب في النار وعذاب في القبر)aur jab subh hoti to bhi usi tarah kaha kartey they : ( أصبحنا وأصبح الملك لله . . . .) . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : is riwayat ko Shoba ne b-waasta Salma bin Kuheil, Ibrahim bin Suwed se riwayat kya to us mein (من سوء الكبر) kaha hai aur ( سوء الكفر )  ka zikr nahin kya."
5072,"Janab abu-Salaam (Mamtur al-Habshi) hims ki masjid mein bethey huey they ke unke paas se eik shakhs guzra. logon ne bataya ke ye aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khaadim raha hai. to abu-Salaam uski taraf uth kar gaey aur kaha : mujhey aisi hadees bayan keejiye jo aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni ho aur wo sirf aap ko batai ho, aam logon se na kahi ho. to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farmatey they : ''jo shakhs subh ya shaam ko ye padh liya karey : (رضينا بالله ربا وبالإسلام دينا وبمحمد رسولا) ''ham is baat par razi hain ke Allah hamara rab, Islam hamara deen aur Muhammad hamarey Rasool hain.'' tu Allah par ye haq hoga ke wo usey razi kar dey.''"
5073,"Janab Abdullah bin Ghinaam al-Bayazi se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney subh ke waqt ye keh liya : ( اللهم ! ما أصبح بي من نعمة فمنك وحدك لا شريك لك فلك الحمد ولك الشكر) ''aey Allah ! mujhey jo bhi nemat hasil hai wo terey akeley hi ki taraf se hai. tera koi shareek nahin. pas teri hi hamd hai aur tera hi shukr hai.'' to usney apney us din ka shukr ada kar liya aur jisney shaam ke waqt usi tarah keh liya, to usney apni us raat ka shukr ada kar liya .''"
5074,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) farmaya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shaam ko aur subh ke waqt ye duayen na chhoda kartey they ( hamesha padha kartey they : ) (اللهم ! إني أسألك العافية في الدنيا والآخرة ‘ اللهم ! إني أسألك العفو والعافية في ديني ودنياى وأهلي ومالي ‘ اللهم ! استر عورتي . ۔) Usman (bin abi Sheba (ke alfaz hain : (عوراتي وآمن روعاتي ‘ اللهم ! احفظني من بين يدى ومن خلفي وعن يميني وعن شمالي ومن فوقي وأعوذ بعظمتك أن أغتال من تحتي) ''aey Allah ! main tujh se duniya aur aakhirat mein her tarah ke aaram aur rahat ka sawal karta hun. aey Allah ! main tujh se maafi aur aafiyat ka talabgaar hun apney deen w duniya mein aur apney ehel w maal mein. aey Allah! merey aeb chupa dey. mujhey merey andeshon aur khatraat se aman inayat farma. ya Allah! merey aagey, merey peechey, merey daeyn, merey baaeyn aur merey ooper se meri hifazat farma . aur main teri azmat ke zariey se is baat se panah chahta hun ke main apney nichey ki taraf se halak kar diya jaun. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya, Janab Wakee ne kaha ke (أغتال من تحتي) se murad hai : '' zameen mein dhansa diya jaun .'' (us se panah chahta hun. )"
5075,"abdul-Hameed maula bano Hashim se riwayat hai ke uski walida Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi sahibzadi ki khidmat kya karti thi. us sahibzadi ne usey bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey sikhaya kartey they aur farmatey they : ''jab tum subh karo to ye kaha karo : (سبحان الله وبحمده لا قوة إلا بالله ما شاء الله كان و ما لم يشأ لم يكن أعلم أن الله على كل شىء قدير وأن الله قد أحاط بكل شىء علما) ''Allah paak hai apni Hamdon ke sath . neki aur khair Allah taala ki tofiq ke baghair mumkin nahin. jo Allah chahta hai ho jata hai aur jo nahin chahta nahin hota . mujhey yaqeen hai ke Allah her chiz par puri qudrat rakhta hai aur uska ilm her cheez ko apney gherey mein liye huey hai.'' bila-shuba jo shakhs subh ke waqt ye kalmaat keh ley, to shaam tak uski hifazat ki jaeygi aur jisney shaam ko ye padh liye, to subh tak uski hifazat ki jaeygi.''"
5076,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ke waqt ( Sura Rome ki nichey likhi aayaat ( padh ley wo apney us din ki faut shuda nekiyan hasil kar lega aur jisney unhen shaam ke waqt padh liya wo apni us raat ki faut shuda nekiyan hasil kar lega .'' ( wo aayaat ye hain : ) ( فسبحان الله حين تمسون وحين تصبحون ، وله الحمد في السموات والأرض وعشيا وحين تظهرون ، يخرج الحي من الميت ويخرج الميت من الحي ويحيي الأرض بعد موتها وكذلك تخرجون )chunanche tum Allah ki tasbih ( paki bayan ( karo jab tum shaam karo aur jab subh karo aur usi ki tareef hai aasmano mein aur zameen mein aur) tasbih karo) pichley pahar aur jab tum do-pehar karo . wo nikalta hai zinda ko murda se aur murda ko zinda sey, aur zameen ko) bhi) uskey murda ( banjar (ho janey ke baad zinda ( shadab ( kar deta hai aur aisey hi tumhen bhi nikala jaeyga.'' Rabeea bin Suleman ki riwayat mein ((أخبرني الليث) ki bajaey (عن الليث) ke alfaz hain."
5077,"ibn Abu-Aaish se riwayat hai, jabkey Hammad ki riwayat mein hai ke abu-Ayash (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ke waqt ye keh ley (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له ‘ له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شىء قدير) '' eik akeley Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin. uska koi sajhi nahin, mulk usi ka hai, tareef usi ki hai aur wo her cheez par khoob qadir hai.'' to usey aulad Ismail mein se eik ghulam azad kerney ka sawab hoga. aur uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jaeyngi, us se das ghaltiyaan mitaai jaeyngi, uskey das darjaat buland kiye jaeyngey aur shaam tak ke liye shetan se hifazat mein rahega aur agar shaam ko ye keh ley , to subh tak ke liye yehi kuch hai. Hammad ki riwayat mein hai ke eik aadmi ne khuwab mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! abu-Ayash aap se us is tarah riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''abu-Ayash ne sach kaha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat ko Ismail bin Jaafar, Musa Zamai aur Abdullah bin Jaafar ne b-waasta suhail, uskey walid se aur usney ibne-Ayash se riwayat kya."
5078,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kya kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ke waqt ye keh ley (اللهم ! إني أصبحت أشهدك وأشهد حملة عرشك وملائكتك وجميع خلقك أنك أنت الله لا إله إلا أنت وحدك لا شريك لك وأن محمدا عبدك ورسولك) ''aey Allah ! maine subh ki, tujhey gawah banata hun aur terey arsh pakadey rehnewalon, doosrey farishton aur teri sari makhluq ko gawah banata hun ke beshak to hi Allah hai, terey eik akeley ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahin, tera koi sajhi nahin aur beshak Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) terey bandey aur terey Rasool hain.'' to wo us din mein jo gunah bhi kerega, Allah usey maaf kar dega . aur agar shaam ko ye keh ley to us raat mein jo gunah us se hon, maaf kar diye jaeyngey .''"
5079,"Muslim bin Haris Tamimi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey razdaari ke andaz mein farmaya : ''jab tum namaze-Maghrib se salam phero to saat baar (اللهم ! أجرني من النار) '' keh liya karo.'' aey Allah ! mujhey jahannam ki aag se mehfooz rakh.'' agar tum ye keh lo aur usi raat mar jao to tumharey liye jahannam se bachao likh diya jaeyga aur jab subh ki Namaz padh chuko to usi tarah keh liya karo, agar tum us din mein mar gaey, to tumharey liye jahannam se bachao likh diya jaeyga. abu-Saeed ne Haris se riwayat kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen ( bil-khusus ( razdaarana andaz mein farmaya tha, to ham ( bhi ye ( apney bhaiyon ko bil-khusus batatey hain."
5080,"Abdur-Rehman bin Hassaan kinaani ne riwayat kya ke mujhey Muslim bin Haris bin Muslim Tamimi ne apney walid se riwayat kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. . . . aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kya. aur) جوار منها ( tak riwayat ki . magar us mein hai ke ye kalma (اللهم أجرني من النار) ( salam ke baad) kisi se baat kerney se pehley kahey . Ali bin Sehal ne kaha ke Muslim bin Haris ke walid ne apney bete ko ye hadees bayan ki, jabkey Ali bin Sehal aur Muhammad bin musaffi ne riwayat kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen eik muhim mein rawana kya. jab ham ladaai ke maqam par pahunch gaey to maine apney ghodey ko tez daudaaya aur apney sathiyon se aagey nikal gaya to mujhey dushman qabiley ki aawazen sunai din. maine un se kaha : ( La-ilaah-illallah ( keh lo bach jaogey . chunanche un logon ne ye kalma keh diya. to merey sathiyon ne mujhey malamat ki aur kehney lagey ke tum ne hamen ghanimat se mehroom kar diya. phir jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas pahunchey aur sathiyon ne wo ( waqia ( bayan kya ke jo kuch maine kya tha. to aapney mujhey bulwaaya aur merey amal ki tahseen farmaai aur farmaya : ''Allah ne terey liye un mein se her her bandey ki wajeh se itna itna sawab likha hai. . .'' Abdur-Rehman (bin Hassaan) ne kaha ke mujhey is sawab ki tafsil bhula di gaee hai. . . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aagah raho ! beshak main apney baad tumharey liye wasiyat likh deta hun.'' chunanche aapney aisey hi kya aur us tehreer mein mohar laga kar merey hawaley kar di aur mujh se farmaya. . . . phir mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani zikr kya. ibne-Musaffi ne kaha : maine Haris bin Muslim bin Haris Tamimi se suna, wo apney walid se hadees bayan kartey they."
5081,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke jisney subh aur shaam ke waqt saat baar ye keh liya : (حسبي الله لا إله إلا هو عليه توكلت وهو رب العرش العظيم) Allah taala uski pareshaniyon mein uski kifaayat farmaeyga chahey usney sachey dil se ye kalma kaha ho ya jhootey dil se."
5082,"Janab Muaz bin Abdullah bin khubaib apney walid se riwayat kartey hain unhoney bayan kya ke ham eik barish wali aur sakht andheri raat mein nikley , jabke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dhoond rahey they taake wo hamen Namaz padhaein . chunanche ham ne aap ko pa liya , to aapney farmaya : '' kaho .'' to main kuch na bola . aapney phir farmaya : '' kaho '' to bhi mein kuch na bola . aapney phir farmaya : '' kaho .'' to maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main kya kahun . aapney farmaya : kaho : ( قل هو الله أحد (aur muawwizatain , yani Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas subh aur shaam teen teen baar ye keh lo , to her chiz se tumhari kifaayat ho jaeygi .''"
5083,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamen koi kalma irshad farmaeyn jo ham subh , shaam aur sotay waqt padha karen. to aapney farmaya , kaha karo : (اللهم ! فاطر السموات والأرض عالم الغيب والشهادة أنت رب كل شىء والملائكة يشهدون أنك لا إله إلا أنت فإنا نعوذ بك من شر أنفسنا ومن شر الشيطان الرجيم وشركه وأن نقترف سوءا على أنفسنا أو نجره إلى مسلم) ''aey Allah ! aasmano aur zameen ke paida kerney waley, ghaib aur hazir ke janney waley ! to hi her chiz ka Malik hai. aur farishtey gawah hain ke terey siwa koi mabud nahin. ham apney nafson ki shararaton se aur shetan mardud ke shar aur shirk se teri panah chahtey hain aur is baat se bhi ke ham apni jaanon par kisi burai ka irtikab keren ya kisi musalman ke liye koi burai keren.''"
5084,"Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne usi asnaad se riwayat kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi subh karey to chahiye ke kaha karey : (أصبحنا وأصبح الملك لله رب العالمين ‘ اللهم ! إني أسألك خير هذا اليوم فتحه ونصره ونوره وبركته وهداه وأعوذ بك من شر ما فيه وشر ما بعده) ''ham ne subh ki aur Allah rabbul-aalameen ke mulk ne bhi subh ki . aey Allah ! main tujh se us din ki khair, kamiyabi , madad , Noor , barkat aur hidayat ka sawal karta hun aur us shar se jo us mein hai aur uskey baad main teri panah chahta hun.'' aur jab shaam ho to usi tarah keh liya karey.''"
5085,Janab Shuraiq Hozani kehtey hain ke main ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaya aur un se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey to kis chiz se ibtida (shuruat) kartey they? unhoney kaha : tehqiq to ne mujh se aisa sawal kya hai jiskey mutalliq tujh se pehley mujh se kisi ne nahin poochha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey they to das baar ( الله اكبر ( das baar ( الحمد الله ( das baar (سبحان الله وبحمده) das baar (سبحان الملك القدوس) das baar ( استغفر الله ( das baar ( La-ilaah-illallah ( phir das baar kehtey (اللهم ! إني أعوذ بك من ضيق الدنيا وضيق يوم القيامة) ''aey Allah ! main duniya aur roze-qiyamat ki tangi se teri panah chahta hun.'' phir Namaz shuru farmatey .
5086,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar mein hotey aur sahar hoti to farmaya kartey (سمع سامع بحمد الله ونعمته وحسن بلائه علينا ‘ اللهم ! صاحبنا فأفضل علينا عائذا بالله من النار) '' sunta hai sunney wala, hamd hai Allah ki aur kya khoob nematon aur ehsan hain uskey ham par. aey Allah ! hamara sathi bin aur ham par apna fazal farma. is haal mein ke ham jahannam ki aag se Allah ki panah chahtey hain.''"
5087,Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke jisney subh ke waqt ye dua padhi : (اللهم ! حلفت من حلف أو قلت من قول أو نذرت من نذر فمشيئتك بين يدى ذلك كله ما شئت كان و ما لم تشأ لم يكن ‘ اللهم ! اغفر لي وتجاوز لي عنه ‘ اللهم فمن صليت عليه فعليه صلاتي ومن لعنت فعليه لعنتي) ''aey Allah ! maine jo koi qasam uthai ho ya koi baat kahi ho ya koi nazar maani ho to teri mashiyat aur irada us sab kuch ke aagey hai. jo to chahta hai ho jata hai aur jo to nahin chahta nahin hota . aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey aur mujh se un umur (baton) mein darguzar farma . aey Allah ! jis par to ne apni ( rehmat ( nazil ki hai to meri taraf se bhi uskey liye ( rehmat ( ho. aur jis par to ney lanat ki hai meri taraf se bhi usko phitkar ho.'' ye kalimat padhney wala us din ki ghaltiyon se mustasna hoga. (mehfooz rahega.)
5088,"Saiyedna Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' jisney ( shaam ko) teen baar ye dua padh li , usey subh tak koi achcha musibat nahin aaeygi (بسم الله الذي لا يضر مع اسمه شىء في الأرض ولا في السماء وهو السميع العليم) ''Allah ke naam se. . . . wo zaat ke uskey naam se koi chiz zameen mein ho ya aasman mein , nuqsan nahin dey sakti aur wo khoob sunta hai aur khoob janta hai.'' aur jisney subh ke waqt teen baar ye dua padh li usey shaam tak koi achcha musibat nahin aaeygi . raawi ne bayan kya ke is hadees ki riwayat kerney waley Aban bin Usman ko falij ho gaya tha to un se hadees sunney wala, unko tajjub se dekhney laga (ke phir ye falij kyonkar ho gaya?) to unhoney kaha : kya hua , mujhey dekhtey kya ho? Allah ki qasam ! maine Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) par jhoot nahin bola hai aur na Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jhoot bola hai. lekin jis din mujhey ye فالج hua mein us din ghussey mein tha aur ye kalmaat padhna bhool gaya tha."
5089,"Muhammad bin Kab ne Aban bin Usman sey, unhoney Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kya magar falij wala qissa zikr nahin kya."
5090,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Bakra se riwayat hai, unhoney apney walid se kaha : abba jaan ! main aap ko sunta hun ke aap her subh ye dua padhtey hain : (اللهم ! عافني في بدني ‘ اللهم ! عافني في سمعي ‘ اللهم ! عافني في بصري لا إله إلا أنت) ''aey Allah ! mujhey merey badan mein aaram dey. aey Allah ! merey kanon ko salaamat rakh, ya Allah! meri nazar ko durust rakh. terey siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahin.'' aap ye dua subh ko teen baar padhtey hain aur shaam hoti hai to teen baar padhtey hain. to unhoney kaha : bila-shuba maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye dua kartey suna hai. to main pasand karta hun ke aap ki sunnat par amal karun. ( doosrey raawi ( Abbas (bin Abdul-Azeem ( ne apni riwayat mein kaha : aur aap ye dua bhi padhtey hain : (اللهم ! إني أعوذ بك من الكفر والفقر ‘ اللهم ! إني أعوذ بك من عذاب القبر لا إله إلا أنت) ''aey Allah main kufr aur mohtaji se teri panah chahta hun. ya Allah ! main qabr ke azab se teri panah chahta hun. terey siwa koi mabud nahin .'' aap ye dua subh ko teen baar dohraatey hain aur shaam ko bhi padhtey hain. ( to unhoney kaha ( mein pasand karta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat par amal karun. aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pareshan haal ke liye ye dua hai : (اللهم ! رحمتك أرجو فلا تكلني إلى نفسي طرفة عين وأصلح لي شأني كله لا إله إلا أنت)''aey Allah ! main teri rehmat ka umeedwar hun, to mujhey aankh jhapakney tak ke liye bhi meri apni jaan ke hawaley na farma dey , aur merey sarey maamlat durust farma dey, terey siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahin.'' us riwayat mein Abbas bin Abdul-Azeem aur Muhammad bin Musanna ne baaz kalmaat eik doosrey se kuch ziyada kahey hain."
5091,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ke waqt so baar (سبحان الله العظيم وبحمده) keh ley aur usi tarah shaam ko bhi , to makhluqat mein koi aisa na hoga jisney is qadr sawab paya hoga .''"
5092,"Hazrat Qatada (Rahimahullah) ko ye riwayat pahunchi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab naya chaand dekhtey , to kehtey : (هلال خير ورشد هلال خير ورشد هلال خير ورشد آمنت بالذي خلقك) ''khair aur hidayat ka chaand , khair aur hidayat ka chaand , khair aur hidayat ka chaand , main emaan laya us zaat par jisney tujhey paida kiya.'' aap ye teen baar farmatey. uskey baad farmatey : (الحمد لله الذي ذهب بشهر كذا وجاء بشهر كذا) ''hamd us Allah ki jo falan mahiney ko ley gaya aur falan mahina ley aaya.''"
5093,"Hazrat Qatada (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab chaand dekhtey to apna chehra us se pher letey ( uskey baad dua padhtey ). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is masley mein koi marfoo sahih hadees Sabit nahin hai."
5094,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi merey ghar se nikaltey to apni nazar aasman ki taraf uthatey aur ye dua padhtey : (اللهم إني أعوذ بك أن أضل أو أضل أو أزل أو أزل أو أظلم أو أظلم أو أجهل أو يجهل على) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun, is baat se ke main gumrah ho jaun ya gumrah kar diya jaun , ya phisal jaun ya phislaa diya jaun , ya zulm karun ya koi mujh par zulm karey, ya koi jihalat ka kaam karun ya koi mujhse jihalat ka bartao karey.''"
5095,"Saiyedna Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda apney ghar se nikley aur ye kalimaat keh ley : (بسم الله توكلت على الله لا حول ولا قوة إلا بالله) ''Allah ke naam sey, main Shan Wale Allah par bharosa karta hun. kisi shar aur burai se bachna aur kisi neki ya khair ka hasil hona Allah ki madad ke baghair mumkin nahin.'' to us waqt usey ye kaha jata hai : tujhey hidayat mili , teri kifaayat ki gaee aur tujhey bacha liya gaya ( her bala sey) . chunanche shayateen us se door ho jatey hain aur doosra shaitan us se kehta hai tera dao aisey aadmi par kyonkar chaley jisey hidayat di gaee , uski kifaayat kar di gaee aur usey bacha liya gaya.''"
5096,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi apney ghar mein dakhil honey lagey to chahiye ke ye dua padhey : (اللهم ! إني أسألك خير المولج وخير المخرج بسم الله ولجنا وبسم الله خرجنا وعلى الله ربنا توكلنا) ''aey Allah ! main tujh se sawal karta hun ke (hamara) aana khair ka ho aur nikalna (bhi) khair ka ho. Allah ke naam se ham dakhil huey aur Allah hi ke naam se bahir nikley aur apney Rab Allah par ham ne tawakkul kiya.'' phir apney ghar walon ko salam kahiye.''"
5097,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''hawa Allah ki rehmat mein se hai.'' Salma (bin Shabeeb) ne kaha : ''Allah ki ye rooh kabhi rehmat laati hai aur kabhi azab bhi ley aati hai. jab tum isey dekho to isey bura mat kaho. balke Allah se iski khair ka sawal karo aur iskey shar se Allah ki panah maango.''"
5098,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine kabhi nahin dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is qadr zor se hansey hon ke main aap (ke halaq) ka kawwa dekh paon, aap muskuraayaa kartey they. jab badal ya tez hawa chalti to pareshani ki si kaifiyat aap ke chehrey par numaya ho jati thi. maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! log jab badal dekhtey hain to khush hotey hain is umeed par ke us se barish hogi magar main dekhti hun ke usey dekh kar aap ke chehrey par pareshani si aa jati hai. aapney farmaya : '' Aaisha ! mujhey ye andesha be-chain karta hai ke kahin is mein azab na ho. bila-shuba eik qom ko hawa ke zariey se azab diya gaya tha. aur eik qom ne azab dekha aur uskey log kehney lagey : ( هذا عارض ممطرنا ( ''ye badal hai is se hamein barish hogi.''"
5099,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab aasman ke kinarey par koi badal ka tukda dekhtey to kaam kaaj chhod detey agar-che Namaz hi mein hotey aur phir ye dua kartey : (اللهم ! إني أعوذ بك من شرها) ''aey Allah ! main iskey shar se teri panah chahta hun.'' aur agar barish honey lagti to kehtey : (اللهم صيبا هنيئا) ''aey Allah ! isey khoob barasney wali nafa-aawar aur Mubarak bana.''
5100,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they ke barish honey lagi . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nikley aur apney jism se kapda hata liya yahan tak ke wo aap ke jism par padney lagi. ham ne arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney aisey kyon kiya hai? aapney farmaya : ''kyonkey ye abhi-abhi apney Rab ke paas se aai hai.''"
5101,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''murgh ko gaali mat diya karo, isliye ke ye Namaz ke liye jagaata hai.''"
5102,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum murgh ki aawaz suno , tu Allah taala se uskey fazal ka sawal karo. beshak usney farishtey ko dekha hota hai. aur jab tum gadhey ki aawaz suno , to shaitan se Allah ki panah talab karo . beshak usney shaitan ko dekha hota hai.''"
5103,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum raat ko kutton ka bhonkna aur gadhon ki aawazen suno, tu Allah ki panah talab karo, bila-shuba ye wo kuchh dekhtey hain jo tum nahin dekhtey ho.''"
5104,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) aur Janab Ali bin umr bin Husain bin Ali (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab qadmon ki aawazen aana band ho jaeyn to bahut kam bahir nikla karo . bila-shuba Allah taala ki makhluq mein kuchh janwer hain jinhen Allah taala phela deta hai. Ibrahim bin Marwan ne kaha : ''us waqt mein mat nikla karo'' aur (فإن لله دواب) (ki bajaey) ye alfaz kahe (فإن لله خلقا) phir kutton ke bhonkne aur gadhon ki aawaazon ka zikr kiya jaisey mazkura baala riwayat mein hua hai. Yazid bin Abdullah bin Haad ne kaha ke mujhey Shurehbil Haajib ne Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ke jaisi riwayat ki."
5105,"Janab Ubaidullah bin Abu-Raafe ne apney walid se riwayat kiya, wo kehtey hain ke jab Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Hazrat Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko janm diya to maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke kaan mein Namaz wali Azan kahi thi."
5106,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chhotey bachchon ko laya jata tha to aap unke liye barkat ki dua farmaya kartey they. Yusuf bin Musa ne mazeed kaha ke . . . . aap unhen ghati bhi diya kartey they. . . . aur barkat ka zikr nahin kiya.
5107,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''kya tum mein koi (maghrrib) bhi paey gaey hain?'' maine arz kiya (maghrrib) se kya murad hai? aapney farmaya : ''wo bachchey jin-mein jinn shareek hon.''
5108,Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo tum se Allah ke naam par panah talab karey usey panah do . aur jo tum se Allah ke chehrey ke wastey se sawal karey usko do.'' Ubaidullah ke alfaz hain : (من سألكم بالله).
5109,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo tum se Allah ke wastey se aman maangey , usey aman do . aur jo tum se Allah ke wastey se sawal karey, usko do.'' Sehal aur Usman ne kaha : ''aur jo tumhari dawat karey, usey qubul karo.'' aur phir ye sab raawi muttafiq hain : ''aur jo tumharey sath neki karey, usko uska badla do.'' Musaddad aur Usman ne kaha ''agar badla na pao to uskey liye Allah se dua karo yahan tak ke tumhen yaqeen ho jaey ke tum ne uska badla dey diya hai.''"
5110,Janab Abu-Zameel (Simaak bin Waleed Hanfi) kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se sawal kiya : is kaifiyat ka kya ho jo main apney seeney mein paata hun? unhoney puchha : wo kya hai? maine kaha : Allah ki qasam ! main usey zaban par nahin la sakta. unhoney kaha : kya wo shak shubhe wali baat hai? aur hans diye aur boley : us se kisi ko najat nahin. yahan tak ke Allah taala ne ye aayat utaari : (فإن كنت في شك مما أنزلنا إليك فاسئل الذين يقرءون الكتاب . ۔) ''agar tumhen us cheez mein shak ho jo hamne utaari hai to un logon se poochh lijiye jo wo kitab padhtey hain jo tum se pehley utaari gaee.'' phir unhoney mujh se kaha : jab tum apney ji mein kuchh mehsoos karo to ye padha karo : (هو الأول والآخر والظاهر والباطن وهو بكل شىء عليم) ''wo Allah hi sab se awwal hai aur wohi sab se aakhir hai. wohi zahir hai aur wohi baatin hai aur wo har cheez se khoob ba-khabar hai.''
5111,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kuchh Sahaba kiram aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham apney dilon mein kuchh aisey khayalat mehsoos kartey hain ke unko zaban par lana bhi hamarey liye bada bhari hai. hamen ye bhi gawara nahin ke hamen duniya ka maal miley aur wo ham apni zabanon par laeyn . aapney farmaya : ''kya bhala tum ye kaifiyat paatey ho?'' unhoney kaha : haan . aapney farmaya : ''ye sareeh (saaf-saaf) emaan hai.''
5112,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey dil mein kuchh khayalat aatey hain aur wo isharay-kanaey se kuchh is tarah keh raha tha ke un khayalat ko zaban par laney ki bajaey koila ho jana usey ziyada pasand hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : (الله أكبر الله أكبر الله أكبر) ''Hamd us Allah ki jisney us (iblees) ke makar ko waswasey ki taraf lauta diya.'' ibne Qudama ne (رد كيده) ki bajaey (رد أمره) ke lafz kahe.
5113,"Hazrat Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke merey kanon ne Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aur merey dil ne yaad rakha hai, aapney farmaya : ''jisney apney aap ko kisi aur ka beta bataya jabkey wo janta ho ke ye (doosra) uska baap nahin hai, to jannat us par haram hai.'' Abu-Usman Nahdii kehtey hain phir main Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se mila , to maine unhen ye hadees bayan ki, to unhoney (tasdeeq kartey huey) kaha isey Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se merey kanon ne suna aur merey dil ne yaad rakha hai. Aasim (Ahwal) ne bayan kiya : maine (apney shaikh) Abu-Usman se kaha ke aap ke samney do aadmiyon ne gawahi di hai, wo kaisey aadmi hain? unhoney kaha : un mein se eik to wo hai jisney Allah ki raah . . . . ya kaha . . . . Islam mein sab se pehley teer maara , yani Hazrat Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) . aur doosra ( Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu)) wo hai jo taaif se pedal chal kar aaya tha aur un logon ki tadaad bees se ziyada thi aur unki fazilat bayan ki. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Nufaili ne kaha : chunkey Shaikh ne ye hadees (حدثنا) aur (حدثني) ke alfaz se bayan ki hai to ye mujhey shehad se bhi piyari hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey they ke maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, farmatey they : Kufiyon ki hadees mein Noor nahin. aur kaha ke maine ehle-Basra jaisa kisi ko nahin paya . unhoney Shoba se ilm (hadees) hasil kiya tha."
5114,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis (ghulam) ne apney malikon ki ijazat ke baghair kisi dusri qom se apna talluq joda us par Allah ki, farishton ki aur tamam logon ki lanat hai. us se qiyamat ke din koi nafl ya farz amal qubul nahin hoga.''"
5115,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''jisney apney baap ke alawa kisi aur ke sath apna nasab joda ya jis ghulam ne apney malikon ke alawa kisi aur ki taraf apni nisbat jodi, to us par qiyamat tak ke liye musalsal Allah ki lanat hai.''"
5116,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Shan Wale Allah ne tum se jahiliyat ki nakhwat (ghmand) aur baap-dada par fakhr ko door kar diya hai. (tumhen emaan aur Islam se moazziz (izzatdar) banaya hai.) (aadmi do qism ke hain :) sahibe emaan , muttaqi ya faajir aur bad-bakht. tum sab Adam ki aulad ho aur Adam mitti se they. logon ko qaumi nakhwat (ghamand) tarak karna padeygi, wo to (kufr aur shirk ke sabab) jahannam ke koiley bin chukey, warna ye (qom par takabbur karney waley) Allah ke yahan gandagi ke kalay keedey se bhi zaleel hongey jo apni naak se gandagi ko dhakelta phirta hai.''"
5117,"Janab Abdur-Rehman apney walid Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, jisney haq ke baghair apni qom ki madad ki to wo aisey oont ki manind hai jo kunwen mein gir gaya ho aur phir usey dam se pakad kar bahir nikala jata hai."
5118,"Janab Abdur-Rehman apney walid Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke aap chamdey ke eik khemey mein thehrey huey they aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya."
5119,"Janab Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! asbiyat kya hai? aapney farmaya : ''ye ke to apni qom ke logon ki madad karey, halanke wo zulm par hon.''"
5120,"Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik bin Ja'sham Mudliji (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khutba diya aur farmaya : ''tum mein behtar wo shakhs hai jo apney qabiley ka difaa karey ba-sharte-ke gunah ki baat na ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Ayub bin Suwaid zaeef hai."
5121,"Hazrat Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney asbiyat (dushmani) ki dawat di , wo ham mein se nahin. jisney asbiyat par ladaai ki, wo ham mein se nahin aur jo asbiyat par mara , wo ham mein se nahin.''"
5122,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qom ki behan ka beta (bhaanjaa) qom ka fard hota hai.''"
5123,"Hazrat Abu-Uqba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur ye ehle Faaris ke ghulam they, bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwae-uhud mein shareek tha. maine mushrekin ke eik aadmi ko maara aur kaha : ye lo aur main hun eik Farsi jawan ! to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''tum ne aisey kyon na kaha : ye lo aur main hun eik Ansari ghulam !''"
5124,"Janab Habib bin Ubaid Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain aur Janab Habib ko Hazrat Miqdam se mulaqat hasil thi. wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jab aadmi ko apney kisi bhai se mohabbat ho, to chahiye ke usey bata dey ke wo us se mohabbat karta hai.''"
5125,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik aadmi baitha hua tha ke eik shakhs uskey paas se guzra . to usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! beshak mujhey us-se mohabbat hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us-se farmaya : ''kya to ne usko bataya hai? '' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''usko bata dey.'' chunanche wo us-se ja kar mila aur us-se bola : mujhey tum se Allah ke liye mohabbat hai. to usney jawab diya : Allah bhi tum se mohabbat karey jiski khatir tum mujh se mohabbat kartey ho.
5126,Saiyedna Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! insan kuchh logon se mohabbat karta hai magar un jaisey amal nahin kar paata. aapney farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! tum un logon ke sath hogey jin se tum mohabbat kartey hogey.'' Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bila-shuba main Allah aur uskey Rasool se mohabbat karta hun. aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba tum unke sath hogey jin se tum mohabbat kartey ho.'' Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni ye baat phir dohrai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bhi usi tarah apna jawab dohraayaa.
5127,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine dekha Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ( ne jabkey mazkura baala farman suna : ''tum usi ke sath hogey jiskey sath tumhen mohabbat hogi.'') to wo is qadr khush huey ke unhen kisi aur cheez se is se badh kar khushi na hui thi. eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! insan eik shakhs ke sath uskey achchhey aamaal ki wajeh se mohabbat karta hai magar khud us jaisey amal nahin kar sakta. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insan uskey sath hoga jiskey sath usey mohabbat hogi.''
5128,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mashwara deney wala ameen hota hai.''
5129,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri sawari nahin rahi , mujhey sawari inayat farmaeyn . aapney farmaya : ''merey paas to koi aisi sawari nahin jo main tumhen dey sakoon . lekin falan shakhs ke paas chaley jao, shayad wo tumhen koi sawari dey dey.'' chunanche wo uskey paas chala gaya aur usney usey sawari dey di. phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur aa kar aap ko bataya (ke usney sawari de-di hai) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi khair ki rehnumai karey, usey bhi bhalai karney waley ki manind sawab milta hai.''"
5130,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi cheez ki mohabbat tumhen andha aur behra bana deti hai.''"
5131,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas (apney sathiyon ki) sifaarishein kiya karo taake sawab pao aur faisla to wohi hoga jo Allah chaheyga aur apney Nabi ki zaban se karaaeyga .''"
5132,"Saiyedna ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai) unhoney apney Ahbaab se kaha (ke sifarish kar diya karo, ajr paogey . [ unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' sifarish kya karo tumhen ajr milega .''] bila-shuba ( kabhi-kabhi ( main eik kaam kar dena chahta hun magar usey (kisi qadr ( taalta rehta hun taake tum sifarish karo aur sawab pao. yaqinan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' sifarish kya karo ajr paogey .''"
5133,"Janab abu-Barda Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki misl riwayat kartey hain."
5134,Hazrat Ala hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutalliq aata hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se Behreen mein governer they. chunanche wo jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf khat likhtey to apney naam se shuru kartey they.
5135,"Janab ibn Sirin ne Hazrat Ala ke bete se riwayat kya, unhoney (apney walid) Hazrat Ala bin hizrami ke mutalliq bataya ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khat likha, to apney naam se ibtida (shuruat) ki."
5136,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hiraql ko khat likha, to yun likha : ''Muhammad Rasulullah ki taraf se Rumiyon ke raees hiraql ki taraf . salamti ho us par jo raah hidayat par chaley .'' ibn Yahya ne bayan kya ke ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke abu-Sufiyaan ne mujhey khabar di ke ham hiraql ke yahan gaey to usney hamen apney samney bithaya . Allah ke Rasool Muhammad ki taraf se roomiyon ke sarbarah hiraql ki taraf . salamti ho us par jo raah hidayat par chaley.''"
5137,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi beta apney baap ke ehsan ka badla nahin dey sakta. siwaye uskey ke usey ( baap ko) ghulam paey , to usey khareedey aur azad kar dey .''"
5138,"Janab Hamza apney walid Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : meri zojiyat main eik aurat thi aur mujhey us se mohabbat thi. magar Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) usey napasand kartey they. to unhoney mujh se farmaya ke usey Talaq dey do . maine inkar kya, to Hazrat umr Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein gaey aur apni baat un se kahi . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( mujh sey) farmaya : '' us aurat ko Talaq dey do.''"
5139,"Janab Behaz bin Hakim apney walid sey, wo dada se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain, maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main kis ke sath Husne-sulook karun? aapney farmaya : ''apni maa ke sath . phir apni maa ke sath , phir apni maa ke sath , phir apney baap ke sath . phir qaribi rishte-daar ke sath, phir qaribi rishte-daar ke sath .'' aur bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi apney maula ( azad karda ghulam ( se uska zayed maal maangey jo uskey paas ho aur wo uskey hotey huey na dey to qiyamat ke din wo ( zayed maal) eik ganjey saanp ki shakal mein uskey samney aaeyga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : (Aqraa) se murad aisa saanp hai ke zahar ki wajeh se uskey sar ke baal ud gaey hon (aur wo ganja ho gaya ho. ("
5140,"Janab Kulaib bin munfia'a apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main kis ke sath husne-suluk karun? aapney farmaya : '' apni maa , baap , behan , bhai aur azad kerney waley sath . unka haq wajib hai aur unke sath rishta jodna lazim hai.''"
5141,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (bin Aas ( (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye baat bahut bada kabira gunah hai ke koi apney maa baap ko lanat karey.'' kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kaisey ho sakta hai ke koi apney maa baap ko lanat karey ? aapney farmaya : '' koi shakhs jab doosrey ke baap ko lanat kerega, to wo uskey baap ko lanat kerega . agar doosrey ki maa ko lanat kerega, to wo uski maa ko lanat kerega .''"
5142,"Janab Abu-Usaid Malik bin Rabeea Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik baar ittifaq se ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan baithey huey they ke qabeela bano Salma ka eik aadmi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya merey maa baap faut ho janey ke baad bhi mujh par unka koi haq baqi hai ke unke sath Husne-sulook karta rahun? aapney farmaya : ''haan . unke liye dua karna , unke liye bakhshish maangna , unke baad unke ehad ko pura karna , aisey rishta daaron se meil-milaap rakhna ke un (maa baap) ke baghair un se milaap na ho sakta tha aur unke dost ki izzat karna.''"
5143,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se bada Husne-sulook ye hai ke baap ke faut ho janey ke baad insan uskey mohabbat karney walon se milaap rakhey.''
5144,"Hazrat Abu-Tufail (Aamir bin Waasila Laisi) (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ja'araana maqam par gosht taqseem kartey dekha, mein un dino nau-khez ladka tha, oont ki haddi utha sakta tha ke achcha eik aurat aai yahan tak ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib aa gaee , to aapney uskey liye apni chadar bichha di aur wo us par baith gaee. maine puchha ke ye kon thi? to Sahaba ne bataya ke ye aap ki maa thi jisney aap ko doodh pilaya tha."
5145,"Janab umr bin Saaib se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain mujhey ye khabar pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik din baithey huey they ke aap ke razaai (doodh shareek) walid aaye. to aapney apni chadar ka eik hissey unke liye bichha diya to wo us par baith gaey. phir aap ki razaai (doodh shareek) walida aaeen to aapney us chadar ki dusri janib bichha di aur wo us par baith gaeen. phir aap ke razaai (doodh shareek) bhai aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey liye uth khadey huey aur usko apney samney bitha liya."
5146,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiskey paas koi ladki ho aur wo usey zinda dafn na kar dey ( jaisey ke kuffar kartey they (aur na uski ihaanat karey aur na ladkey ko us par fazilat dey , tu Allah taala us aadmi ko jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga . aur raawi hadees Usman ne lafz (الذكور) zikr nahin kiya."
5147,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne teen betiyon ki parwarish ki, unhen (Hasane-muaashrat ka ( adab sikhaya , unki shaadi ki aur unke sath ehsan ka maamla karta raha , to uskey liye jannat hai.''"
5148,Suhail ne isi sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kartey huey kaha : ''jisney teen behnon ya teen betiyon ya do betiyon ya do behnon ki parwarish ki.''
5149,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aur kaley rukhsaaron wali aurat qiyamat ke din is tarah (qarib qarib) hongey.'' Yazid (bin Zareea') ne apni darmiyan wali aur shahadat wali ungli milaate huey ishara karkey dikhaya. (yani) wo moazzaz aur Husn aur jameel aurat jo bewa ho gaee aur (izzat aur khoobsurti ke bawajood) usney (nikah na kiya balke) apney yateem bachchon ki khatir (nikah karney sey) ruki rahi yahan tak ke wo badey ho gaey ya wafat pa gaey."
5150,"Hazrat Sehal (bin Saad Ansari ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aur yateem ki kifalat karney wala jannat mein aisey hongey.'' aur aapney apni darmiyan wali aur shahadat wali ungli ko mila kar ishara farmaya."
5151,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael Ameen mujhey hamsaaey (padausi) ke mutalliq wasiyat kartey rahey yahan tak ke mujhey khayal hua ke wo usey waris hi bana dengey.''"
5152,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke mutalliq marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney eik bakri zibeh ki aur phir puchha : kya tum ne merey yahudi hamsaaey (padausi) ki taraf bhi kuchh bheja hai? bila-shuba maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''Jibrael Ameen mujhey hamsaaey ke mutalliq wasiyat kartey rahey yahan tak ke mujhey khayal hua ke wo usey waris hi bana dengey.''"
5153,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik shakhs aaya, usney apney padausi ki shikayat ki. aapney farmaya : ''jao aur sabr karo.'' wo phir aap ke paas do ya teen baar aaya to aapney farmaya : ''ja apna saman raastey par dal dey.'' chunanche usney apna maal-dolat raastey par dal diya. log us se poochhney lagey (ke kya hua?) to usney unhen apney padausi ka sulook bataya. to log usey lanat malamat kerney lagey . Allah uskey sath aisey karey aur aisey karey. to wo hamsaaya uskey paas aaya aur us se bola : apney ghar mein wapis chaley jao .) aainda ( meri taraf se koi na-pasandida sulook nahin dekhogey."
5154,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah par aur qiyamat par emaan rakhta ho usey chahiye ke apney mehman ki izzat karey. jo shakhs Allah par aur qiyamat par emaan rakhta ho usey chahiye ke apney padausi ko dukh na dey . aur jo shakhs Allah par aur qiyamat par emaan rakhta ho usey chahiye ke khair ke lafz boley ya khamosh rahey .''"
5155,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo kehti hain, maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey do hamsaaey hain. main ( ehsan kerney mein) kis se ibtida (shuruat) karun ? aapney farmaya : ''jis ka darwaza ziyada qarib ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya ke Shoba ne is hadees ki sanad mein Talha ke ta'aruf mein kaha : wo eik Quraishi aadmi tha."
5156,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aakhiri baat yehi thi : '' Namaz ! Namaz ! aur apney ghulamon ke baarey mein Allah se dartey rehna.''
5157,"Janab Maarur bin suwed (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko rabza maqam mein dekha, wo eik moti ooni chadar odhey huey they aur unke ghulam par bhi usi tarah ki chadar thi. hamarey sathiyon ne kaha : aey abu-Zar ! agar aap ghulam wali chadar khud ley letey to is tarah aap ka ye hulla ( pura joda (bin jata. ghulam ko aap koi aur kapda ley detey. to Hazrat abu-Zar ne jawab diya ke maine eik aadmi ko gaali di thi jiski maa ajmi thi. maine usko uski maa ka taana diya to usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan meri shikayat kar di. to aapney farmaya : ''aey abu-Zar! to aisa aadmi hai jis mein jahiliyat ka asar hai.'' aapney mazeed farmaya : ''bila-shuba ye ( ghulam ( tumharey bhai hain. Allah ne tum ko un par fazilat bakhshi hai. pas jiskey sath tumhari tabiat na milti ho, to usey bech do lekin Allah ki makhluq ko dukh na do .''"
5158,"Janab Maaroor bin Suwed (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rabza maqam mein Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se miley . ham ne dekha ke un par eik ooni chadar thi aur unke ghulam par bhi usi tarah ki eik chadar thi. to ham ne kaha : aey abu-Zar ! agar aap apney ghulam wali chadar apni chadar ke sath mila letey to eik joda bin jata aur usey aap koi aur kapda ley detey . to unhoney farmaya , maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''ye tumharey bhai hain jinhen Allah ne tumharey matehet kar diya hai. chunanche jis ka bhai uskey matehet ho to usko chahiye ke usey wohi khilaaey jo wo khud khata hai aur usey wohi pahnaaey jo khud pahnta hai. aur usey uski himmat se ziyada kaam na dey, agar usey mukallaf karey, to uski madad bhi karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke us riwayat ko ibne-Numair ne Aamash se mazkura baala ki manind riwayat kya hai."
5159,Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke) eik baar ( mein apney ghulam ko maar raha tha. to maine apney peechey se aawaz suni : '' abu-Masood ! khayal karo . . . .'' ibn Musanna ke alfaz hain : maine ye aawaz do baar suni . . . .'' Allah ko tum par us se ziyada qudrat hai jitni ke tum us par rakhtey ho.'' maine mud kar dekha to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) they. to maine ( fauran ( kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye Allah ke liye azad hua . aapney farmaya : ''agar tum ye na kartey to aag tumhen apni lapet mein ley leti .'' alfaz ( [ للفعتك النار ] ( they ya ( [ لمستك النار ] ( .
5160,Aamash ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya. us mein hai ke main apney eik (kaley) ghulam ko kodey se maar raha tha. magar us mein usko azad kerney ka bayan nahin hai.
5161,"Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey londi ghulamon mein se jo tumharey muwaafiq ho (tumhari pasand ke mutabiq tumhari khidmat karta ho) to usko usi se khilao jo tum khatey ho aur usko usi se pehnao jo tum pehantey ho. aur jo tumharey muwaafiq na ho, to usey bech dalo aur Allah ki makhluq ko azab na do.''"
5162,Hazrat Raafe bin Makees (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur ye ghazwa Hudebiya mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shareek they. unhoney bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (apney matehet aur zer milkiyat ke sath ( umda bartao karna barkat hai aur bd-khulqi nahusat hai.''
5163,"Janab Haris bin Raafe bin Makees se riwayat hai, aur Hazrat Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) qabeela juhaina se they aur ghazwa Hudebiya mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya, aapney farmaya : '' (zer milkiyat aur matehet ke sath) umda bartao karna baaise-barkat hai aur bd-khulqi nahusat hai."
5164,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham khaadim ko kis qadr maaf keren? to aap khamosh rahey . usney phir sawal kya, to aap khamosh rahey. phir jab teesri baar puchha , to aapney farmaya : ''usey her roz sattar baar maaf karo.''"
5165,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain, mujh se Hazrat abul-Qaasim Nabi tauba (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bayan farmaya : '' jisney apney ghulam par tohmat lagai halanke wo us se bari tha jo uskey baarey mein kaha gaya tha to us ( Malik ( ko qiyamat ke din had lagai jaeygi .'' Momil (bin fazal) ne sanad yun bayan ki) [ حدثنا عيسى an (an) الفضيل يعني ibn ghazawaan ] ("
5166,"Janab Hilal bin Yasaf se marwi (bayan) hai ke ham Hazrat Suwaid bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein thehrey huey they, hamarey sath eik badi umr ka Shaikh bhi tha jiski tabiat mein tezi thi aur uskey sath uski londi thi. to us shaikh ne apni us londi ke chehrey par thappad maar diya. us din Hazrat Suwaid (Raziallahu anhu) jis qadr ghussay huey maine us se badh kar unhen kabhi ghazabnaak nahin dekha. unhoney kaha : kya to itna hi aajiz (aur maghloob (ghazab ka maara)) ho gaya tha ke usko maarney ke liye tujhey sirf uska izzat wala chehra hi mila tha. mujhey wo manzar yaad hai ke main aulade-Muqrin mein saatwan fard tha aur hamari eik hi khaadima thi. hamarey eik chhotey ne uskey chehrey par thappad maar diya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke usko azad kar do.''"
5167,"Janab Muawiya bin Suwaid bin Muqrin kehtey hain ke maine apney eik ghulam ko thappad maar diya. to merey walid ne usko aur mujhey bula liya aur ghulam se kaha : us se apna badla lo . aur bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ham bano Muqrin ke saat afrad they aur hamari eik hi khaadima thi. hamarey eik aadmi ne usko thappad maar diya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey azad kar do.'' Sahaba ne kaha ke unke paas uskey alawa aur koi khaadima nahin hai. farmaya : ''chalo jab tak koi aur nahin milti khidmat karti rahey, jab is-se mustaghni (be-niyazi) ho jaeyn to isey azad kar den.''"
5168,"Janab Azan bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas aaya jabkey unhoney apna eik ghulam azad kiya tha. unhoney zameen se eik tinkaa ya us qisam ki koi cheez uthai aur kaha : mujhey uskey azad karney mein is jitna bhi sawab nahin hai. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''jisney apney ghulam ko thappad lagaya ho ya maara ho, to uska kaffara yehi hai ke usey azad kar dey.''"
5169,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tehqiq jo ghulam apney aaqa ko khair khuwahi ki baat kahe aur Shan Wale Allah ki ibadat bhi achchhey tareeqey se karey, to usko do guna sawab hai.''"
5170,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi kisi ki biwi ko uskey shohar ke khilaf ya ghulam (khaadim) ko uskey Malik ke khilaf bhadkaaye , wo ham mein se nahin.''"
5171,Saiyedna Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi ghar mein jhaankaa . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik lambey phal ka neza liye huey uski janib uthey . Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : goya ke main dekh raha hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye neza usey maarney ke liye laharaa rahey they.
5172,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''jisney kisi ke ghar mein unki ijazat ke baghair jhaankaa aur unhoney uski aankh phod di to ye zaya hai (is mein koi qisaas nahin).''"
5173,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab nazar andar chali gaee to phir ijazat kaisi?''"
5174,Hazrat Huzail (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs . . . . aur baqaul Usman bin Abi Sheba Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu)  aaye aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke darwazey par khadey ho kar ijazat talab karney lagey . . . . Usman bin Abi Sheba ne wazahat ki ke wo darwazey ke aen samney khadey ho gaey . . . . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : ''us taraf hatt kar khadey ho ya us taraf . ijazat leney ka hukm nazar hi ki wajeh se hai (ke insan andar na jhaankey).''
5175,"Talha bin Musrif ne eik aadmi ke wastey sey, Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya."
5176,"Hazrat Kalda bin Hanbal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko doodh, hiran ka bachcha aur kakdiyan de-kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja , jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka ki baalai (upri) janib mein thehrey huey they. Kalada kehtey hain ke main aap ki majlis mein ja dakhil hua aur salam na kaha. to aapney farmaya : ''peechhey hato aur kaho ''السلام علیکم'' ye waqia Safwan bin Umayya ke musalman ho janey ke baad ka hai. Amr (bin Abu-Sufiyaan) ne kaha : mujhey ye sab (Umayya) ibne Safwan ne Kalda bin Hanbal ke wastey se bayan kiya aur is mein samaa, ka zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Yahya bin Habib ne (ibne Umayya ki saraahat ki aur) Umayya bin Safwan kaha . aur Kalda bin Hanbal se samaa, (suna) ki saraahat nahin ki. aur Yahya bin Habib ne ye bhi kaha ke Amr bin Abdullah bin Safwan ne b-seegha akhbaar riwayat kiya."
5177,Janab Rabae se riwayat hai ke bano Aamir ke eik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat chahi jabkey aap ghar ke andar they. aur usney kaha : ''kya main andar aa sakta hun?'' to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney khaadim se farmaya : ''uski taraf jao aur usey ijazat talab karney ka adaab sikhao usey kaho ke (is tarah) kahe : ''السلام علیکم'' kya main andar aa sakta hun?'' us aadmi ne ye baat sun li to bola : ''السلام علیکم'' kya main andar aa sakta hun? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey ijazat de-di aur wo andar aa gaya.
5178,"Janab Rabae bin Harash se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain mujhey bayan kiya gaya ke bano Aamir ke eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat chahi. aur mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain Musaddad ne Abu-Awaana sey, unhoney Mansoor se (aur unhoney Rabae sey) aisey hi riwayat kiya hai. . . aur us mein bano Aamir ke aadmi ka zikr nahin kiya."
5179,"Ubaidullah bin Muaz ne apney walid se bayan kiya, unhoney Shoba sey, unhoney Mansoor sey, unhoney Rabae sey, aur wo bano Aamir ke eik aadmi se riwayat kartey hain ke usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. kaha ke maine aap ki baat sun li to maine kaha : ''السلام علیکم'' kya main andar aa sakta hun?"
5180,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main ansaar ki eik majlis mein baitha hua tha ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) ghabraey ghabraey se aaye. ham ne un se puchha : aap ghabraey huey kyon hain? to unhoney bataya ke mujhey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bulwaya tha ke unke paas jaun. main unke yahan gaya aur teen baar ijazat talab ki magar mujhey ijazat nahin di gaee , to main wapis honey laga . to unhoney kaha : kya wajeh thi ke tum merey paas nahin aaye? maine un se kaha ke main aaya tha aur teen baar ijazat maangi magar nahin di gaee . aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''tum mein se jab koi teen baar ijazat maangey aur usey ijazat na di jaey to chahiye ke wo laut aaye.'' to unhoney (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( kaha hai : tumhen apney is bayan par gawah pesh karna padeyga. to Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tumharey sath qaum ka koi chhota bacha bhi ja sakta hai. (wo is hadees ke sahih honey ki gawahi dey sakta hai) chunanche Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) unke sath gaey aur Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke haq mein gawahi di."
5181,"Janab Abu-Barda se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey aur teen baar ijazat maangi aur kaha : Abu-Musa ijazat chahta hai. Ash'ari ijazat chahta hai. Abdullah bin Qais ( Abu-Musa Ash'ari) ijazat chahta hai. magar ijazat na mili to ye wapis ho liye. chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko peechhey se bulwaya ke wapis kyon ja rahey ho? to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' ijazat teen baar maango , agar mil jaey to behtar warna wapis ho jao.'' Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : apney bayan par mujhey gawah pesh karo (ke haqeeqat mein ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman hai.) to wo gaey aur wapis aaye aur kaha : ye Abi (Raziallahu anhu) aagey hain. to Hazrat Abi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey umr ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ke liye azab na banen. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ke liye azab nahin hun."
5182,Janab Ubaid bin Umair se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se ijazat talab ki . aur mazkura qissa bayan kiya. aur is mein hai ke wo Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar gaey to unhoney unke haq mein gawahi di. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman mujh se makhfi (chhipa) raha hai? mujhey baazar ke tijaarati mashaaghil ne mashghool rakha . aur tum jab chaho salam keh ke aa jaya karo aur ijazat na manga karo.
5183,Janab Abu-Barda ne apney walid Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura qissa riwayat kiya. us mein hai ke phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : bila-shuba mein tum par kisi tarah ki tohmat nahin laga raha (ke tum jhoot keh rahey ho) lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees naqal karney ka maamla bada sakht (aur aham) hai.
5184,"Janab Rabeea bin Abu-Abdur-Rehman aur kaee eik muhaddeseen se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : main aap par koi tohmat nahin laga raha , lekin mujhey andesha hai ke kahin log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf waisay hi ahadis ki nisbat na karney lagen."
5185,"Hazrat Qais bin Saad (bin Ubada) (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein milney ke liye hamarey ghar tashrif laye. aur (ijazat talab kartey huey farmaya : ''السلام علیکم ورحمۃ اللہ !'' (merey walid) Saad ne aap ko jawab diya magar halki aawaz se. Qais kehtey hain, maine kaha : kya aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ijazat nahin dengey? to unhoney kaha : chhodo . unhen ham par ziyada se ziyada salam kehney do. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir farmaya : ''السلام علیکم ورحمۃ اللہ'' to Saad ne halki ( aahista ( aawaz se jawab diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir farmaya : ''السلام علیکم ورحمۃ اللہ'' aur wapis janey lagey . to Saad peechhey se lapkey aur arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main aap ka salam sun raha tha aur jawab bhi dey raha tha magar halki (aur aahista) aawaz sey, taake aap (hamein) ziyada se ziyada salam kahen (aur hamein aap ki duayen hasil hon). chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tashrif ley aaye . Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se ghusl karney ka kaha to aapney ghusl farma liya . phir aap ko Zaafran ya waras se rangi hui chadar di jo aapney lapet li . phir aapney ye kehtey huey apney dono haath buland farmaai : (اللهم ! اجعل صلواتك ورحمتك على آل سعد بن عبادة) ''aey Allah ! aale Saad bin Ubada par apni khas barkaten aur rahmatein nazil farma .'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuchh khana khaya . jab aapney wapsi ka irada farmaya to Saad ne gadhaa qarib kar diya jabkey uski peeth par kapda dal diya tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uspar Sawar ho gaey . to Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Qais ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jao . Qais kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''Sawar ho jao.'' magar maine inkar kiya to aapney farmaya : ''ya to Sawar ho jao ya wapis chaley jao.'' chunanche main wapis aa gaya. Hisham , Abu-Marwaan ne ye riwayat Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Asaad bin Zarara se b-seegha riwayat ki hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke umr bin Abdul-Waahid aur ibn Sama'aa ne ye riwayat Auzaai se mursal riwayat ki hai aur un dono ne Qais bin Saad ka zikr nahin kiya."
5186,Hazrat Abdullah bin basar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah jab kisi ke darwazey par jatey to uskey bilkul samney khadey na hua kartey they. balke daain ya baain janib ho kar khadey hotey aur farmatey : ''Assalamualaikum Assalamualaikum.'' aur un dino darwazon par pardey nahin hua kartey they.
5187,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke main apney walid ke qarzey ke silsiley mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir hua to maine darwazey par dastak di. aapney puchha : '' kon hai? ''maine jawab mein kaha : main hun. aapney farmaya : ''main hun, main hun.'' goya aapney us andaz ko napasand farmaya."
5188,Hazrat Naafe bin Abdul Haris (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikla yahan tak ke eik baagh mein dakhil hua . to aapney mujh se farmaya : '' darwazey ko) andar sey) rokey rakho ( usey kholna nahin .'' ( phir darwaza khatkhataaya gaya. ( bahir se kisi ne dastak di ( to maine puchha : kon hai? aur hadees bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us se murad Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) wali hadees hai. raawi ne us mein kaha : to unhoney darwaza khatkhataaya.
5189,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi ko bulaney ke liye aadmi ka bheja jana, us ( aaney waley (ke liye ijazat (ke maani mein) hai.''"
5190,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab kisi ko khaney par bulaya jaey aur wo bulaney waley ke sath chala aaye to yehi uskey liye ijazat hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : kaha jata hai ke Qatada ne abu-Raafe se kuch nahin suna ."
5191,"Janab Ubaidullah bin abu-Yazeed se riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko suna, wo kehtey they ke aksar log (sura Noor mein waarid aayat : 58 ( ijazat talab kerney wali aayat par (kama-haqqahu) emaan nahin laye, halanke main apni us londi ko kehta hun ke merey paas aatey huey bhi ijazat liya karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : Ata ne bhi ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se aisey hi riwayat kya hai ke wo uska hukm diya kartey they."
5192,"Janab Ikrima se riwayat hai ke Iraq ke kuch logon ne kaha : aey ibne-Abbas ! aap is aayate-kareema ke baarey mein kya kehtey hain ke us mein jo hukm hamen diya gaya hai, us par koi amal nahin karta hai? yani Allah taala ka farman : ( يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا لِيَسْتَأْذِنْكُمْ . . . . عَلَيْكُمْ (aey emaan walo ! chahiye ke tumhari londi ghulam aur tumharey nabaaligh bachey teen oqaat mein tum se ijazat lein. namaze-Fajr se pehley, aur do-pehar ko jab tum apney kapdey utaartey ho aur Namaz Isha ke baad , ye teen oqaat tumharey pardey ke hain, unke ilawa tum par aur un par koi harj nahin, ye tumharey paas aaney janey waley hain, ( Abdullah bin Muslima ( Qaanabi ne aayat aakhir tak , yani ( aleem hakim ( tak padhi . Hazrat ibne-Abbas ne farmaya : bila-shuba Allah azz-w-jall haleem hai (bardasht karta hai) aur momineen par rehem kerney wala hai aur pardey ko pasand karta hai. (jab ye aayat utri ( logon ke gharon mein pardey hotey they na otein hoti thin . kabhi-kabhi aadmi apni ehliya se sohbat kar raha hota to koi khaadim aa jata ya bacha ya yateem bachi ( jo ghar mein hoti to ye keyfiyat had se zyada namunasib hoti thi) tu Allah taala ne unhen un pardey ke oqaat mein ijazat leney ka hukm diya. to ab Allah ne unko pardey dey diye hain aur khair ( faraakhi) inayat farma di hai) to us wajeh sey) mein kisi ko us par amal kartey huey nahin dekhta hun. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : (mazkura baala riwayat ( Ubaidullah aur Ata ki hadees is hadees ke khilaf banti hai."
5193,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum log us waqt tak jannat mein nahin ja sakogey jab tak ke emaan na ley aao. aur tum us waqt tak momin nahin ho saktey jab tak ke aapas mein mohabbat na kerney lago. kya main tumhen aisi baat na bata dun ke us par amal kerney se aapas mein mohabbat kerney lago ? aapas mein salam bahut kya karo.''"
5194,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya : kon sa Islam ( Islam ki kon si khaslat ( behtar hai? aapney farmaya : '' tumhara khana khilana aur salam kehna usey, jisey tum pehchantey ho ya na pehchantey ho.''"
5195,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : '' Assalamualaikum '' aapney uskey salam ka jawab diya aur wo beth gaya. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' das .'' phir doosra aadmi aaya aur usney kaha : '' Assalamualaikum warahmatullah '' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko jawab diya aur wo beth gaya. to aapney farmaya : '' bees .'' phir eik aur aaya to usney kaha  '' Assalamualaikum warahmatullah wabarkatuh '' aapney uska jawab inayat farmaya aur wo beth gaya , to aapney farmaya : '' tees .''"
5196,"Janab Sehal apney walid ( Muaz bin Anas ( sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya. us mein izafa hai ke phir eik ( chotha aadmi ( aaya to usney kaha : '' Assalamualaikum warahmatullah wabarkatuh wamaghfiratuh'' to aapney farmaya : ''chaalis (chaalis nekiyan milen.) aur nekiyan aisey hi badhti hain.''"
5197,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon mein Allah ke yahan sab se ziyada qarib wo shakhs hai jo unhen salam kehney mein ibtida (shuruat) karey.''"
5198,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chhota badey ko , guzarney wala bethey huey ko aur kam log ziyada tadaad walon ko salam kahen .''"
5199,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Sawar aadmi pedal ko salam kahey.'' phir mazkura hadees bayan ki ."
5200,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi apney bhai se miley to usey salam kahey. pas agar unke darmiyan koi darkht , deewar ya pathar rukawat ho jaey aur phir dobara miley, to bhi salam kahey. Janab Muawiya (bin Saleh ( ne kaha : mujhey abdul-wahaab bin bakht ne abu-Zanaad sey, usney Aaraj sey, usney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ki misl riwayat kya."
5201,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne riwayat kya ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye jabkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney hujrey mein they. unhoney kaha : ( Assalamualaik ya Rasulullah Assalamualaikum ( kya umr andar aa sakta hai?
5202,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bachon ke paas se guzrey jabkey wo khel rahey they to aapney unko salam kaha.
5203,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye jabkey main ladkon mein se eik ladka tha. pas aapney hamen Assalamualaikum kaha . phir aapney mera haath pakda aur mujhey eik pegham deney ke liye bhej diya. aur khud eik deewar ke saye mein . . . . ya kaha . . . . deewar ke sath ho kar beth rahey yahan tak ke main aap ke paas wapis aa gaya.
5204,Hazrat Asma bint Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham aurton ki jamaat par guzrey to aapney hamen salam kaha .
5205,"Janab Suhel bin abu-Saaleh ne kaha : main apney walid ke sath shaam ki taraf gaya to log esaiyon ke ibadat khaanon par se guzrey , to unhen salam kehtey they. merey walid ne kaha : unhen salam kehney mein ibtida (shuruat) na karo, isliye ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman bayan kya hai : '' un logon ( kafiron ( ko salam kehney mein ibtida (shuruat) na karo aur jab tum unhen raastey mein milo to unhen tang raastey ki taraf majboor kar do .''"
5206,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' yahudi jab tumhen salam kehtey hain to ( lafz ( ) Assamualaikum ( boltey hain ( tum par maut aaye ( to tum unhen jawab mein) Waalekum ( kaha karo .) jo tum ne kaha hai wo tum par ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Imam Malik aur Sauri ne Abdullah bin Dinar se usi tarah bayan kya hai. us mein kaha : ( Waalekum ( ."
5207,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Sahaba kiram ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya ke ehle-kitab (yahudi aur esai) hamen salam kehtey hain to ham unhen kis tarah jawab den? aapney farmaya : ''tum unhen (Waalekum) kaha karo.'' ( Assalam) ka lafz na bola karo . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Sayeda Aaisha, abu-Abdur-Rehman Johni aur Abu-Basra ghifaari ki riwayat bhi usi tarah hai."
5208,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi kisi majlis mein pahunchey to chahiye ke salam kahey aur jab wahan se uthna chahey to bhi salam kahey. pehli dafa salam kehna dusri dafa ke muqabley mein koi ziyada aham nahin hai.''"
5209,"Hazrat Abu-Jari Hujemi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , to maine kaha : ( Alaikassalam ya Rasulullah!) aapney farmaya : ye lafz ( Alaikassalam) mat bolo, ye mardon ka salam hai.''"
5210,"ameerul-momeneen Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, . . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke unke Shekh Hasan bin Ali ne us riwayat ko marfoo zikr kya. . . . farmaya ke eik jamaat guzar rahi ho to un mein se kisi eik ka salam keh dena kafi hai. aur bethey huey ( logon ( mein se koi eik jawab de-dey to kafi hai."
5211,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab do musalmanon ki mulaqat hoti hai aur wo musaafa kartey hain, Allah ki hamd bayan kartey aur us se bakhshish maangtey hain, tu Allah azz-w-jall un dono ki maghfirat farma deta hai.''"
5212,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi do musalman mulaqat kartey aur phir musaafa kartey hain, to juda honey se pehley hi un dono ki maghfirat farma di jati hai.''"
5213,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab ehle Yamen aaye, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tehqiq ehle Yamen tumharey paas aagey hain. aur ye pehley log hain jinhon ne musaafey ka amal shuru kya. ''"
5214,"Janab Ayub bin Bashir bin Kab Adwi, bano anza ke eik aadmi se riwayat kartey hain ke usney Hazrat abu-Zar ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha jabkey unhen shaam se rawana kar diya gaya tha. unhoney kaha ke main aap se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik hadees daryaft karna chahta hun. unhoney kaha : agar raz ki baat na hui to main bata dunga. maine kaha : koi raz ki baat nahin hai. aap log jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mulaqat kartey they to kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tum logon se musaafa kya kartey they? unhoney kaha : main jab bhi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mila, aapney mujh se musaafa farmaya. aur eik din aapney mujhey bulwaaya, magar main ghar mein nahin tha. jab main wapis aaya to mujhey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bulaawey ka bataya gaya. mein aap ki khidmat mein pahuncha . aap apni chaarpai par tashrif farma they. to aapney mujh se galey miley aur ye ( merey liye ( umda , bahut umda baat thi."
5215,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke banu Qureza ne jab Hazrat Saad (bin Muaz ( (Raziallahu anhu) ka faisla qubul kar leney par ittifaq kar liya to aapney Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulwaya , wo eik safed gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaye , to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney sardar ki taraf ya apney afzal ki taraf badho .'' to wo ( Saad ( aaye yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas beth gaey ."
5216,Janab Shoba ne ye riwayat bayan ki . kaha ke jab wo masjid ke qarib aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ansariyon se farmaya : '' apney sardar ki taraf badho .''
5217,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine kisi ko nahin paya ke wo apni aadaat, chaal chalan aur baat cheet mein Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) se badh kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mushabeh ho. . . Hasan bin Ali ki riwayat mein) حديثا وكلاما (ke lafz waarid hain. ( السمت والهدى والدل (ke alfaz nahin hain. . . . jab wo aap ke yahan aatin to aap uth kar unki taraf badhtey, unka haath pakadtey, bosa detey aur apni jagah par bitha letey aur (usi tarah) jab aap unke yahan jatey to wo uth kar aap ki taraf badhtin, aap ka haath pakadtin bosa detin aur apni jagah par bitha detin .''"
5218,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Aqraa bin Haabis (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko bosa dey rahey they. to usney kaha : yaqinan merey das bachey hain aur maine kisi ke sath aisey nahin kya. ( kisi ko kabhi bosa nahin diya ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo rehem nahin karta us par rehem nahin kya jata .''
5219,"Janab Urwa se riwayat hai ke Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne ( waqia ifk ke silsiley mein bayan kartey huey ( kaha phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aaisha khushkhabri ho ! Allah azz-w-jall ne teri baraat nazil farma di hai.'' aur usey Quran majeed ki aayaat padh kar sunaain, to merey maa baap ne mujhey kaha : utho aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar ko bosa do . to maine kaha : main Allah azz-w-jall ki hamd karti hun, tum dono ki nahin."
5220,"Janab Shobi (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Hazrat Jaafar bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se miley ( jabkey wo safar se wapis aaye they ( to aapney un se muaaniqa kya aur unki aakhon ke darmiyan bosa bhi diya."
5221,Janab Ayas bin Daghfal (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke maine Janab abu-Nazara ( munzir bin Malik ( (Rahimahullah) ko dekha ke unhoney Saiyedna Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke rukhsaar par bosa diya.
5222,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath aaya jabkey ye log naey naey Madina aaye they, aur unki sahibzadi Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bukhar ki wajeh se leti hui thi , to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) unke qarib huey aur puchha : batiyaa tumhara kya haal hai? aur unke rukhsaar par bosa bhi diya."
5223,Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Laila ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne qissa bayan kya ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib huey aur ham ne aap ke haath ko bosa diya.
5224,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Laila , Hazrat Usaid bin Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain aur ye ansaar mein se they. ye eik dafa apni qom se baaten kar rahey they. mazahiya aadmi they. aur unhen hansa rahey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki kokh main eik lakdi chubho di. to unhoney ( Usaid bin Huzair ne ( kaha : mujhey badla diijiye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''le lo.'' unhoney kaha : aap par to qamis hai aur mujh par qamis nahin thi. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni qamis ooper kar di. to Usaid ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney baazuon mein ley liya aur aap ke pehlu par bosey deney lagey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri yehi niyat thi."
5225,"Umme- Aban binte-Waze bin Zaare apney dada Zaare se riwayat karti hain aur ye wafad abdul-Qais mein shareek they. unhoney kaha : jab ham Madina munawwara pahunchey to ham jaldi jaldi apni sawaariyon se utar kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey aur aap ke haath aur paon ko bosey deney lagey lekin munzir ashajj ne intizar kya yahan tak ke wo apney saman ke paas gaey aur apney do kapdey pehney phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba tum mein do khaslatein aisi hain jinhen Allah taala pasand farmata hai. hilm ( buland hosla hona aur jald bazi na karna (aur ba-waqar hona .'' usney puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main un baaton ka takalluf se izhar karta hun, ya Allah azz-w-jall ne mujhey un par paida kya hai. aapney farmaya : '' balke Allah ne tumhen un par paida farmaya hai.'' to usney kaha : hamd us Allah ki jisney mujhey aisi aadaton par paida farmaya hai jinhen Allah aur uska Rasool pasand farmatey hain."
5226,"Saiyedna abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha : ''aey abu-Zar ! ''maine kaha : main hazir hun aur bada ba-saadat hun. aey Allah ke Rasool ! main aap par fida aur qurban ."
5227,Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) ya kisi doosrey se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : ham jahiliyat mein) eik doosrey ko) yun kaha kartey they : ( أنعم الله بك عينا) ''Allah tumhari aankhen thandi rakhey . ya tumhari wajeh se tumharey mehboob ki aankhen thandi rahen.'' aur (أنعم صباحا) '' subh b-khair .'' phir jab Islam aa gaya to hamen us se rok diya gaya. abdur-Razzaaq ne bayan kya ke Maamer ne kaha : ( أنعم الله بك عينا) kehna makruh hai. lekin agar ( أنعم الله عينك ( kahey to koi harj nahin.
5228,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney eik safar mein they ke Sahaba ko piyas ne sataya to jald-baaz log aagey badh gaey aur main us raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sath raha , to aapney farmaya : ''Allah teri hifazat karey jaisey to ne uskey Nabi ki hifazat ki .''"
5229,"Janab abu-Mujliz bayan kartey hain ke ameerul-momeneen Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) , Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber aur Abdullah bin Aamir (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ke yahan aaye to ibn Aamir (Raziallahu anhu)) unke ehtiraam mein) khadey ho gaey . lekin ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) bethey rahey . to Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibn Aamir se kaha : beth jaeyn , isliye ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''jo shakhs ye pasand karta ho ke log uskey liye khadey rahen to usey chahiye ke apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.''"
5230,"Hazrat abu-Umama baahli (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye . aap apney asa ke saharey se chal rahey they. ham aap ki taraf khadey huey to aapney farmaya : '' ajmiyon ( ghair muslimon ( ki tarah mat utha karo, jis mein ke wo eik doosrey ko tazeem detey hain.''"
5231,"Janab ghalib (bin Khataaf Basri) ne bayan kya ke ham Janab Hasan Basri ke darwazey par bethey huey they ke eik aadmi aaya aur usney kaha ke mujhey merey walid ne merey dada se riwayat kya, usney kaha : merey walid ne mujh ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja aur kaha ke aap ke paas jao aur aap ko mera salam kehna. chunanche main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke merey walid ne aap ko salam kaha hai. to aapney farmaya : '' ( عليك وعلى أبيك السلام ( ''tum par aur tumharey walid par salamti ho.''"
5232,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : '' tehqiq Jibrael Alehissalam tujhey salam keh rahey hain.'' to unhoney kaha : ( w alaihissalam warahmatullah)"
5233,"Hazrat abu-Abdur-Rehman Fahri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main ghazwa Hunain mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha. ham intehai garmi ke din mein chaltey rahey, phir eik darkht ke saye taley utrey. jab Suraj dhal gaya to maine apni zireh pahni, ghodey par Sawar hua aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aa gaya. aap apney khemey mein they. maine arz kya ( Assalamualaik ya Rasulullah warahmatullahi wabarkatuh) kooch ka waqt ho gaya hai. aapney farmaya : '' haan ! '' phir farmaya : '' Bilal ! utho '' to wo eik keekar ke darkht ke nichey se uchal kar uthey aur unka saya aisey pad raha tha jaisey kisi perindey ka ho. (wo bahut hi naheef jism ke they) unhoney kaha : main hazir hun aur hazir hun aur aap par fida hun. aapney farmaya : ''mera ghoda tayyar karo.'' (us par zeen rakho) chunanche usney aisi zeen nikali jiski gaddiyaan khajoor ki chhaal se bhari gaee thin. un mein kisi qism ka takabbur aur badai na thi (intehai saada thin.) chunanche aap Sawar ho gaey aur ham bhi . aur puri hadees bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke abu-Abdur-Rehman fahri se yehi eik hadees marwi (bayan) hai aur ye umda hadees hai jisey Hammad bin Salma ne riwayat kya hai."
5234,Janab ( Abdullah ( ibn Kinaana bin Abbas bin Mirdas apney walid se wo dada se riwayat kartey hain ke (eik baar ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans diye to Hazrat abu-Bakar ya umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : Allah aap ko) hamesha ( hansta muskraata rakhey . aur hadees bayan ki .
5235,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke main aur meri walida apney ehatey ki deewar leep rahey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas se guzrey . aapney puchha : '' Abdullah ! kya ho raha hai? ''maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! iski kuch marammat kar raha hun. aapney farmaya : '' maamla to is se bahut jald hai.''
5236,"Janab Aamash ne apni sanad se mazkura baala riwayat bayan ki, kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas se guzrey aur ham apni jhuggi (ya kothri) jo boseedah ho gaee thi, uski marammat kar rahey they. aapney puchha : ''kya ho raha hai? '' ham ne arz kya ke hamari ye jhuggi boseedah ho gaee hai, to uski marammat kar rahey hain, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main to maamley ko us se bhi jald samajhta hun.''"
5237,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahir nikley to eik ooncha quba ( numa makan) dekha . aapney puchha : ''ye kya hai? '' Sahaba ne arz kya ke ye falan Ansari ka hai. kehtey hain ke aap khamosh ho rahey aur baat apney dil mein rakhi . jab uska Malik doosrey logon ke sath aap ke paas salam kerney ke liye aaya, to aapney us par tawajjoh na di. aur baar baar aisey hua yahan tak ke wo samajh gaya ke aap naraz hain aur tawajjoh nahin farmatey hain. to usney us keyfiyat ki apney sathiyon se shikayat ki aur kaha qasam Allah ki mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko badla badla sa paata hun. uskey sathiyon ne bataya ke aap bahir gaey they aur tumhara quba dekha tha. chunanche wo aadmi apney us quba numaa makaan par gaya aur usey gira diya, yahan tak ke usey zameen ke barabar kar diya. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik din bahir gaey aur makaan nazar na aaya to puchha : ''qubey ka kya hua? Sahaba ne bataya ke uskey Malik ne aap ki be tawajjohi ki ham se shikayat ki thi to ham ne usey wajeh batai to usney usey gira diya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her taameer apney Malik ke liye wabal ka baais hai magar wo jo . . . . magar wo jiskey baghair chaara na ho.''"
5238,Hazrat Dukain bin Saeed Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur ham ne aap se ghalley ka mutalba kya. to aapney farmaya : ''Umar! jao aur unko do .'' chunanche wo hamen lekar eik bala-khaney par chadhey aur apney hujrey se chaabii lekar usko khola .
5239,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Habshi (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney beri ka darkht kaata, Allah uskey sar ko jahannam mein ulta latkaaega. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) se is hadees ki wazahat puchhi gaee , to unhoney farmaya : ye hadees mukhtasar hai. us se murad ye hai ke jangal mein lagi beri ka darkht jo aaney janey waley musafiron aur janweron ke liye saye ka kaam deta ho aur koi shakhs be maqsad zulm se usey kaat daley , tu Allah usey jahannam mein ulta latkaaeyga."
5240,"Janab Usman bin abu-Suleman ne Saqif ke eik aadmi sey, usney Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfoo riwayat kya aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan ki ."
5241,"Hassaan bin Ibrahim kehtey hain : maine Hisham bin Urwa se ye masla puchha ke beri ka kaatna kaisa hai jabkey wo apney walid Urwa ke mehal ke sath tek lagaey bethey they? to unhoney kaha : kya tum ye darwazey aur chaukhtein dekh rahey ho, ye Urwa ki beriyon se banaey gaey hain aur Urwa unhen apni zameen se kaat liya kartey they aur kaha ke is mein koi harj nahin hai. Humaid bin musada ne mazeed kaha ke Hisham ne kaha : arey Iraaqi! ( Hassaan bin Ibrahim ( to to merey paas eik bidat wali baat laya hai. usney kaha : maine jawab diya ke bidat to tumhari taraf se hai. maine Makka mein ulama se suna hai jo ye bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey aadmi par lanat ki hai jo beri ko kaatey . phir mazkura baala ke ham-maani bayan kya."
5242,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' insan ke andar teen so saath jod hain. to us par wajib hai ke apney her her jod ke badley sadqa diya karey.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! kon iski himmat rakhta hai? aapney farmaya : ''masjid mein padi raint (halaq ki gandagi) ko dafn kar dena, raastey mein padi ( takleef deh ( chiz hata dena aur agar ye na ho sakey to chaasht ki do rakatein hi tumhen us ( tamam sadqey ( se kafi ho jaeyngi.''"
5243,"Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' subh hoti hai aur Adam zaad ke jod jod par sadqa wajib ho chuka hota hai. uska apney milney waley ko salam kehna sadqa hai, kisi ko neki ki baat batana sadqa hai, burai se mana karna sadqa hai, raastey se takleef deh chiz door kar dena sadqa hai, biwi se sohbat karna sadqa hai.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo apni shehwat puri karey aur wo uskey liye sadqa baney ye kyonkar hai? aapney farmaya : '' batao agar wo haram mein ye kaam karey to kya gunah gaar nahin hoga ?'' ( uskey bilmuqaabil halal se apni khahish puri karna sawab aur sadqa hua .) . aapney farmaya : '' in sab kamon se uskey liye chaasht ki do rakatein kifaayat kar jati hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hammad (bin Zaid) ne Amr bil-maaroof aur nahi anul-munkar ka zikr nahin kya."
5244,Hazrat abu-Aswad Deli ne Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se ye riwayat naqal ki . aur kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye hadees apni guftgu ke doran bayan farmaai.
5245,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik aadmi jisney kabhi koi neki ka kaam nahin kya tha, usney raastey se kaanton ki eik tehni door kar di. ye ( tehni (ya to darkht par thi ke usney kaat phenki ya raastey mein padi thi aur usney eik taraf hata di tu Allah taala ne uska ye amal qubul kar liya aur uski wajeh se usey jannat mein dakhil farma diya .''"
5246,Janab Salim (Rahimahullah) apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain aur eik baar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfoo bhi zikr kya ke : '' sotey waqt apney gharon mein aag na rehney diya karo.''
5247,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik baar eik chuhiya chiragh ki batti ghaseet'ti hui ley aai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney us chatai par dal di jis par aap tashrif farma they aur eik dirham ke barabar jagah jal gaee. to aapney farmaya : ''jab tum soney lago to apney chiragh bujha diya karo. bila-shuba shetan is jaisi makhluq ko is qism ka kaam sujha deta hai aur tumharey gharon mein aag laga deta hai.''
5248,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab se hamari un ( saanpon ( se ladaai shuru hui hai ham ne un se suleh nahin ki aur jisney dar ke maarey un mein se kisi ko chhod diya wo ham mein se nahin.''"
5249,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sab qism ke saanpon ko maar dala karo . jo unke badley se darey , wo mujh se nahin .''"
5250,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney saanpon ko unke badley ke dar se chhod diya, wo ham se nahin. jab se hamari in se ladaai shuru hui hai ham ne un se suleh nahin ki .''"
5251,Saiyedna Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha ke ham zamzam ke kunwen ko saaf karna chahtey hain lekin us mein chhotey chhotey saanp hain. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko maar dalney ka hukm diya.
5252,"Janab Salim apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sab qism ke saanpon ko maar dala karo . wo bhi jiski pusht par siyah (ya safed ( rang ki do lakeerein hoti hain aur jiski dam nahin hoti . bila-shuba ye nazar khatm kar detey hain ( jiskey sath unki nazar mil jaey .) aur ye hamal giraaney ka baais bhi bantey hain.'' chunanche Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) jis saanp ko bhi paatey, usey qatl kar daltey they. chunanche Hazrat abu-Lubaba ya Zaid bin Khattab (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne unko dekha ke wo saanp ko dhoond rahey they, to unhoney bayan kya ke ye jo gharon mein rehney waley saanp hain unko qatl kerney se mana kya gaya hai."
5253,Hazrat abu-Lubaba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un saanpon ko jo gharon mein rehtey hain maarney se mana farmaya hai. siwaye unke jin ki pusht par (kali ya safed ( do dhaariyaan hoti hain aur jiski dam nahin hoti . bila-shuba ye nazar khatm kar deney aur aurton ka hamal gira deney ka baais bantey hain.
5254,Janab Naafe riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat abu-Lubaba (Raziallahu anhu) ki mazkura baala hadees maloom honey ke baad Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko dekha gaya ke unhoney apney ghar mein saanp dekha ( to usey qatl nahin kya balke ( uskey mutalliq hukm diya aur baqeea ki taraf bhagaa diya.
5255,"Janab Usama , Hazrat Naafe se mazkura hadees ke silsiley mein riwayat kartey hain. . . . Naafe ne kaha ye riwayat sunney ke baad maine ghar mein saanp dekha . . . .) maarney ki bajaey baqee ki janib bhaga diya. ("
5256,"Janab Muhammad bin Abu-Yahya riwayat kartey hain ke unke walid ne bayan kya ke wo aur unka eik sathi Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ke liye gaey . phir ham unke yahan se nikley to hamen hamara eik sathi mila jo Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan ja raha tha. chunanche ham aa kar masjid mein beth gaey to hamara wo sathi bhi aa gaya. usney bataya ke usney Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''bila-shuba kaee saanp jinn hotey hain. chunanche jo koi apney ghar mein kuch dekhey to chahiye ke usey teen baar mutanabbeh karey, agar wo phir nazar aaye to maar daley . bila-shuba wo shetan hai.''"
5257,"Hazrat abu-Saaib bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein aaya . main unke paas betha hua tha ke maine unki chaarpai ke nichey kisi chiz ki sarsarahat mehsoos ki, maine dekha to wo saanp tha. chunanche main uth kar khada ho gaya , to Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : kya hai? maine kaha ke yahan saanp hai. unhoney kaha : to kya chahtey ho? maine kaha ke usey maarta hun. to unhoney apney ghar ke samney eik makaan ki taraf ishara kya aur kaha : beshak mera chacha zaad usi makaan mein rehta tha. jange-ehzaab ke din usney apney ghar aaney ki ijazat maangi jabke uski nae-nae shaadi hui thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko ijazat de-di aur farmaya ke hathiyar lekar jana . wo apney ghar aaya to dekha ke uski biwi ghar ke darwazey par khadi hai. chunanche usney neze se uski taraf ishara kya ( maarney laga .) to usney kaha : jaldi mat karo . pehley dekh lo ke mujhey kis chiz ne bahir nikala hai? ( dekh lo ke main bahir kyon nikli hun?) chunanche wo ghar ke andar gaya to dekha ke wahan eik bad-soorat saanp tha. chunanche usney apna neza usi mein chubho diya aur usi tarah chubhotey huey bahir ley aaya aur saanp neze ke sath tadap raha tha. unhoney kaha, mujhey nahin maloom ke un mein se pehley kon mara , wo aadmi ya saanp ? chunanche uski qom Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur unhoney kaha : dua farmaeyn ke Allah taala hamarey is aadmi ko wapis (zinda) kar dey . aapney farmaya : ''apney sathi ke liye bakhshish ki dua karo.'' phir farmaya : ''Madina mein kuch jinn musalman huey hain, to jab tum un mein se kisi ko dekho to usey teen baar khabrdar karo . uskey baad agar qatl kerney ka khayal ho to teesri baar ke baad qatl karo.''"
5258,"Janab ibne-Ajlaan ne ye hadees ikhtisaar se riwayat ki, kaha : ''usey teen baar khabardar karey. uskey baad agar zahir ho to qatl kar dey, bila-shuba wo shetan hai.''"
5259,Janab abu-Saaib maula Hisham bin Zohra se riwayat hai ke wo Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey. aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind balke us se kamil riwayat kya. kaha : ''usey teen din tak mutanabbeh karo. agar uskey baad tumharey samney aaye to qatl kar do. bila-shuba wo shetan hai.''
5260,Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Laila apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se gharon mein paey janey waley saanpon ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : ''jab tum un mein se kisi chiz ko apney gharon mein dekho to un se kaho : main tumhen wo qasam deta hun jo Hazrat Nooh Alehissalam ne tumhen di thi. main tumhen wo qasam deta hun jo Hazrat Suleman Alehissalam ne tumhen di thi ke hamen kisi qism ki eza (takleef) na dena. agar phir bhi wo niklen to qatl kar do.''
5261,Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke sab qism ke saanpon ko qatl kar diya karo . siwaye unke jo safed chaandi ki chhadi ki manind hon. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke mujhey eik shakhs ne bataya ke saanp ki shakal mein jinn apney chalney mein tedha ho kar nahin chalta hai. agar wo bilkul sidha chaley to un sha Allah ye uskey jinn honey ki alamat hogi .
5262,Hazrat Aamir bin Saad apney walid Hazrat Saad bin abu-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chhipkali (aur girgit) ko qatl kar deney ka hukm diya hai aur usey chhota fasiq bataya.'' (nuqsan deh janwer.)
5263,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney chhipkali (aur girgit ( ko pehli chot mein maara uskey liye itna-itna sawab hai. aur jisney dusri chot mein maara usey itna itna sawab hai. yani pehley se kam . aur jisney teesri chot mein maara uskey liye itna itna sawab hai. yani dusri baar se bhi kam .''"
5264,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney chhipkali (ya girgit ( ko pehli hi chot mein maar diya uskey liye sattar nekiyan hain.''"
5265,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''anbiya (Alaihimussalam) mein se eik Nabi kisi darkht ke nichey utrey to eik chewnti ne unko kaat liya to unhoney uskey purey bil ko uskey nichey se nikalney ka hukm diya aur phir hukm diya aur unhen jala diya gaya. tu Allah azz-w-jall ne unki taraf wahi ki ke sirf eik hi ko kyon na maara ( jisney ke kaataa tha.'' ("
5266,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik chewnti ne kisi Nabi ko kaat liya to unhoney unke purey bil ke mutalliq hukm diya aur usey jala dala gaya. tu Allah azz-w-jall ne unki taraf wahi ki : kya wajeh hui ke tujhey to eik chewnti ne kaata tha aur to ney puri jamaat ko halak kar dala jo ke) Allah ki) tasbih karti thi?''"
5267,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaar qism ke janweron ko qatl kerney se mana farmaya hai : chewnti , shehad ki makkhi , hudhud aur latura."
5268,"Janab Abdur-Rehman apney walid Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke ham eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. aap qazaey-hajat ke liye gaey, to ham ne eik chidiya dekhi jiskey sath do bachey bhi they. ham ne uskey bachey pakad liye to unki maa apney bachon par girney lagi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur puchha : '' usko uskey bachon se kis ne pareshan kya hai? uskey bachey usko wapis kar do . . . .'' aur aapney dekha ke chewntiyon ka eik bil ham ne jala dala hai. to aapney puchha : ''usko kis ne jalaaya hai?'' ham ne bataya ke ham ne jalaaya hai. aapney farmaya : '' aag ke rab ( Allah taala) ke siwa kisi ko munasib nahin ke kisi ko aag se azab dey .''"
5269,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ek muaalij ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maindak ke mutalliq puchha ke wo usey kisi dawa mein daalta hai to aapney usey uskey qatl kerney se mana farmaya.
5270,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kankariyan maarney se mana farmaya hai. aapney farmaya : '' us se kisi ka shikar nahin hota, na koi dushman zakhmi hota hai, albatta kisi ki aankh phoot sakti hai, ya daant toot sakta hai.''"
5271,"Hazrat umme-Atiya ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Madina main eik aurat thi jo khatney kya karti thi. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : '' khatna gehra mat kya kar , kyonkey us mein aurat ke liye ziyada lazzat aur shohar ke liye bhi ye keyfiyat ziyada pasandida hoti hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke b-waasta Abdul-Malik , Ubaidullah bin Amr se bhi usi ke ham-maani aur iski sanad se marwi (bayan) hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : aur ye hadees qawi nahin hai. usey mursal bhi riwayat kya gaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : aur Muhammad bin Hassaan majhool hai aur hadees zaeef hai."
5272,"Janab Hamza apney walid Hazrat abu-Usaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aapney farmaya jabkey aap masjid se nikal rahey they aur mard aurton ke sath beech raastey mein ghus kar chal rahey they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton se farmaya : '' peechey peechey raho. tumhen munasib nahin ke raastey ke thik beech mein chalo . balke raastey (aur gali (ke ek taraf chala karo.'' chunanche aurat deewar ke sath lag kar chala karti thi. yahan tak ke uska kapda deewar ke sath atak atak jata tha. isliye ke wo deewar ke sath lag kar chalti thi."
5273,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya ke koi aadmi do aurton ke darmiyan ho kar chaley .
5274,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya , Allah azz-w-jall farmata hai ke Adam ka beta mujhey dukh deta hai, wo zamaney ko gaali deta hai. halanke main hi zamana hun, maamla merey hi haath mein hai, raat aur din ko mein hi pherta hun. ibn sarah ne sanad mein Saeed ki bajaey (عن ابن المسيب) kaha (aur wo eik hi shakhsiyat hai. yani Saeed bin Musaiyab ( ."
